\id PRO - Mbula NT with Gen, Exo, Ruth, Psa, Pro, and Jonah [mna] -Papua New Guinea 1996 (DBL 2015) 
\h Sua Tutŋana 
\toc1 Sua Tutŋana 
\toc2 Sua Tutŋana 
\toc3 Tut 
\mt1 Sua Tutŋana  
\c 1  
\q1
\v 1 Iŋgi sua tutŋana mi sua tooroŋan pakan ki Dabit lutuunu Salumo ta king kizin Israel na.   
\s1 Sua tutŋana tiŋgi ka uunu  
\q1
\v 2 Sua tiŋgi ko ipaute iti pa ŋgar ambaiŋana mi ipazal ŋgar kiti.  
\q1 Mi ipei ŋgar kiti pa sua ta izzwe mbulu ambaiŋana mi mbulu sananŋana na.   
\q1
\v 3 Mi sua tiŋgi ko iuulu iti be tagabiizi itundu, mi takam mbulu kiti raama ŋgar.  
\q1 Naso takam mbulu ambaiŋana men ta indeeŋe pa Anutu mi tomtom matan, mi takam mbulu raraate men pizin tomtom ta boozomen.   
\q1
\v 4 Zin wal tau len ŋgar biibi som na, sua tiŋgi ko ipei ŋgar kizin mi iso zin pa mbulu ambaiŋana tabe tikam i.  
\q1 Sua tiŋgi ko ipaute zin naŋgaŋ pa so ŋgar i tabe tito.   
\q1
\v 5 Mi zin wal ta len ŋgar biibi na, zin tomini irao tileŋ la sua ti. Naso tiseeŋge ŋgar kizin.  
\q1 Zin wal tau ŋgar kizin ipet kek na, sua tiŋgi irao ikam peeze pizin.   
\q1
\v 6 Sua tiŋgi ko iuulu iti be takam kat ŋgar pa sua matakiŋa: sua tutŋan, sua tooroŋan, mi sua pambaaraŋan kizin wal ŋgarŋan, ramaki sua kizin pakan ta tizzo na.   
\b  
\q1
\v 7 Mbulu tau tomototo Yooba mi teleŋleŋ la kalŋaana, ina ŋgar ambaiŋana uunu ŋonoono.  
\q1 Tamen wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, matan repilpiili ŋgar ambaiŋana mi sua pazalŋana.\x + \xo 1:7 \xt Kam 20:20; Mbo 111:10; Tut 9:10\x*   
\s1 Tagaaba zin wal sananŋan pa mbulu kizin pepe  
\q1
\v 8 O lutuŋ, sombe tomom ipazalu, na leŋ la sua kini.  
\q1 Mi mbulu ambaiŋana ta nom ipaute u pa na, ta kembena. Zem pepe. Kiskis mi to.\x + \xo 1:8 \xt Tut 6:20, 19:20\x*   
\q1
\v 9 Pa sua kizin ko iurpe mbulu ku ma ambai pa Anutu mi tomtom matan,  
\q1 kembei natabu ma mogar ta iwe aigau piti na.\x + \xo 1:9 \xt Tut 4:9, 19:20\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 10 Lutuŋ, sombe wal sananŋan tiwatu pa sua kizin mbuyeeneŋana be gaaba zin,  
\q1 na leŋ zin pepe.\x + \xo 1:10 \xt Tut 16:29\x*   
\q1
\v 11 Wal tana tizzo ta kembei:  
\q1 “Ai, mar itiŋan tala ma teke su zaala lwoono mi tazaŋzaaŋa.  
\q1 Beso tomtom tasa ipa pa zaala ma imar, to tupuni sorok ma imeete.   
\q1
\v 12 Ko tapamorsopi, mi tupuni ma imeete,  
\q1 kembei meeteŋana ipamorsop tomtom mata yaryaaraŋana, mi imeete karau men ma isula lene naala.   
\q1
\v 13 Naso takam lende koroŋ ambaimbaiŋan matakiŋa ta kan kadon bibip i,  
\q1 mi tadaaba ruumu kiti pa mburu tana ma bok.   
\q1
\v 14 Mi nu ta kembena. Sombe gaaba yam, inako amur ndomom tomini. Pa mburu ta so takam na, ko tarai ma lende lende.”   
\b  
\q1
\v 15 O lutuŋ, sombe tikam sua ta kembei pu, na ruutu itum, mi la gaaba zin pepe.  
\q1 Zaala ta titoto na, nu to zin pa pepe.   
\q1
\v 16 Pa zin na, karau men mi timaŋgaŋga be tikam zaaba pizin tomtom, mi tipun zin ma timetmeete.  
\q1 Tiserseere kat pa sanaana kamŋana.\x + \xo 1:16 \xt Ro 3:15\x*   
\q1
\v 17 Kwiili ta imbot la mban na, ye tire kek.  
\q1 Tamen tikam kinkiini pa mban be tikan, tana tila ma kwiili ikam zin.   
\q1
\v 18 Mi wal sananŋan tana ta kembena. Mbulu kizin ta tikewe mi tizaŋzaaŋa zin tomtom, ina kaimer ko imiili pizin mi ikam zaaba pizin ma timetmeete.  
\q1 Tamen tikilaala som, mi tila men.   
\q1
\v 19 Ŋonoono kat. Wal boozomen taso tikamam malmal be tikem len koroŋ, na zaala kizin ta kembei.  
\q1 Mbulu kizin tana ko ipasaana mbotŋana kizin, mi tisaana ma tila len.\x + \xo 1:19 \xt 1Tim 6:10\x*   
\s1 Bobi ki ŋgar ambaiŋana  
\q1
\v 20 Ŋgar ambaiŋana ikewe piti som. Ina kembei moori ta imbotmbot zaala biibi,  
\q1 mi ilala nol uunu tomini mi ipaŋarairai kalŋaana.\x + \xo 1:20 \xt Tut 8:1-3\x*   
\q1
\v 21 Mi sombe zin iwal biibi tilup zin su kar keteene, som zaala kwoono,  
\q1 na ni iboboobo zin ma izzo ta kembei:   
\q1
\v 22 Niom wal ta leyom ŋgar biibi som na, parei? Leleyom be kombotmbot men ta kembei ma alok?  
\q1 Niom wal ta kapakurkur ituyom mi kerepilpiili ŋgar ambaiŋana na, mi niom wal kankaanaŋoyom ta kapase pa ituyom mi leleyom pa ŋgar ambaiŋana ri sa som na, ŋiizi mi kezem mbulu tiom tana?   
\q1
\v 23 Nio aŋso aŋpazal yom. Tamen leleyom be kotooro ŋgar tiom som.  
\q1 Mibe kotooro yom, so aŋswe ŋgar ta imbotmbot la leleŋ i, mi aŋso yom pa.   
\b  
\q1
\v 24 Nio ti, aŋbelmbel sua piom. Tamen niom kitidit kalŋoŋ.  
\q1 Mi aŋkololo yom be kamar, tamen leleyom be kamar som.   
\q1
\v 25 Pa ŋgar ambaiŋana ta aŋzzo yom pa i na, leleyom pa som.  
\q1 Mi aŋtomtoombo be aŋpazal yom na, keleŋleŋ la kalŋoŋ som.   
\b  
\q1
\v 26-27 Tana kaimer, sombe pataŋana biibi sa itok yom kembei miiri biibi,  
\q1 mi ipasaana yom kembei miiri napiu,  
\q1 mi isalakaala yom, mi ikau yom, mi ikam yom ma keseŋeeŋe,  
\q1 na nio tomini ko uteŋ katkat piom, mi aŋseeŋge piom.\x + \xo 1:26-27 \xt Mbo 2:4+\x*   
\q1
\v 28 To niom ko kataŋroro yo be aŋuulu yom. Tamen nio ko aŋleŋ yom som.  
\q1 Mi ko kuru yo. Tamen ko karao be kendeeŋe yo na som.\x + \xo 1:28 \xt Mbo 18:41+\x*   
\q1
\v 29 Pa leleyom pa ŋgar ambaiŋana ri sa som.  
\q1 Mi leleyom be komoto Yooba mi keleŋ la kalŋaana som.   
\q1
\v 30 Indeeŋe ta aŋzzo yom pa ŋgar ambaiŋana na, kakan la kalŋoŋ som.  
\q1 Mi indeeŋe ta aŋtoombo be aŋpazal yom na, motoyom pasom sua tio kembei koroŋ sorok.   
\q1
\v 31 Tana mbulu bozboozo ta kakamam, ta iŋgi be kakan ka ŋonoono.  
\q1 Gorgori kurru zaala sananŋana, tana iŋgi be kayamaana kat ka pataŋana.\x + \xo 1:31 \xt Tut 14:14; Ga 6:7\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 32 Pa zin wal ta len ŋgar biibi som, mi tileŋsil sua na, mbulu kizin tana ko ipun zin ma timetmeete.  
\q1 Mi zin wal kankaanaŋan ta tipase pa zitun mi tindemeere sorok na, mbulu kizin tana ko ipasaana zin ma tila len.   
\q1
\v 33 Tamen zin wal ta so tileŋleŋ la kalŋoŋ, na nio ko aŋporoukaala zin ma timbot ambai.  
\q1 Irao timoto na som. Pa kosa sa ko irao be ipasaana zin na som.”\x + \xo 1:33 \xt Mbo 112:8\x*   
\c 2  
\s1 Takam kinkiini pa ŋgar ambaiŋana  
\q1
\v 1 O lutuŋ, kan la sua tio ti.  
\q1 Re tutu tio ta boozomen kembei koroŋ ku ŋonoono, mi kiskis ma imbol la lelem.   
\q1
\v 2 Ŋgun talŋom pa ŋgar ambaiŋana,  
\q1 mi ur lelem be kilaala kat ŋgar iŋgoi ta ambai ma ilip.   
\q1
\v 3 Taŋroro Anutu be ipei ŋgar ku,  
\q1 mi iso u pa ŋgar iŋgoi ta ambai ma ilip.\x + \xo 2:3 \xt Yems 1:5\x*   
\q1
\v 4 Kam kinkiini pa ŋgar ambaiŋana mi rru,  
\q1 kembei tomtom tikelel toono mi tirru silba mi koroŋ ndabokbokŋan pakan ta timbotmbot la toono leleene na.   
\q1
\v 5 Naso mbot mat pa mbulu ki tomototo Yooba mi teleŋleŋ la kalŋaana.  
\q1 Mi nu ko ute kat Anutu.\x + \xo 2:5 \xt Pil 3:10\x*   
\q1
\v 6 Pa Yooba ta ikamam lende ŋgar ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Sua ta iwedet pa kwoono, ta ipeyei ŋgar kiti, mi iuluulu iti be tikilaala ŋgar iŋgoi ta ambai ma ilip.   
\q1
\v 7 Zin wal ta mbulu kizin iŋgeeze men na, ni iuluulu zin ma uraata kizin iurur ŋonoono.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tipa pai kizin ma ambai men na, ni iwe kembei siŋgiao pizin.\x + \xo 2:7 \xt Mbo 84:11\x*   
\q1
\v 8 Pa ni mataana pizin wal ndeeŋeŋan pa pai kizin.  
\q1 Zin wal ta tiurur lelen pini mi tikiskis mbulu kini na, ni imborro zin ma timbotmbot ambai.\x + \xo 2:8 \xt Mbo 1:6, 18:25, 91:3-7\x*   
\s1 Ŋgar ambaiŋana iuluulu iti be tombot molo pa mbulu sananŋana  
\q1
\v 9 Tana kam kinkiini pa ŋgar ambaiŋana. Naso mbot mat pa zaala ambaimbaiŋan ta boozomen.  
\q1 Nu ko kilaala mbulu ta indeeŋe men pa Anutu mi tomtom matan,  
\q1 mi kam mbulu raraate men pizin tomtom ta munŋaana men.   
\q1
\v 10 Pa ŋgar ambaiŋana ko izeebu.  
\q1 Mi sombe kam kat ŋgar, nako yamaana ambai.   
\q1
\v 11 Mbulu ki tombot mi takam kat ŋgar muŋgu, inako imboro u ma mbot ambai.  
\q1 Mi sombe nu rao be kilaala ŋgar iŋgoi ta ambai ma ilip, nako iuulu u be mbotmbot molo pa koroŋ boozomen tabe ipasaanu i.   
\b  
\q1
\v 12 Ŋgar ambaiŋana ko iuulu u be mbotmbot molo pa zaala ta wal sananŋan titoto na.  
\q1 Wal tana tipasansaana zin tomtom pa sua kizin pakamkaamŋana.   
\q1
\v 13 Zin tizem zaala ndeeŋeŋana kek,  
\q1 mi iŋgi titoto zaala ki zugut.   
\q1
\v 14 Zin lelen pa mbulu sananŋana ilip.  
\q1 Sombe tikam ŋoobo mbulu pa tomtom sa, ina ikam zin ma menmeen zin biibi.   
\q1
\v 15 Tana zaala ŋonoono, zin tizem kek.  
\q1 Mi iŋgi titoto zaala sananŋana.   
\b  
\q1
\v 16 Ŋgar ambaiŋana ko iuulu u be mbotmbot molo pizin moori zaala lwoono kan.  
\q1 Zin moori ta kembei kwon imbesmbeeze pizin tomooto bekena tiyaaru zin ma tila kizin.\x + \xo 2:16 \xt Tut 6:24, 7:5\x*   
\q1
\v 17 Pa zin moori ta kembei tipizil ndemen pa kusin bizin ta mata popoten kana i kek.  
\q1 Mi sua kizin mbukŋana ta tikam la Anutu mataana na, matan mbelele kek.   
\q1
\v 18 Zaala ta isula pa Andewa na, kwoono imbot kat ta ndeete uunu kizin.  
\q1 Tana wal ta so titop la kizin, nako tisula ma tigaaba zin wal meeteŋan ma ziŋan timbotmbot.\x + \xo 2:18 \xt Tut 5:5, 7:27\x*   
\q1
\v 19 Zin wal ta so tila kizin moori ta kembei, na kizin tasa ko imiili mi ito zaala ki mbotŋana mata yaryaaraŋana mini na som.  
\q1 Sombe tila, na timbot pataaŋa.   
\s1 Zaala ru  
\q1
\v 20 Tana zaala tau wal ambaimbaiŋan titoto na, nu tomini motom iŋgal be pa pa.  
\q1 To zin wal ndeeŋeŋan pa mbulu kizin totomen. Zem pepe.   
\q1
\v 21 Pa zin wal ta len uunu sa isaana som, mi mbulu kizin iŋgeeze men,  
\q1 ta tirao be timbotmbot pa toono ta Yooba ikam pa wal kini na.\x + \xo 2:21 \xt Mbo 37:9; Mt 5:5\x*   
\q1
\v 22 Tamen zin wal ta tipizil ndemen pini na, Yooba ko ipuru zin ma tila len pa toono kini, kembei ta tomtom tipuru ro sananŋan pa mokleene kizin.  
\q1 Ni ko iyembut kat zin wal sananŋan ma irao timar tigarau toono kini mini som.   
\c 3  
\s1 Tapase pa Yooba men  
\q1
\v 1 Lutuŋ, sua ta nio aŋkam pu na, motom mbelele pepe.  
\q1 Motom iŋgalŋgal tutu tio ta boozomen mi kiskis la lelem.   
\q1
\v 2 Pa ina ko ikamu ma mbot ambai,  
\q1 mi iseeŋge mbotŋana ku ma molo.   
\q1
\v 3 Mbulu ki tu'urur lelende pa Anutu mi zin tomtom mi tototo sua kiti mbukŋana na, zem pepe.  
\q1 Mbulu ru tana, kiskis la lelem mi zzwe totomen. Pa ina ko iwe kembei aigau ta imbot la ketem na.\x + \xo 3:3 \xt Tut 6:21, 7:3\x*   
\q1
\v 4 Tana kiskis mbulu ru tana. Naso ndeeŋe kampeŋana biibi,  
\q1 mi Anutu ziŋan zin tomtom tire u kembei nu lem ŋgar ambaiŋana.   
\b  
\q1
\v 5 Re: Kokena pase pa itum ŋgar ku.  
\q1 Ur lelem imap ila ki Yooba, mi pase pini men.   
\q1
\v 6 Mi so zaala i ta lelem iur pa be to, na kam ŋgar pa Yooba muŋgu, mana kam.  
\q1 Naso ni ikam peeze piwi mi iso u pa ka zaala.   
\q1
\v 7 Re itum kembei nu rao kat pa ŋgar pepe.  
\q1 Moto Yooba, leŋleŋ la kalŋaana, mi pizil ndemem pa mbulu sananŋan ta boozomen.\x + \xo 3:7 \xt Tut 28:26; Ro 12:16\x*   
\q1
\v 8 Pa mbulu ta kembei ko iuulu kulim ma imbot ambai,  
\q1 mi ikam ma kulim iŋgeeze mi nim se pa uraata.   
\b  
\q1
\v 9 Yooba, ni ikam lem koroŋ boozo kek. Tana pimilmiili koroŋ pakan ma ilala kini bekena pakuri pa.  
\q1 Koroŋ ku paazaŋan ta boozomen na, motom iŋgal be pazas mataana kana ma ilala kini.\x + \xo 3:9 \xt Kam 23:19\x*   
\q1
\v 10 Naso Anutu ikam ma mokleene ku ipiyooto kini boozo, mi diditu ku bokbok men.  
\q1 Mi baen ku ko ipiyotyooto ŋonon ta sorok som, mi baen piiziŋana muriini bokbok kat pa yok baen popoŋana.   
\b  
\q1
\v 11 Lutuŋ, sombe Yooba ikam mbulu sa pu bekena ipazalu pa, na parsiki pepe.  
\q1 Mi sombe iyaambu, na lelem iŋgis pa pepe.\x + \xo 3:11 \xt Ibr 12:5-7,10; Tur 3:19\x*   
\q1
\v 12 Pa zin wal ta Yooba leleene pizin na, ni ipazalzal zin,  
\q1 kembei ta takamam pa lutundu bizin tau lelende pizin ilip na.\x + \xo 3:12 \xt Tut 13:24\x*   
\s1 Ŋgar ambaiŋana iuluulu iti pa zaala matakiŋa  
\q1
\v 13 Tomtom ta so iru ŋgar ambaiŋana ma indeeŋe, mi ikilaala ŋgar iŋgoi ta ambai ma ilip,  
\q1 nako leleene ambai kat, mi kampeŋana ki Anutu imbotmbot se kini.   
\q1
\v 14 Pa ŋgar ambaiŋana ipiyotyooto ŋonoono ambaimbaiŋan boozomen piti.  
\q1 Ilip pa silba ma gol.\x + \xo 3:14 \xt Mbo 19:10, 119:72,127; Tut 8:10+\x*   
\q1
\v 15 Mi ilip pa pat milmilŋan pakan ta ndabokbokŋan kat.  
\q1 Tana koroŋ boozomen ta nu lelem pa i na, sa irao kembei ŋgar ambaiŋana na som.\x + \xo 3:15 \xt Mt 13:45\x*   
\q1
\v 16 Ŋgar ambaiŋana namaana ru iteege koroŋ boozomen be ikam piti.  
\q1 Namaana woono irao iseeŋge swondo ma molo.  
\q1 Mi namaana ŋas na, irao ikam lende koroŋ boozo, mi ikam ma zanda iwe biibi.\x + \xo 3:16 \xt Tut 4:10, 8:18, 9:11, 10:27, 22:4\x*   
\q1
\v 17 Zin wal ta so titoto zaala ki ŋgar ambaiŋana, nako tiyamaana ambai.  
\q1 Pa mboti kizin ko ndabok kat.   
\q1
\v 18 Ŋgar ambaiŋana, ina iwe kembei ke ki mbotŋana mata yaryaaraŋana.  
\q1 Pa zin wal ta so tikami ma iwe len mi tikiskisi, nako timbot ambai, mi kampeŋana ki Anutu imbotmbot se kizin.\x + \xo 3:18 \xt Un 2:9; Tut 11:30; Tur 2:7\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 19 Muŋgu kat Yooba ito ŋgar kini ambaiŋana, mi iur toono uunu ma imbol.  
\q1 Mi ikam kat ŋgar, mana iur saamba.\x + \xo 3:19 \xt Mbo 136:5\x*   
\q1
\v 20 Muŋgu kat yok ta imbot meleebe na, ise raama mburaana biibi. Ito ni ŋgar kini.  
\q1 Mi ŋgar kini, ta izzo i pa mbulu tabe ikam ma yaŋ izzu pa gubur tiene, mi tolou iwedet.   
\b  
\q1
\v 21 Lutuŋ, motom iŋgal be kiskis ŋgar ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Ŋgar ta iurur ŋonoono na, zem pepe.   
\q1
\v 22 Pa ina ko ikamu ma mbot ambai,  
\q1 mi ipeŋgeeze mbulu ku, kembei aigau ta imbot la ketem na.   
\q1
\v 23 To pa pai ku ma ambai men.  
\q1 Pa kosasa ko ipasaanu som, mi irao tutkat kumbum na som.\x + \xo 3:23 \xt Mbo 37:24; Tut 4:12\x*   
\q1
\v 24 Mi sombe su murim be keene, nako moto som.  
\q1 Ko keene kat lem.\x + \xo 3:24 \xt Mbo 4:8, 91:5+; Tut 6:22\x*   
\q1
\v 25 Tana pataŋana biibi tabe ipamurur zin wal sananŋan mi ipasaana zin i, nu ko irao moto na som.\x + \xo 3:25 \xt Mbo 112:7+\x*   
\q1
\v 26 Pa Yooba ko imbotmbot zilŋom uunu mi imborro u.  
\q1 Tana kilis sa ko irao ikeene kumbum na som.   
\s1 Sua tutŋana pakan  
\q1
\v 27-28 Sombe pataŋana indeeŋe tomtom sa mi nu lem uraata be uuli, na titi pepe. Sombe rao be uuli, na kam pataaŋa.  
\q1 So pini be ila ma gaaga to imiili mini pepe. Sombe lem koroŋ imbot, na kam pini pataaŋa.\x + \xo 3:27-28 \xt Ŋgo 9:36; Ga 6:10; 1Yo 3:17-18\x*   
\q1
\v 29 Tomtom ta so ruumu kini igarau u, na kam ŋgar be pasaani pepe.  
\q1 Pa ina ni indemeere kembei nu ko kam mbulu ambaiŋana men pini.   
\q1
\v 30 Mi tomtom ta so ikam ŋoobo mbulu som,  
\q1 na maŋga mi kam sorok sua pini pepe.   
\q1
\v 31 Zin wal ta tikamam zaaba pizin tomtom na, motom berber pa mburu kizin pepe,  
\q1 mi to zin pa zaala kizin pepe.\x + \xo 3:31 \xt Mbo 1:1, 37:1,7; Tut 4:14-15\x*   
\q1
\v 32 Pa zin wal ta tikamam ŋoobo mbulu na, Yooba leleene pizin ri sa som kat.  
\q1 Tamen zin wal ta mbulu kizin iŋgeeze men na, Yooba igabgaaba zin mi izzwe leleene mi ŋgar kini pizin.\x + \xo 3:32 \xt Mbo 101:4, 25:14\x*   
\q1
\v 33 Wal sananŋan ziŋan wal kizin na, Yooba kete malmalŋana kini imbotmbot se kizin.  
\q1 Mi wal ndeeŋeŋan ziŋan wal kizin na, kampeŋana kini imbotmbot se kizin.   
\q1
\v 34 Zin wal ta tipakurkur zitun mi matan pasom ŋgar ambaiŋana na, Yooba irepilpiili zin.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tikototo zitun na, ni leleene pizin mi ikampewe zin.\x + \xo 3:34 \xt 1Pe 5:5+; Yems 4:10\x*   
\q1
\v 35 Zin wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana, nako zan iwe biibi.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro, nako kan miaŋ biibi.   
\c 4  
\s1 Takam kinkiini pa ŋgar ambaiŋana  
\q1
\v 1 O lutuŋŋan, tomoyom ta nio i. Keleŋ sua tio tutŋana ti mi motoyom iŋgalŋgal.  
\q1 Naso ŋgar tiom ipet mi kikilaala ŋgar iŋgoi ta ambai ma ilip.\x + \xo 4:1 \xt Tut 1:8, 13:1\x*   
\q1
\v 2 Ŋgar ambaiŋana ta tipaute yo pa kek, ta iŋgi be aŋkam piom i.  
\q1 Tana kezem sua tio ti pepe.   
\q1
\v 3 Muŋgu ta nio naŋgaŋŋoŋ mi aŋbotmbot tamaŋ ruumu kini na, naŋgoŋ lutuunu tamen ŋonoono ta nio i.  
\q1 Tana ni leleene pio ilip.   
\q1
\v 4 Indeeŋe mazwaana tana, tamaŋ ipaute yo ma iso ta kembei:  
\q1 “Motom iŋgal be kiskis sua tio ila lelem, mi toto tutu tio. Naso mbot ambai.   
\q1
\v 5 Kam kinkiini be kam lem ŋgar ambaiŋana mi kilaala ŋgar iŋgoi ta ambai ma ilip.  
\q1 Mi motom mbelele sua tio pepe, mi paŋoobo pa pepe.   
\q1
\v 6 Pizil ndemem pa ŋgar ambaiŋana pepe.\f + \fr 4:6 \ft Pa ina ko iuulu be mbotmbot molo pa mbulu sananŋana.\f*   
\q1
\v 7 Kam kinkiini pa ŋgar ambaiŋana. Pa ina ilip pa koroŋ ta boozomen.  
\q1 Tana ru zaala be kam lem ŋgar ambaiŋana. Sombe zem koroŋ ku ta boozomen ma ila bekena kam lem ŋgar ambaiŋana, na ila lak! Nin pepe.\x + \xo 4:7 \xt Mt 13:45,46; Tut 23:23\x*   
\q1
\v 8 Nu sombe pakur ŋgar ambaiŋana, nako ŋgar ambaiŋana ipakuru tomini.  
\q1 Mi sombe yogeege lem ŋgar ambaimbaiŋan matakiŋa, nako ikam ma zom iwe biibi.   
\q1
\v 9 Ŋgar ambaiŋana ko iwe kembei mogar ndabokŋana kat tau imbot la ndomom mi iwe aigau pu.   
\b  
\q1
\v 10 O lutuŋ, leŋ sua tio ti mi kan la.  
\q1 Naso mbotmbot su toono ma molo, mi kom ndaama boozo.\x + \xo 4:10 \xt Tut 3:16+\x*   
\q1
\v 11 Nio iŋgi aŋpaute u pa zaala ki ŋgar ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Aŋmuŋmuuŋgu pu, mi aŋzzo u pa zaala ndeeŋeŋana.   
\q1
\v 12 Zaala tana, ambaiŋana. Sombe pa pa, na koroŋ sa ko irao iŋgal kumbum na som.  
\q1 Mi sombe loondo pa, na kumbum ko irao ikam giris ma mel na som.   
\q1
\v 13 Sua tutŋana ta aŋkam pu na, zem pepe.  
\q1 Motom iŋgalŋgal mi kiskis la lelem.  
\q1 Pa ina ko ikamu ma mbot ambai.   
\s1 Tombot molo pizin wal sananŋan  
\q1
\v 14-15 Zaala ta zin wal sananŋan titoto na, ur kumbum ise ri sa pepe.  
\q1 Kokena gaaba zin mi to zin pa mbulu kizin.  
\q1 Tana pizil ndemem pa zaala kizin mi mbotmbot molo pa. Motom iŋgalŋgal zaala ambaiŋana men mi toto.\x + \xo 4:14-15 \xt Mbo 1:1, 17:4-5; Tut 1:15, 3:31\x*   
\q1
\v 16 Pa wal sananŋan ŋgar kizin ta kembei: Aigule ta boozomen bela tikam mbulu sananŋana sa, tona lelen ambai mi tisu murin ma tikeene kat len.  
\q1 Mi sombe tipasaana tomtom sa som, na irao tikeenekaala matan na som.   
\q1
\v 17 Pa mbulu sananŋana ta iwe kan kini. Mi mbulu ki malmal ta iwe kan yok.  
\q1 Aigule ta boozomen bela tikam, to lelen ambai.   
\q1
\v 18-19 Tana zin wal sananŋan titoto zaala ki zugut biibi.  
\q1 Mi koroŋ tabe titutkat zin sala ma sursur ma tila kaŋkuruŋ su na, tikilaala som.  
\q1 Tamen wal ndeeŋeŋan na, zaala kizin toro. Mbotŋana kizin kembei zoŋ mataana ta pok ma ise,  
\q1 mi iyaara iyaara ma ila irao aigule palakuutu, to ka azuŋka biibi kat.\x + \xo 4:18-19 \xt Mt 5:13; Yo 8:12; Pil 2:15\x*   
\s1 Matanda iŋgal itundu  
\q1
\v 20 O lutuŋ, motom mar mi ŋgun talŋom pa sua ta aŋzzo i.   
\q1
\v 21 Motom mbelele sua tio pepe.  
\q1 Kiskis mi ur la lelem.\x + \xo 4:21 \xt Tut 3:21\x*   
\q1
\v 22 Pa zin wal ta so tikam sua tio ti ma iwe len, nako tindeeŋe mbotŋana ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Mi sua tio ko iuulu zin ma kulin tomini imbot ambai.\x + \xo 4:22 \xt Tut 3:8\x*   
\q1
\v 23 Motom iŋgalŋgal be mboro kat lelem. Ina koroŋ biibi ta ilip pa koroŋ ta boozomen.  
\q1 Pa lelende ta ipiyotyooto mbotŋana kiti.\x + \xo 4:23 \xt Mt 12:34; Mk 7:20+; Lu 6:45\x*   
\q1
\v 24 Mi mboro kat kwom tomini:  
\q1 Kokena sua sananŋana, som pakaamŋana sa ipet pa.\x + \xo 4:24 \xt Ep 4:29; Yems 3:6\x*   
\q1
\v 25 Motom su pa zaala ndeeŋeŋana men mi toto.  
\q1 Motom rikrik pepe.\x + \xo 4:25 \xt Mbo 119:37\x*   
\q1
\v 26 Motom iŋgalŋgal kumbum be itoto kat zaala ndeeŋeŋana.  
\q1 Naso pa pai ku ma ambai men, mi irao yasipir na som.\x + \xo 4:26 \xt Mbo 119:5; Ibr 12:13\x*   
\q1
\v 27 Kumbum ilalae mi imarmare pepe.  
\q1 Kokena kam mbulu sananŋana sa.   
\c 5  
\s1 Mbulu ki tuurnol ko ipasaana kat iti  
\q1
\v 1 O lutuŋ, leŋ la ŋgar ambaiŋana tabe aŋso u pa i.  
\q1 Ŋgun talŋom pio. Pa sua tio ti ko iuulu u be kilaala mbulu iŋgoi ta ambai ma ilip.   
\q1
\v 2 Naso kam kat ŋgar,  
\q1 mi kwom izzo ŋgar ambaiŋana men.   
\q1
\v 3 Kozo re u pizin moori zaala lwoono kan. Pa sua kizin inamut kat, kembei ta bigil suruunu.  
\q1 Sua ta iwedet pa kwon na, mbuyeeneŋana ma ilip.\x + \xo 5:3 \xt Mbo 55:21; Tut 2:16+, 6:24\x*   
\q1
\v 4 Mi nu sombe la ki moori sa ta kembei, na kaimer mbotŋana ku ko isaana ma ipakpak kat.  
\q1 Ko kembei ta buza mata mbaaru iŋgalu.   
\q1
\v 5 Nu sombe to zaala kini, nako meete ma la lem.  
\q1 Pa ni ko iyaaru ma sula lem naala.\x + \xo 5:5 \xt Tut 2:18, 7:27\x*   
\q1
\v 6 Zaala ki mbotŋana mata yaryaaraŋana na, ni ikamam ŋgar pa ri sa som kat.  
\q1 Zaala ta ni itoto, ina ipa ndel pa zaala ndeeŋeŋana.  
\q1 Tamen ni ikilaala som.   
\q1
\v 7 Tana lutuŋŋan, keleŋ la kalŋoŋ.  
\q1 Kipizil ndemeyom pa sua tio ti pepe.   
\q1
\v 8 Moori ta kembei na, kagarau i pepe.  
\q1 Kombotmbot molo pini.\x + \xo 5:8 \xt 2Tim 2:22\x*   
\q1
\v 9 Kokena ipasaana zoyom, mi koroŋ tiom ta ndaama ndaama mi kembelmbel uraata pa na, imap pini sorok.  
\q1 Mi koroŋ toro tomini. Sombe kusiini ileŋ, nako iseeze kat motoyom. Irao imuŋai yom ri sa na som. Som kat!\x + \xo 5:9 \xt Tut 6:34-35\x*   
\q1
\v 10 Tana koroŋ tiom ambaimbaiŋan ta uze tiom tiene na, ko iwe wal pakan len,  
\q1 be tikanan ma tiwinin.   
\q1
\v 11 Mi niom ko kusu ma kewe koroŋ sorok, mi mete ikam yom ma mburoyom imap mi saana kat.  
\q1 Mi sombe swoyom igarau, to ko ketwer ma koso ta kembei:   
\q1
\v 12 “O yae, muŋgu wal pakan titut yo. Mi parei ta aŋleŋ la kalŋan som?  
\q1 Indeeŋe ta titoombo be tipazal yo na, aŋrepilpiili sua kizin.   
\q1
\v 13 Mi titoombo be tipaute yo na, aŋgun talŋoŋ pizin som,  
\q1 mi aŋto sua kizin som.   
\q1
\v 14 Tana iŋgi mbotŋana tio isaana kat,  
\q1 mi koŋ miaŋ biibi ila iwal matan.”\x + \xo 5:14 \xt 1Kor 6:18\x*   
\s1 Matanda iŋgal itundu kusindi bizin men  
\q1
\v 15 O lutuŋ, niomru kusim men kaparlup yom mi menmeen yom pa mbulu ki ula.  
\q1 Pa ina kembei nu winin yok ta itum touŋom na.   
\q1
\v 16 Parei ta nu lelem be la kizin moori pakan ma niomŋan kekeene?  
\q1 Pa ina kembei nu kam yok ta ireere pa yok ku lepeene na, mi liŋ sorok su zaala lwoono, som kar keteene.   
\q1
\v 17 Ula ka mbulu, ina koroŋ ki niomru kusim men be menmeen yom pa.  
\q1 Tana niomŋan moori pakan kakam pepe.   
\q1
\v 18 Bela nu menmeenu pa kusim ta nu naŋgaŋŋom mi wooli na.  
\q1 Naso kampeŋana ki Anutu imbotmbot se ula tiom, mi waem ko ikamu ma lelem ambai kat.   
\q1
\v 19 Pa ni ko iurur kat leleene pu, mi nu re ruŋguunu mi koroŋŋanŋan ta boozomen na, ambai men pa motom.  
\q1 Zuzuunu ko ikamu ma so tekteege lem.  
\q1 Tana ni ko ikam kat lelem, mi ŋgar ku imap ma ilala kini.   
\b  
\q1
\v 20 O lutuŋ, kokena moori toro ikam lelem ma zem ula ku.  
\q1 Re: Nu sombe teege tomooto toro kusiini zuzuunu, ko ambai? Som.   
\q1
\v 21 Pa mbulu boozomen ta iti tomtom takamam na, imbot kat mat pa Yooba mataana.  
\q1 Ni itirtiiri iti pa mbulu kiti ta boozomen.\x + \xo 5:21 \xt Mbo 11:4, 26:2, 139:23; Ibr 4:13\x*   
\q1
\v 22 Mbulu sananŋana kizin wal sananŋan ta ikaukau zin.  
\q1 Mbulu kizin ta irao pa Yooba mataana som na, ina iwe kembei wooro be tipo zin pa.\x + \xo 5:22 \xt Mbo 9:16\x*   
\q1
\v 23 Tana wal ta kembei ko timeete ma tila len. Paso tiyaraama zitun som tau.  
\q1 Ŋgar kizin ikankaana kat mi timbelmbel zooroŋana. Tabe ikam zin ma tipaŋoobo pa zaala ambaiŋana.\x + \xo 5:23 \xt Tut 11:5\x*   
\c 6  
\s1 Tumbuk sua be tokot tomtom toro mbun kini pepe  
\q1
\v 1 Lutuŋ, sombe waem toro sa ikam mbun, mi tiwi u be mbuk sua ta kembei: “Sombe ni itunu irao be ikot som, na nio ko aŋmender pini mi aŋkot mbun kini.” Na sua mbukŋana ta kembei, kam pepe.\x + \xo 6:1 \xt Tut 11:15, 17:18, 20:16, 22:26, 27:13\x*   
\q1
\v 2 Pa ina, sua ta ipet pa itum kwom, ta ko iwe kembei kilis pu be ikeenu.   
\q1
\v 3 Tana mbotmbot pepe! Ru lem zaala sa be tatke itum pa kilis tana. Pa tomtom ta waem tana ikam mbun la kini na, nu mbotmbot la namaana kek.  
\q1 Tana koto itum, koŋuru tomtom tana ma la, mi taŋroro i be mataana mbiriizikaala sua ku mbukŋana tana.  
\q1 Pazonognoogi ma irao ileŋ la kalŋom.   
\q1
\v 4 Keene ma mbot aigule toro pepe.  
\q1 Maŋga mi la ta buri be re i!   
\q1
\v 5 Kozo kam kembei ŋge ta iti la pu, mi ipus ma ila ne,  
\q1 som kilis ikeeni mi ipurus.   
\s1 Tamaol pepe  
\q1
\v 6 Nu ta tomtom maolŋom na, la ma re moolo mbulu kizin mi kam ŋgar pa.\x + \xo 6:6 \xt Tut 10:4, 20:4\x*   
\q1
\v 7 Zin len biibi sa be iur zin pa uraata mi ikam peeze pizin na som.   
\q1
\v 8 Tamen mazwaana ta so kini boozo imbotmbot na, tiyyo mi tindoundou lae.  
\q1 Beso mazwaana ki peteele, to tirao pa kan kini.\x + \xo 6:8 \xt Tut 30:24-25\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 9 Nu tomtom maolŋom, ŋiizi na zem keeneŋana mi maŋga?   
\q1
\v 10-11 Parei, nu sombe mbulu ki namanda ikamam uraata som, mi ketende izzu, mi tekenne lende sorok, ina ambai? Na kozo re u. Pa molo som to su ma mbot ŋoobo kat mi ru zolom.  
\q1 Mbulu ta kembei ko ipamorsopu kembei ta wal kuumbuŋan tikamam i. Mi ko iwe kembei tomtom ta ipasepeelu pa le koroŋ, mi iniimu ma map kat.\x + \xo 6:10-11 \xt Tut 24:33+\x*   
\s1 Wal sananŋan ko tindeeŋe pataŋana  
\q1
\v 12 Wal sananŋan ta tipasansaana mboti kizin tomtom na, kwon ambai som kat.   
\q1
\v 13 Mi lelen be tiswe mbulu mi ŋgar kizin ma ipet mat na som.  
\q1 Tana matan ikinmetmeete, mi tiurur naman, mi tikamam mbulu pakan pa kumbun, bekena tipatooŋo waen bizin pa so mbulu i tabe tikam i.\x + \xo 6:13 \xt Mbo 35:19; Tut 10:10\x*   
\q1
\v 14 Lelen na, iurur pa mbulu soroksorok boozomen ta sananŋan i.  
\q1 Mi tipesese zin tomtom mi tikamam ma ŋoŋi imbotmbot la mazwan.   
\q1
\v 15 Tamen molo som to pataŋana biibi sa ko ipamurur zin, mi ipasaana zin ma tila len.  
\q1 Mi ko len zaala sa be timbot ambai mini na som.   
\s1 Mbulu pakan ta Yooba leleene pa ri sa som  
\q1
\v 16 Mbulu lamata mi ta, ta Yooba leleene pa ri sa som, mi iurur koi pa.  
\q1 E-e, aŋso ŋoobo. Mbulu lamata mi ru:   
\q1
\v 17 Mbulu ki tapakur itundu mi matanda pasom zin tomtom,  
\q1 mbulu tau kwondo ipakamkaam,\x + \xo 6:17 \xt Mbo 101:5; Tut 16:5\x*  
\q1 mbulu ki namanda iteege siŋ pizin wal ta len uunu sa isaana som,   
\q1
\v 18 mbulu tau lelende iur pa ŋgar sananŋana,  
\q1 mbulu tau kumbundu ipawwai iti be takam mbulu sananŋana,   
\q1
\v 19 mbulu ki topombol sorok sua pakaamŋana ila zin bibip matan,  
\q1 mi mbulu tau tukuru toŋmatiziŋ kopon, mi takam ma ŋoŋi imbotmbot la mazwan.\x + \xo 6:19 \xt Tut 12:17, 14:5\x*   
\s1 Tuurnol pepe  
\q1
\v 20 O lutuŋ, motom iŋgalŋgal tutu ta boozomen ki tomom mi toto.  
\q1 Mi ŋgar ambaiŋana ta nom ikam pu na, zem pepe.   
\q1
\v 21 Po sua kizin ila ndomom, mi kiskis la ŋgar ku.  
\q1 Pa ina ko ipeŋgeeze mbulu ku, kembei aigau ta imbot la ketem na.\x + \xo 6:21 \xt Tut 1:9, 3:3\x*   
\q1
\v 22 Sua kizin irao ikam peeze pu, mi iuulu u be pa pai ku ma ambai men.  
\q1 Mi keeneŋana ku tomini ko ambai. Pa sua kizin ta imborro u.  
\q1 Mi sombe maŋga, na sua kizin ko ipeyei ŋgar ambaiŋana pu.   
\q1
\v 23 Tutu kizin ko iwe kembei ta kai pu be iyaara pu mi iso u pa zaala.  
\q1 Sua ta tikam pu na, ko iurur mat pu.  
\q1 Mi sua tutŋana ta tikam pu bekena tipazalu pa na, ina ko iwe zaala pu be ndeeŋe mbotŋana ambaiŋana.\x + \xo 6:23 \xt Mbo 19:8, 119:105; 2Pe 1:19\x*   
\q1
\v 24 Sua kizin ko iuulu u be mbotmbot molo pizin moori zaala lwoono kan.  
\q1 Kokena timbuulu kwon pu, to tikam lelem.\x + \xo 6:24 \xt Tut 2:16, 5:3, 7:5\x*   
\q1
\v 25 Ŋonoono, zin moori ta kembei na, ruŋgun ambaimbaiŋan. Tamen motom la pizin pepe.  
\q1 Mi sombe matan ikinmeete pu, na tikam lelem pepe.\x + \xo 6:25 \xt Mt 5:28-29\x*   
\q1
\v 26 Zin moori ta zaala lwoono kan na, kan kadon bibip som.  
\q1 Mi nu sombe la ki tomtom toro kusiini ma niomru kekeene, nako ka kadoono biibi kat. Pa nu ko meete ma la lem!   
\q1
\v 27 Lak, sombe tomtom sa iur namaana sala you, ko ikani som?   
\q1
\v 28 Mi sombe ipa se you keseene, ko kumbuunu ipokpok som?   
\q1
\v 29 Mi ina raraate men pa tomtom ta so ila ki tomooto toro kusiini na.  
\q1 Ni kola ire ka kadoono. Irao tileeli na som.\x + \xo 6:29 \xt Ibr 13:4\x*   
\q1
\v 30 Sombe tomtom sa peteli ma isaana kat, mi ikam kuumbu pa ka kini,  
\q1 nako tomtom tire kembei ambai ri. Paso lelen isaana pini.   
\q1
\v 31 Tamen sombe tindeeŋi, nako tiur sua pini be ikot koroŋ ta ni ikem na pa lamata mi ru.  
\q1 Ko ikot mi ila ila ma irao ruumu kini leleene ikolkol kat.   
\q1
\v 32 Mi tomtom ta so ila ki tomooto toro kusiini, na ni kankaanaŋana kat.  
\q1 Pa ina, ipasaana itunu.   
\q1
\v 33 Ko tipuni ma ruŋguunu isaana, mi ka miaŋ biibi kat.  
\q1 Mi ka miaŋ tana ko irao imap na som.   
\q1
\v 34 Pa re. Sombe nu la ki tomooto toro kusiini, nako kam tomooto tana ma mataana mburmbur mi keteene malmal biibi kat.  
\q1 Tana ni kola ipokot mbulu ku. Irao imuŋai u ri sa na som.   
\q1
\v 35 Sombe toombo sua pini be ŋgiimi sosor ku, na irao ileŋu na som.  
\q1 Sombe kam le koroŋ zaanaŋana sa, ina tomini, irao iurpe leleene na som.   
\c 7  
\s1 Tomooto bela tire zin pizin moori zaala lwoono kan  
\q1
\v 1 O lutuŋ, motom iŋgalŋgal sua tio ti,  
\q1 mi kiskis tutu tio ta boozomen ma imbol kat la ŋgar ku.   
\q1
\v 2 Motom iŋgalŋgal tutu tio mi toto. Naso mbotmbot ambai.  
\q1 Sua boozomen ta aŋkam pu na, kozo mboro kat, kembei ta mborro kat itum motom na.   
\q1
\v 3 Tana kiskis sua tio ta boozomen ma imbol la ŋgar ku totomen,  
\q1 kembei ta kukuugu imbotmbot la nomom totomen.   
\q1
\v 4 Ur kat lelem pa ŋgar ambaiŋana,  
\q1 kembei ta lelem pa lumri bizin mi toŋmatiziŋ ku.   
\q1
\v 5 Pa sombe kam lem ŋgar ambaiŋana, nako iuulu u be mbotmbot molo pizin moori zaala lwoono kan ta tiwadat zin tomooto na.  
\q1 Kokena kwon imbuulu u, to sua kizin ikam lelem.\x + \xo 7:5 \xt Tut 2:16, 6:24\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 6-7 Kembei ta lwoono ta. Nio aŋbotmbot ruumu leleene, mi aŋmender la miiri kwoono.  
\q1 Mi motoŋ la na, aŋre naŋgaŋ pakan timendernder ma timbotmbot. Ŋgar kizin ipet zen.  
\q1 Mi tomtom kizin ta, ni le ŋgar somŋana.   
\q1
\v 8 Iwwa pa zaala ma ila, mi igarau ruumu ki moori ta.   
\q1
\v 9 Ila ipet ruumu tana na, zoŋ isula mi zugut isu.   
\b  
\q1
\v 10 To moori tana izeebi pa mburu kembei ta moori zaala lwoono kan tiurur na, mi ipaŋuru i ma imar.  
\q1 Imar raama ŋgar turkeŋana ta.   
\q1
\v 11 Moori tana mbuleene izzu ruumu som.  
\q1 Gorgori iwwa lene mi ipaŋarairai kalŋaana.\x + \xo 7:11 \xt Tut 9:13\x*   
\q1
\v 12 Mi irru zin tomooto su nol muriini,  
\q1 mi ikewe su zaala lwoono be izaŋzaaŋa zin.   
\q1
\v 13 Tana ire naŋgaŋ tina, to loŋa men mi isou i, mi ikan kwoono.  
\q1 Mi ka miaŋ ri sa som. Iso kat pini ma iso:   
\q1
\v 14 “Ai, nio ti, muŋgu aŋbuk sua pa Anutu be aŋkam patoronŋana pini.  
\q1 Mi koozi aŋkam patoronŋana tana, mi buzur ka lwoono imbotmbot ruumu tio be takan.   
\q1
\v 15 Tana aŋyooto pa ruumu ma aŋmar be aŋru u tau.  
\q1 Mi iŋgi aŋdeeŋu kek.   
\q1
\v 16 Leŋ. Nio aŋurpe mbalia tio, mi aŋwar mburu ta kan mos ambaimbaiŋan na ise muriŋ.  
\q1 Mburu tana imbot taa Aikuptu mi imar.   
\q1
\v 17 Mi aŋliŋ koroŋ pakan ta kuzin ambaimbaiŋan na ise ma ambai leen!   
\q1
\v 18 Tana mar ma ituru tekeene.  
\q1 Ko menmeen ti mi takamam ma ila irao zoŋ ise!   
\q1
\v 19 Kam ŋgar pa kusiŋ pepe. Pa ni imbotmbot ruumu som. Iŋga ila pa lele molo.  
\q1 Ko loŋa imar na zeen.   
\q1
\v 20 Pa ila raama kautu kini ta bok pa pat.  
\q1 Tana ko imbotmbot ma puulu ilupi, tona imar.”   
\b  
\q1
\v 21 Moori tana ikam mbulu boozo pa naŋgaŋ tana bekena iyaaru i. Mi kwoono imbesmbeeze pini ma tau!  
\q1 Tabe ikam leleene, mi ni ito i ma ziru tila.   
\q1
\v 22 Naŋgaŋ tana inamnaama som. Ziru tila pataaŋa.  
\q1 Ni kembei makau ta iur niini mi tikami ma tila be tipuni ma imeete.  
\q1 Mi kembei buzur ta ikilaala kilis som mi kumbuunu isula.   
\q1
\v 23 Ni ikilaala som. Mbulu ta ikam na, ko ikami ma imeete.  
\q1 Kaimer peene lutuunu sa ko iŋgetŋgeete ise kuliini.  
\q1 Ni ko iwe kembei ŋge ta ila ma kilis ikami.\x + \xo 7:23 \xt Tut 5:4+\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 24 Tana lutuŋŋan, keleŋ la sua tio ti, mi motoyom iŋgalŋgal.   
\q1
\v 25 Kere yom pizin moori ta kembei: Kokena tikam leleyom ma kezem zaala ambaiŋana, mi koto zin pa zaala kizin.   
\q1
\v 26 Pa zin wal ta titop la kizin na, sorok som.  
\q1 Tikazas wal boozo kat ma timetmeete.   
\q1
\v 27 Zaala biibi ta isula pa naala na, kwoono imbot kat ta ndeete kizin uunu na.  
\q1 Tana zin wal ta so tito zaala kizin, nako tisula kizin wal meeteŋan.\x + \xo 7:27 \xt Tut 2:18, 9:18; Mt 7:13; 1Kor 6:9-10\x*   
\c 8  
\s1 Ŋgar ambaiŋana izzo pa itunu mi uraata ta ni ikamam na  
\q1
\v 1 Ŋgar ambaiŋana, ina kembei moori ambaiŋana ta imbotmbot, mi ipaŋarairai kalŋaana ma iboboobo iti tomtom be tala kini, bekena ipaute iti pa ŋgar iŋgoi ta ambai ma ilip.   
\q1
\v 2 Ni ikewe piti som. Imbotmbot sala lele mbukuunu ta igarau zaala biibi na,  
\q1 mi isu ma imendernder la zaala boogoŋan tomini.   
\q1
\v 3 Mi ilala pa zaala kwoono,  
\q1 mi ipaŋarairai kalŋaana ma izzo ta kembei:   
\b  
\q1
\v 4 “O niom iwal biibi ki toono, nio iŋgi aŋboboobo yom be kamar ma keleŋ sua tio ti.   
\q1
\v 5 Niom wal ta leyom ŋgar biibi som na, kamar tio. Naso aŋuulu yom be kakam kat ŋgar.  
\q1 Niom wal kankaanaŋoyom ta kozorzooro na, kamar tio bekena aŋuulu yom ma kikilaala ŋgar iŋgoi ta ambai ma ilip na.   
\q1
\v 6 Keleŋ sua tio ti. Pa nio leŋ ŋgar ambaimbaiŋan boozomen be aŋso yom pa.  
\q1 Sua ta iwedet pa kwoŋ na, indeŋdeeŋe men.\x + \xo 8:6 \xt Pil 4:8\x*   
\q1
\v 7 Sua sananŋana sa irao ipet pa kwoŋ na som. Som kat.  
\q1 Sua tio, ina ŋonoono men.   
\q1
\v 8 Sua boozomen ta iwedet pa kwoŋ na, sa ipaŋoobo som.  
\q1 Indeŋdeeŋe men.\x + \xo 8:8 \xt Mbo 119:160; Pil 2:15\x*   
\q1
\v 9 Zin wal ta ŋgar kizin ipet kek na, tikilaala kembei sua tio ta boozomen izal men.  
\q1 Zin wal ta len ŋgar na, tiute: Sua tio, ina ambai men.   
\q1
\v 10 Kakam ŋgar pa pat silba pepe. Kakan la sua tio pazalŋana. Pa ina ilip pa pat silba.  
\q1 Mi ŋgar ambaiŋana tabe aŋso yom pa i, ta kembena. Ilip pa gol ta ambaimbaiŋan kat. Tana kakam ma iwe leyom.\x + \xo 8:10 \xt Mbo 19:10; Tut 3:14, 16:16\x*   
\q1
\v 11 Pa ŋgar ambaiŋana, ina ilip pa pat milmilŋan ta kan kadon bibip i.  
\q1 Koroŋ boozomen ta leleyom pa i, sa irao iuulu yom kembei ŋgar ambaiŋana na som.”   
\b  
\q1
\v 12 Ŋgar ambaiŋana izzo ta kembei: “Nio aŋbotmbot raama ŋgar ta iurur ŋonoono.  
\q1 Pa aŋkam kat ŋgar kek. Tana aŋrao be aŋpaute yom pa so mbulu tabe kakam i.   
\q1
\v 13 Tomtom ta so imototo Yooba mi ileŋleŋ la kalŋaana, nako iurur koi pa mbulu sananŋana.  
\q1 Mi nio ta kembena. Mbulu ki pakurŋana mi repiiliŋana, ramaki mbulu sananŋan mi sua pakamkaamŋan ta boozomen na, leleŋ pa ri sa som kat.   
\q1
\v 14 Nio aŋrao be aŋso yom pa ŋgar ambaiŋana, mi aŋuulu uraata tiom ma iur ŋonoono.  
\q1 Pa leŋ ŋgar ambaiŋana mi mburoŋ biibi.\x + \xo 8:14 \xt Ro 16:27\x*   
\q1
\v 15 Nio aŋuluulu zin king mi wal peeze kan be tikam kat peeze,  
\q1 mibe tiur tutu ndeeŋeŋan men pizin tomtom.   
\q1
\v 16 Nio aŋuluulu zin bibip be timboro kat zin tomtom,  
\q1 mibe tiurpe pataŋana kizin ma indeeŋe men.   
\b  
\q1
\v 17 Zin wal ta so tiurur lelen pio, na nio aŋurur leleŋ pizin.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta so tikam kinkiini be tiru yo, nako tindeeŋe yo.\x + \xo 8:17 \xt Yo 14:21-23; Mt 7:7-11; Yems 1:5\x*   
\q1
\v 18 Sombe nio aŋbotmbot raama tomtom sa, na ni ko ikam le koroŋ ndabokbokŋan boozomen mi zaana iwe biibi.  
\q1 Ni ko iute zaala ndeeŋeŋana tabe irao kat pa le koroŋ.  
\q1 Mi koroŋ kini ko imbotmbot ambai ma molo.\x + \xo 8:18 \xt Tut 3:16\x*   
\q1
\v 19 Ŋonoono ambaimbaiŋan ta aŋpiyotyooto na, ilip pa gol ma silba ta iŋgeeze kat na.   
\q1
\v 20 Mi zaala ta aŋtoto, ina ndeeŋeŋana.  
\q1 Zin wal ta so titoto zaala tio, nako tirao be tiurpe pataŋana kizin tomtom ma indeeŋe men.   
\q1
\v 21 Zin wal ta so tiurur lelen pio, na aŋkamam len koroŋ boozomen.  
\q1 Tabe ruumu leleene kizin tau titiurkewe koroŋ kizin ambaimbaiŋan ilelala pa i na, bokbok.   
\s1 Ta muŋgu mi imar na, ŋgar ambaiŋana imbotmbot  
\q1
\v 22 Indeeŋe ta matapopo ten na, Yooba iur yo ma aŋpet muŋgu,  
\q1 mana imaŋga pa uraata kini be iur koroŋ ta boozomen.\x + \xo 8:22 \xt Mbo 104:24\x*   
\q1
\v 23 Muŋgu kat, indeeŋe toono ipet zen na, ni iur yo ma aŋpet.\x + \xo 8:23 \xt Yo 1:1, 17:5\x*   
\q1
\v 24-25 Mazwaana ta ni ipiyooto yo na, tai imbotmbot som.  
\q1 Mi yok lepenlepen ta yok irereere pa i ta kembena. Timbotmbot som.  
\q1 Mi abal ma dogo ta boozomen tomini, tipet zen.\x + \xo 8:24-25 \xt Mbo 90:2\x*   
\q1
\v 26-27 Indeeŋe ta Yooba iur toono, su, mi ululu zen na, nio aŋbotmbot raami.  
\q1 Mazwaana tana, ni iur saamba, mi iut ma imbot ndel pa yok ta imbot meleebe na.   
\q1
\v 28-29 Mi iur gubur tiene ma isala kor,  
\q1 mi iyaraama yok ta imbot meleebe na, mi iur mbut pa. Kokena izooro tutu kini mi ilol toono.  
\q1 Mi ŋgar kini iur pa lele tabe toono imbot pa i, mana iur toono ma ipet, mi ipombol uunu ma imbol.   
\q1
\v 30 Indeeŋe tana, nio aŋbotmbot zilŋaana uunu, mi aŋkamam peeze pa uraata ta boozomen tana. Pa nio nomoŋ mosŋoŋ.  
\q1 Aigule ta boozomen, nio aŋbotmbot su kereene uunu na, menmeen yo mi aŋzeŋzeeŋge.   
\q1
\v 31 Pa leleŋ ambai kat pa toono ramaki ka koroŋ ta boozomen,  
\q1 mi menmeen yo pizin tomtom tomini.\x + \xo 8:31 \xt Yo 1:1-4; Kol 1:15-20\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 32 Tana lutuŋŋan, kuur talŋoyom pio.  
\q1 Pa zin wal ta so matan iŋgalŋgal zaala tio mi titoto, nako lelen ambai kat mi kampeŋana ki Anutu imbotmbot se kizin.   
\q1
\v 33 Sua ta aŋkam piom na, keleŋtut pepe.  
\q1 Keleŋ la mi koto. Naso kakam leyom ŋgar ambaiŋana.   
\q1
\v 34 Zin wal tau timbotmbot ruumu tio kwoono pa aigule ta boozomen mi tinamnaama bekena aŋso zin pa ŋgar ambaiŋana, mi tileŋleŋ la sua tio na,  
\q1 zin ko lelen ambai kat mi kampeŋana ki Anutu imbotmbot se kizin.\x + \xo 8:34 \xt Mbo 119:1-2\x*   
\q1
\v 35 Pa tomtom ta so indeeŋe yo, nako ikam mbotŋana ambaiŋana,  
\q1 mi Yooba leleene pini.\x + \xo 8:35 \xt Tut 3:16; 1Yo 5:11\x*   
\q1
\v 36 Tamen tomtom ta so iru yo ma som, ina ni imbel itunu.  
\q1 Mi wal boozomen ta lelen pio som mi tiurur koi pio, na zin lelen be timeete.   
\c 9  
\s1 Sua tooroŋana pa bobi ki ŋgar ambaiŋana  
\q1
\v 1 Ŋgar ambaiŋana, ni ipo le ruumu kek,  
\q1 mi isap nasil lamata mi ru ta mosŋan na, mi ipamender zin ma tiliu ruumu kini bekena ipeŋgeeze ruumu.\x + \xo 9:1 \xt Ep 2:20-22\x*   
\q1
\v 2 Mi iurpe buzur mi yok baen ambaiŋana,  
\q1 mi iur se mbalia, mi iparaŋraŋ bekena tomtom tikan mi tiwin.   
\q1
\v 3 Mi iŋgo zin mbesooŋo moori kini ma tisala lele mbukuunu ta igarau kar na,  
\q1 bekena tiboboobo la pizin tomtom be timar pa kini kanŋana.\x + \xo 9:3 \xt Mt 22:1-11\x*   
\q1
\v 4 Mi zin wal ta ŋgar kizin ipet zen na, ni izzo pizin ta kembei:  
\q1 “Ai, niom wal ta leyom ŋgar biibi som na, niom ta boozomen kamar ruumu tio.   
\q1
\v 5 Pa kini mi yok baen, ta aŋurpe ma imap kek.  
\q1 Kamar ma kakan mi kiwin.\x + \xo 9:5 \xt Yo 6:27, 7:37-38\x*   
\q1
\v 6 Kezem mbulu tiom kankaanaŋana ma imborene. Naso kombot ambai.  
\q1 Koto zaala ki ŋgar ambaiŋana.”   
\b  
\q1
\v 7 Zin wal ta tipakurkur zitun mi tirepilpiili ŋgar ambaiŋana na, sombe tomtom sa itoombo be ipazal zin, nako tipiri sua sananŋana pini.  
\q1 Mi sombe tayaamba zin wal sananŋan, nako tipekel sua sananŋana kat piti ma kanda miaŋ!\x + \xo 9:7 \xt Tut 23:9; Mt 7:6; 1Pe 4:4\x*   
\q1
\v 8 Tana zin wal ta tipakurkur zitun mi tirepilpiili ŋgar ambaiŋana na, toombo be pazal zin pepe. Kokena tiur koi pu.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta le ŋgar ambaiŋana, to pazali. Pa ni ko leleene ambai pa sua ku pazalŋana mi iur leleene pu.\x + \xo 9:8 \xt Mbo 141:5; Tut 10:8, 28:23\x*   
\q1
\v 9 Zin wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na, sombe so zin pa sua ambaiŋana, nako tikam len ŋgar pakan ma isala ki.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ndeeŋeŋana ta kembena. Sombe paute i, nako iseeŋge ŋgar kini.\x + \xo 9:9 \xt Tut 18:15; Mt 13:12\x*   
\q1
\v 10 Mbulu tau tomototo Yooba mi teleŋleŋ la kalŋaana, ina ŋgar ambaiŋana uunu ŋonoono.  
\q1 Pa sombe tuute kat Anutu ta potomŋana i, inako tarao be tikilaala kat ŋgar iŋgoi ta ambai ma ilip.\x + \xo 9:10 \xt Mbo 111:10; Tut 2:4-5\x*   
\q1
\v 11 Ŋgar ambaiŋana ko iseeŋge swom ma molo.  
\q1 Ko ikam ma kom ndaama boozo, mana meete.\x + \xo 9:11 \xt Tut 3:16\x*   
\q1
\v 12 Tana nu sombe to ŋgar ambaiŋana, nako iuulu u ma biibi.  
\q1 Mi sombe pakurkur itum mi zorzooro, na kozo re u. Pa mbulu ku tana ko ipasaanu.   
\s1 Sua tooroŋana pa bobi ki ŋgar kankaanaŋana  
\q1
\v 13 Ŋgar kankaanaŋana, ina kembei moori ta le ŋgar somŋana, mi irao iyaraama itunu som, mi kalŋaana izalla sorok.   
\q1
\v 14 Ikewe piti som. Imbutultul su ruumu kini kwoono bekena iboboobo la pizin tomtom be tila kini.  
\q1 Mi ilala mbalia kini ta imbotmbot sala lele mbukuunu ta igarau kar na tomini be iboboobo zin tomtom.   
\q1
\v 15 Zin wal ta matan iŋgalŋgal zaala ambaiŋana be titoto na, ni iboboobo la pizin bekena iyaaru zin ma tizem zaala ambaiŋana.   
\q1
\v 16 Mi zin wal ta ŋgar kizin ipet zen na, ni izzo pizin ta kembei:  
\q1 “Ai, niom wal ta leyom ŋgar biibi som na, niom ta boozomen kamar ruumu tio.   
\q1
\v 17 Pa yok ta so takam kuumbu pa i, ina inamut kat.  
\q1 Mi kini ta so tekewe mi takanan, ina ikamam ŋgurende.”\x + \xo 9:17 \xt Tut 20:17\x*   
\q1
\v 18 Tamen zin wal ta tileŋ la kalŋaana ma tila kini na, tikilaala som.  
\q1 Zin wal ta so tiwe leembe kini, na kaimer ko timetmeete ma tisula len naala.   
\c 10  
\s1 Sua tutŋana ki King Salumo  
\q1
\v 1 Iŋgi sua tutŋana mi sua tooroŋan pakan ki King Salumo.  
\b  
\q1 Naŋgaŋ sa, sombe le ŋgar ambaiŋana, nako ikam ma tamaana leleene ambai.  
\q1 Mi zin naŋgaŋ kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro, nako tikam ma nan bizin lelen ipata.\x + \xo 10:1 \xt Tut 15:20, 17:21,25, 29:3\x*   
\q1
\v 2 Iti irao takam lende koroŋ boozomen pa zaala sananŋana. Tamen koroŋ tana ko irao iuulu kat iti na som.  
\q1 Mi mbulu ndeeŋeŋana na, itatkewe iti pa meeteŋana.\x + \xo 10:2 \xt Tut 11:4\x*   
\q1
\v 3 Wal ndeeŋeŋan na, Yooba irao izem zin ma tikan peteele na som.  
\q1 Mi koroŋ ta wal sananŋan lelen pa i na, ni ipiŋgisŋgis pizin.\x + \xo 10:3 \xt Mbo 34:9-10, 37:19,25\x*   
\q1
\v 4 Sombe namanda ikamam kat uraata som, nako tombot ŋoobo.  
\q1 Mi sombe namanda ikamam kat uraata, nako lende koroŋ boozo.\x + \xo 10:4 \xt Tut 12:24,27, 13:4, 19:15\x*   
\q1
\v 5 Sombe mazwaana ki mai ipet, mi lutundu bizin tikam uraata ma tiyo kanda kini, ina iswe kembei zin len ŋgar ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Mi sombe tikenne mi timbombooren, ina tipamiaŋ ti.\x + \xo 10:5 \xt Tut 6:8-11\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 6 Wal ndeeŋeŋan na, kampeŋana matakiŋa imbotmbot se kizin.  
\q1 Mi wal sananŋan na, tizzwe malmal tabe tikam i som. Titurkewe.   
\q1
\v 7 Sombe wal ndeeŋeŋan timeete, na tomtom matan lala pa mbulu kizin ambaiŋana mi tipakurkur Anutu pa.  
\q1 Mi wal sananŋan na, zan ko isaana ma isaana kat.\x + \xo 10:7 \xt Mbo 37:9,22,28,38\x*   
\q1
\v 8 Wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na, sombe tutut zin, nako tileŋ la kalŋanda.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro mi kwon perper sorok na, zin ko tisaana ma tila len.\x + \xo 10:8 \xt Tut 9:8-9\x*   
\q1
\v 9 Tomtom ta so ipa pai kini ma ambai men, na kosasa ko irao be ipasaana kati na som.  
\q1 Tamen zin wal ta tipaŋobŋoobo pa zaala ambaiŋana na, kaimer mbulu kizin ta tikamam ki keŋana na, ko imbot kat mat mi tomtom tiute.\x + \xo 10:9 \xt Mbo 23:4; Lu 8:17; 1Tim 5:24-25\x*   
\q1
\v 10 Zin wal ta matan iparkinmeete pizin na, kaimer ko tikam mbulu sa mi tikam pataŋana piti.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro mi kwon perper sorok na, zin ko tisaana ma tila len.   
\q1
\v 11 Sua kizin wal ndeeŋeŋan, ina kembei yok lepeene. Pa iuluulu zin tomtom be timbot ambai.  
\q1 Mi zin wal sananŋan na, tizzwe malmal tabe tikam i som. Titurkewe.\x + \xo 10:11 \xt Mbo 37:30\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 12 Mbulu ki tuurur koi, ina ikamam ma ŋoŋi imbotmbot la mazwanda.  
\q1 Mi sombe tuurur lelende pizin tomtom, nako matanda mbiriizikaala sanaana kizin, mi takam ŋgar pa mini som.\x + \xo 10:12 \xt Tut 17:9; 1Kor 13:4-7; 1Pe 4:8; Yems 5:20\x*   
\q1
\v 13 Zin wal tau tikilaala ŋgar iŋgoi ta ambai ma ilip na, kwon ipiyotyooto ŋgar ambaiŋana men.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta len ŋgar somŋan na, teene ko ikan zin!\x + \xo 10:13 \xt Tut 19:29\x*   
\q1
\v 14 Zin wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na, gorgori tirru ŋgar pakan be isala ki.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, molo som to sua sananŋana ta iwedet pa kwon na, ko ipasaana zin.   
\q1
\v 15 Zin wal ta len koroŋ boozo na, tipase pa pat ma koroŋ kizin be iporoukaala zin pa pataŋana.  
\q1 Mi zin wal sorrokŋan ta len koroŋ som mi timbot ŋoobo na, pataŋana kizin tana ko ipun zin ma tisaana kat.   
\q1
\v 16 Kadoono ta wal ndeeŋeŋan tikamam pa uraata kizin, ina iuluulu zin be tikam mbotŋana ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Mi kadoono ta wal sananŋan tikamam pa uraata kizin, ina tiwirri sorok pa koroŋ sananŋan men.   
\q1
\v 17 Tomtom ta so ileŋleŋ la sua pazalŋana, na imbotmbot la zaala ki mbotŋana ambaiŋana kek.  
\q1 Mi zin wal tau tileŋtut sua pazalŋana, nako tiyaaru zin tomtom pakan ma tipaŋoobo pa zaala ambaiŋana.\x + \xo 10:17 \xt Tut 13:1,18\x*   
\q1
\v 18 Tomtom ta so iurur koi pu mi ikiskis la leleene, nako kwoono ipakamkaam.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ileŋ sua ŋgalŋana sa mi ila ma izzo pizin wal pakan, na ni tomtom kankaanaŋana.   
\b  
\q1
\v 19 Sombe nu kwom suaŋom, na re u. Pa nu kola kam sanaana. Irao kam som na som.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so imborro kat kwoono, na ni tomtom ŋgarŋana.\x + \xo 10:19 \xt Mt 12:36,37; Yems 1:19, 3:2-10\x*   
\q1
\v 20 Sua ta iwedet pa wal ndeeŋeŋan kwon, ina kembei pat silba ta tomtom lelen pa ilip.  
\q1 Tamen ŋgar ta imbotmbot la wal sananŋan lelen, ina ŋono somŋana.   
\q1
\v 21 Sua ta iwedet pa wal ndeeŋeŋan kwon, ina iuluulu tomtom boozomen be timbot ambai.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, tikam kat ŋgar som. Tana kaimer ko timetmeete ma tila len.   
\q1
\v 22 Kampeŋana ki Yooba, ta ikamam lende koroŋ boozomen.  
\q1 Mi koroŋ ta so ni ikam piti, nako ka pataŋana sa som.\x + \xo 10:22 \xt Mbo 128:2\x*   
\q1
\v 23 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, sombe lelen iurur pa mbulu sananŋana sa, to ikam zin ma lelen ambai mi menmeen zin.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ŋgar kini ipet kek, na ŋgar ambaiŋana ta ikami ma leleene ambai.\x + \xo 10:23 \xt Tut 15:21\x*   
\q1
\v 24 Koroŋ ta wal sananŋan timototo, ta ko ipet pizin.  
\q1 Mi koroŋ ta wal ndeeŋeŋan lelen pa na, Yooba ko ikam pizin.\x + \xo 10:24 \xt Mbo 37:4; Mt 5:6; 1Yo 5:14-15\x*   
\q1
\v 25 Pataŋana biibi ko ipambiriizi zin wal sananŋan.  
\q1 Tamen wal ndeeŋeŋan ko timendernder mbolŋana ma alok.\x + \xo 10:25 \xt Mbo 37:35-36; Mt 7:24-27; 2Tim 2:19\x*   
\q1
\v 26 Zin wal ta so tiŋgo tomtom maolŋana ma ila be ikam uraata, nako lelen ambai som.  
\q1 Ko kembei koroŋ ta ikam ma zoŋon imenel, mi you ka koi ila matan.   
\q1
\v 27 Sombe tomototo Yooba mi teleŋleŋ la kalŋaana, nako iseeŋge swondo ma molo.  
\q1 Tamen ni iyembutmbut wal sananŋan swon bekena timeete ma tila len karau men.\x + \xo 10:27 \xt Tut 3:16+; Mbo 55:23\x*   
\q1
\v 28 Koroŋ ambaimbaiŋan ta wal ndeeŋeŋan tiurur matan pa na, zin kola tire mi menmeen zin pa.  
\q1 Mi wal sananŋan na som. Koroŋ ta tiurur matan pa na, zin ko tirao be tire na som.\x + \xo 10:28 \xt Mbo 112:10; Tut 11:7\x*   
\q1
\v 29 Yooba, ni iwe kembei siiri mbolŋana pizin wal ndeeŋeŋan be tike lela.  
\q1 Tamen ipasansaana zin wal sananŋan.   
\q1
\v 30 Wal ndeeŋeŋan, zin kembei ke mbolŋana ta irao be imuzu na som.  
\q1 Mi wal sananŋan na, zin ko tirao be timbot pa toono ta Yooba ikam pa wal kini na som. Ni ko iziiri zin ma tila len.\x + \xo 10:30 \xt Mbo 37:28+, 112:6, 125:1; Tut 2:22, 14:11\x*   
\q1
\v 31 Wal ndeeŋeŋan na, kwon ipiyotyooto ŋgar ambaiŋana men.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta kwon ipiyotyooto sua sananŋana na, Yooba ko ipasaana zin ma tila len bekena ipumun kwon.\x + \xo 10:31 \xt Mbo 37:30, 52:3-5\x*   
\q1
\v 32 Wal ndeeŋeŋan matan iŋgalŋgal be tiso sua ambaiŋana men.  
\q1 Mi wal sananŋan na, sua soroksorok men ta iwedet pa kwon.   
\c 11  
\q1
\v 1 Mbulu ki tapakaam zin tomtom mi tawatke lende koroŋ kizin na, Yooba leleene pa ri sa som.  
\q1 Tana iti sombe takam ŋgomo pa koroŋ sa, na tere be tuur kadoono ma irao kat pa ka kin. Pa Yooba leleene pa mbulu ta kembei. Kokena tasala mete.\x + \xo 11:1 \xt Tut 20:10\x*   
\q1
\v 2 Tomtom ta so ipakurkuri ma iso ni irao, na kaimer ko ka miaŋ.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ikototo itunu, nako ikam le ŋgar ambaiŋana.\x + \xo 11:2 \xt Tut 16:18, 18:12\x*   
\q1
\v 3 Zin wal ta lelen ŋgeezeŋan na, lelen be tipa pai kizin ma ambai men. Mi ŋgar tana ta ikamam peeze pizin.  
\q1 Tamen zin wal ta so tisu mini mi tiur koi pa zitun wal kizin na, mbulu kizin pakaamŋana ko ipasaana zin.   
\q1
\v 4 Anutu isombe iswe kete malmalŋana kini ma ipet kat mat, na koroŋ boozomen ta wal sananŋan tindoundou na, ko irao iuulu zin ri sa som.  
\q1 Tamen mbulu ndeeŋeŋana, ina ikamkewe iti pa meeteŋana.\x + \xo 11:4 \xt Tut 10:2\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 5 Zin wal ta len uunu sa isaana som na, mbulu kizin ndeeŋeŋana ta iurpewe zaala pizin.  
\q1 Mi zin wal sananŋan na, mbulu kizin sananŋana ta ipasansaana zin.   
\q1
\v 6 Zin wal ta lelen ŋgeezeŋan na, mbulu kizin ndeeŋeŋana itatkewe zin pa pataŋana kizin.  
\q1 Tamen zin wal pakamkaamŋan ta so tisu mini mi tiur koi pa zitun wal kizin na, koroŋ ta zin lelen pa i ko iwe kembei kilis pizin mi ikeene zin.\x + \xo 11:6 \xt Tut 5:22, 12:13, 13:6\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 7 Wal sananŋan tipase pa zitun mburan, mi tiso ko tikam len koroŋ boozo.  
\q1 Tamen sombe timeete, na tisula len naala raama ŋgar kizin tana. Tabe koroŋ ta tiurur matan pa i, na tire ka ŋonoono som.\x + \xo 11:7 \xt Tut 10:28\x*   
\q1
\v 8 Pataŋana tabe ikam zin wal ndeeŋeŋan na, Anutu ipiŋgisŋgis  
\q1 ma ila izze kizin wal sananŋan.   
\b  
\q1
\v 9 Tomtom ta so ikamam ŋgar pa Anutu som, na kwoono ko ipasansaana waene bizin.  
\q1 Mi wal ndeeŋeŋan na, ŋgar kizin izzo zin pa zaala tabe tiko pa pataŋana kizin.   
\q1
\v 10 Sombe wal ndeeŋeŋan timbot ambai, na kar kan ko menmeen zin.  
\q1 Mi sombe zin wal sananŋan tisaana ma tila len, ina tomini ikam zin tomtom ma lelen ambai.   
\q1
\v 11 Kampeŋana ta imbotmbot se kizin wal ŋgeezeŋan na, ikamam ma kar niini ise.  
\q1 Mi sua ta iwedet pa wal sananŋan kwon, ta ipasansaana kar.   
\q1
\v 12 Zin wal ta len ŋgar somŋan na, kwon pasomsom waen bizin pakan.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ikam kat ŋgar, nako imborro kat kwoono.   
\q1
\v 13 Zin wal ta tininin kao na, tilala ma tizzwe sua turkeŋana kizin tomtom.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ŋonoono na, ni irao iswe sua turkeŋana ki waene bizin pakan na som. Tana iti irao tendemeeri.\x + \xo 11:13 \xt Tut 20:19, 25:9\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 14 Sombe zin bibip ki lele sa tikamam kat peeze som, nako lele tana isaana.  
\q1 Mi sombe wal boozomen tiuluulu zin bibip tana pa ŋgar, nako lele tana imbot ambai.\x + \xo 11:14 \xt Tut 15:22, 20:18\x*   
\q1
\v 15 Tomtom ta so imbuk sua be imender pa tomtom toro mi ikot mbun kini, nako indeeŋe pataŋana.  
\q1 Tana nu sombe lelem be mbot ambai, na mbuk sua ta kembei pepe!\x + \xo 11:15 \xt Tut 6:1+, 17:18, 20:16\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 16 Moori sa, sombe mbulu kini irao pa tomtom lelen, nako ikam zaana biibi.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tikamam zaaba pizin tomtom na, tikamam len pat men. Koroŋ toro sa som.   
\q1
\v 17 Tomtom ta so iurur leleene pa wal kini mi ikampewe zin, na iuluulu itunu.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so imuŋaiŋai zin tomtom som, ina ni ipasansaana itunu.\x + \xo 11:17 \xt Mt 5:7\x*   
\q1
\v 18 Kadoono ta wal sananŋan tikamam pa uraata kizin, ina ŋono somŋana.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so iwaswaaza mbulu ndeeŋeŋana, na kadoono tabe ikam i, ina koroŋ ŋonoono.\x + \xo 11:18 \xt Tut 22:8-9; Ga 6:8-9; Yems 3:18\x*   
\q1
\v 19 Tomtom ta so ikam kinkiini be ito mbulu ndeeŋeŋana, nako ikam mbotŋana ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tirru zaala pa mbulu sananŋana, nako timetmeete ma tila len.   
\b  
\q1
\v 20 Zin wal ta tikamam ŋgar sananŋana na, Yooba leleene pizin ri sa som kat.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tipa pai kizin ma ambai men na, ni leleene pizin ilip.\x + \xo 11:20 \xt Mbo 15:1-2, 101:4, 119:1; Tut 12:22\x*   
\q1
\v 21 Lelem iwe ru pepe. Wal sananŋan na, Anutu irao ileele zin na som. Zin kola tire kadoono pa mbulu kizin.  
\q1 Mi wal ndeeŋeŋan ziŋan popoŋan kizin na, zin len uunu sa isaana som. Tana pataŋana sa ko irao ikam zin na som.   
\b  
\q1
\v 22 Moori ta so ruŋguunu ambai, mi tamen ipizil ndemeene pa mbulu ambaiŋana,  
\q1 ina kembei aigau ta izuk koroŋ buzaanaŋana.   
\q1
\v 23 Wal ndeeŋeŋan lelen pa koroŋ ambaimbaiŋan men. Tana kaimer zin ko tindeeŋe kampeŋana ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Mi wal sananŋan na, tiurur matan pa koroŋ sananŋan men. Tana kaimer Anutu kete malmalŋana kini ko ikam kat zin.\x + \xo 11:23 \xt Ro 2:8-9\x*   
\s1 Matanda kon pepe  
\q1
\v 24 Tomtom ta, ni mata merereŋana mi irairai koroŋ boozo pizin tomtom. Tamen koroŋ ta imilmiili pini na, boozo ma ilip.  
\q1 Mi tomtom toro, ni mata konŋana, mi ikiskis koroŋ kini ta boozomen. Tamen molo som na, koroŋ kini tana imbiriizi, mi isu ma imbot ŋoobo.\x + \xo 11:24 \xt Mbo 112:9; Tut 22:9; 2Kor 9:6-9\x*   
\q1
\v 25 Tomtom rairaiŋana ko ikam mboti ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Pa tomtom ta so ise yok mi ikam pizin wal pakan, na itunu ko iwin kana tomini.\x + \xo 11:25 \xt Lu 6:38\x*   
\q1
\v 26 Tomtom ta so iruutu kini kini pa mazwaana ki peteele, nako tipiri sua sananŋana pini.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so iyok pizin tomtom be tiŋgiimi kini kini na, kampeŋana tabe imbotmbot se kini i ko ikam ma zaana iwe biibi.\x + \xo 11:26 \xt Un 41:53-57\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 27 Zin wal ta tikamam kinkiini pa koroŋ ambaimbaiŋan, nako tindeeŋe kampeŋana biibi.  
\q1 Mi sombe ŋgar kiti ilala pa koroŋ sananŋan men, na mbulu sananŋana ko ipet piti.\x + \xo 11:27 \xt Mbo 7:15-16; Mt 7:12\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 28 Tomtom ta le koroŋ boozo mi ipase pa, na mbotŋana kini ko isaana.  
\q1 Mi wal ndeeŋeŋan na, zin kembei ke ka saluundu ta indom ma ise i.\x + \xo 11:28 \xt Mbo 1:3, 49:6-8; Mk 10:25; 1Tim 6:17\x*   
\q1
\v 29 Tomtom ta so ikamam pataŋana pa wal kini, nako irao ikam le matamur sa na som.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, zin ko tiwe mbesooŋo sorok pizin wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na.   
\q1
\v 30 Wal ndeeŋeŋan tiuluulu zin tomtom be timbot ambai, kembei ke ta ipiyotyooto ŋonoono ambaimbaiŋan.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tikamam zaaba pizin tomtom na, tipunun zin tomtom ma timetmeete.   
\q1
\v 31 Iti tuute: Indeeŋe ta wal ndeeŋeŋan timbotmbot men su toono na, tikamam len kadoono ambaiŋana pa mbulu kizin.  
\q1 Kenako toso parei pizin wal sananŋan mi zin wal ta tikamam ŋgar pa Anutu som na? Zin tomini ko tire kat kadoono pa mbulu kizin.\x + \xo 11:31 \xt Mbo 11:5-7, 73:17-19; 1Pe 4:17-18\x*   
\c 12  
\q1
\v 1 Iti sombe lelende be tomtom tipazal ti, ina iswe kembei lelende pa ŋgar ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so leleene iŋgis pa sua pazalŋana, na ni italli kembei ta wok!\x + \xo 12:1 \xt Tut 13:1,18, 15:5\x*   
\q1
\v 2 Tomtom ambaiŋana na, Yooba leleene pini mi ikampewe i.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tirru zaala be tikam mbulu sananŋana na, Yooba iurur kadoono pizin.   
\q1
\v 3 Tomtom sa irao imbol se mbulu sananŋana na som.  
\q1 Mi wal ndeeŋeŋan na, zin kembei ke ta uraana isula kat toono. Irao timuzu na som.\x + \xo 12:3 \xt Tut 10:25,30\x*   
\q1
\v 4 Moori ta so ikamam kat uraata ma mbulu, na iwe kembei mogar pa kusiini. Pa ikamam ma kusiini niini izze.  
\q1 Mi moori ta so mbulu kini ipamiaŋ kusiini, ina ni kembei motmooto ta itoutou kusiini tiroono.\x + \xo 12:4 \xt Tut 14:1, 31:10+\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 5 Wal ndeeŋeŋan na, lelen iurur pa koroŋ ambaimbaiŋan men.  
\q1 Mi wal sananŋan na, sombe tikamam peeze piti, nako tipasaana iti. Tana irao tendemeere ŋgar kizin na som.   
\q1
\v 6 Sua kizin wal sananŋan iwe kembei kilis be ikeene zin tomtom mi ipasaana zin.  
\q1 Mi wal ndeeŋeŋan na, sua kizin itatkewe zin pa pataŋana kizin.   
\q1
\v 7 Wal sananŋan, sombe koroŋ sa ipasaana zin, nako irao timaŋga mini na som.  
\q1 Mi wal ndeeŋeŋan ziŋan wal kizin na, zin ko timender mbolŋana ma timbotmbot.\x + \xo 12:7 \xt Tut 14:11\x*   
\q1
\v 8 Tomtom ta so ikamam kat ŋgar mi uraata kini ilonloondo ambai men, nako tipakuri.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tikamam ŋgar sananŋana na, tomtom tirepilpiili zin.   
\b  
\q1
\v 9 Wal sorrokŋan ru, ta len pat riŋa be iuulu zin. Ta na, ikam ŋgar pa mboti kini, tana iŋgiimi le mbesooŋo be imbeeze pini.  
\q1 Mi toro na, iwirri sorok pat kini bekena ikam tomtom lelen mi tipakuri. Tabe kaimer isu ma imbot ŋoobo.  
\q1 Asiŋ ilip?   
\q1
\v 10 Tomtom ndeeŋeŋana, ni leleene izanzaana pizin mbili kini mi imbesmbeeze pizin.  
\q1 Mi wal sananŋan na, tiute mbulu ki muŋaiŋana ri sa som. Tanata tiseseeze tomtom matan.   
\q1
\v 11 Tomtom ta so ikamam kat uraata pa mokleene kini, nako ka kini boozo.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta gorgori tirru zaala pa koroŋ ta ŋonon somŋan i, na zin len ŋgar sa som.\x + \xo 12:11 \xt Tut 28:19\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 12 Wal sananŋan sombe tiur kilis kizin sananŋana sa be tikam zin tomtom, ina ikam zin ma lelen ambai kat.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ndeeŋeŋana, ni kembei ke ta uraana isula kat toono mi indom ma iwe biibi.   
\q1
\v 13 Sua ta wal sananŋan tizorzooro pa i, ko iwe kembei ta kilis pizin.  
\q1 Mi wal ndeeŋeŋan na, zin len zaala be tiko pa pataŋana kizin.\x + \xo 12:13 \xt Mbo 7:15+, 9:17; 2Pe 2:9\x*   
\q1
\v 14 Sombe sua ambaiŋana men iwedet pa kwondo, inako ikam ti ma tombot ambai.  
\q1 Mi sombe namanda ikamam kat uraata, inako tere lende kadoono ambaiŋana.   
\q1
\v 15 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, lelen be tileŋ la tomtom toro kalŋaana som. Pa tindemeere sorok ma tiso titoto kat zaala ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta le ŋgar ambaiŋana na, ni ileŋleŋ la sua tutŋana ta tomtom tikamam pini na.   
\b  
\q1
\v 16 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, sombe wal pakan tikam mbulu sa pizin, na karau men mi keten malmal.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta le ŋgar na, sombe wal pakan tipiri sua sananŋana pini, na irao niini puliizi pa na som.   
\q1
\v 17 Zin wal ta titoto mbulu ŋonoono men, sombe tipombol tomtom toro sua kini, na irao tendemeere sua kizin. Pa ina sua ŋonoono.  
\q1 Mi sombe wal pakamkaamŋan tipombol tomtom toro sua kini, na irao tendemeere sua kizin na som. Pa ina sua pakaamŋana.   
\q1
\v 18 Sua ta so takam ŋgar pa som mi tipiri sorok, ina irao ipasaana tomtom lelen ma kembei ta izi iŋgal zin.  
\q1 Mi sua ta iwedet pa wal ŋgarŋan kwon, ina iurpewe tomtom lelen.   
\q1
\v 19 Zin wal ta kwon ipiyotyooto sua ŋonoono men, inako timbotmbot ma alok.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta kwon ipiyotyooto sua pakaamŋana, inako timbot rimen mi timap.   
\q1
\v 20 Zin wal ta lelen iurur be tikam mbulu sananŋana na, ŋgar kizin bok pa pakaamŋana.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tirru zaala be tilup zin tomtom mibe tikam zin ma timbot ambai, inako lelen ambai kat.\x + \xo 12:20 \xt Mt 5:9; Ro 14:18-19\x*   
\q1
\v 21 Tomtom ndeeŋeŋana na, koroŋ sa irao ipasaana kati na som.  
\q1 Mi wal sananŋan na, pataŋana ilolol zin.\x + \xo 12:21 \xt Mbo 91:10-12\x*   
\q1
\v 22 Zin wal ta kwon ipiyotyooto sua pakaamŋana na, Yooba leleene pizin ri sa som kat.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tizzo sua ŋonoono men mi titoto sua kizin mbukŋana na, ni leleene pizin ilip.\x + \xo 12:22 \xt Tut 6:16+, 11:20\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 23 Wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na, sombe lelen iurur pa ŋgar sa, na irao tiso sorok pizin tomtom na som. Pa ŋgar kizin tana ko iur ŋonoono kek?  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, keten pitpit mi loŋa tizzwe ŋgar kizin talliŋana pizin tomtom.\x + \xo 12:23 \xt Tut 10:14, 13:16\x*   
\q1
\v 24 Tomtom ki uraata, nako iwe biibi mi ikam peeze.  
\q1 Mi tomtom maolŋana, nako isu ma iwe mbesooŋo sorok.\x + \xo 12:24 \xt Tut 10:4, 13:4, 19:15\x*   
\q1
\v 25 Sombe lelende ipata kat, ina ipun ti ma mburanda imap.  
\q1 Mi sombe tomtom tikam sua ambaiŋana piti, nako ikam ma lelende ambai mini.\x + \xo 12:25 \xt Mbo 94:19\x*   
\q1
\v 26 Tomtom ndeeŋeŋana, ni itiiri kat zin tomtom muŋgu, mana ikam zin ma tiwe toroono bizin.  
\q1 Mi mbulu ta wal sananŋan titoto, ina iyaryaaru zin be tizem zaala ambaiŋana.\x + \xo 12:26 \xt Tut 18:24\x*   
\q1
\v 27 Wal maolŋan na, tirao be tiru kan buzur sa som.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ki uraata, nako le koroŋ boozo. Tabe ikami ma leleene ambai.   
\q1
\v 28 Zaala ndeeŋeŋana, ina zaala ki mbotŋana ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Sombe tototo zaala tana, na irao temeete ma tala lende na som.   
\c 13  
\q1
\v 1 Pikin ta le ŋgar ambaiŋana, nako ileŋ la sua tutŋana ki tamaana.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tipakurkur zitun mi tirepilpiili ŋgar ambaiŋana na, sombe tayaamba zin, na irao tileŋ la kalŋanda na som.   
\q1
\v 2 Sombe sua ambaiŋana men iwedet pa kwondo, ina irao iwe zaala piti be takam lende koroŋ ambaimbaiŋan.  
\q1 Mi zin wal pakamkaamŋan tau tisu mini mi tiur koi pa zitun wal kizin na, lelen ilip be tikam zaaba pizin tomtom.   
\q1
\v 3 Tomtom ta so mataana iŋgalŋgal itunu mi imborro kat kwoono, nako imbot ambai.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ikam kat ŋgar som mi iwirri sorok sua, ina ni ipasaana itunu.\x + \xo 13:3 \xt Mbo 12:2, 34:13; Tut 21:23\x*   
\q1
\v 4 Tomtom beleegeŋana, ni leleene pa koroŋ boozo. Mi irao ikam na som.  
\q1 Mi wal uraataŋan na, koroŋ boozomen ta lelen pa i, nako tikam ma tirao pa kat.\x + \xo 13:4 \xt Tut 10:4, 12:24,27, 19:15, 21:25\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 5 Tomtom ndeeŋeŋana, ni iurur koi pa mbulu pakaamŋana.  
\q1 Mi wal sananŋan na, mbulu buzaanaŋana mi mbulu pamiaŋŋana ta igabgaaba zin ma ziŋan tiwwa.   
\q1
\v 6 Tomtom ta ikamam kat mbulu na, mbulu kini ndeeŋeŋana ko iporoukalkaali ma imbotmbot ambai.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta mbulu kizin irao som na, mbulu kizin sananŋana ko ipasaana zin ma tisaana kat.   
\b  
\q1
\v 7 Tomtom ta, iti tere i na, toso ni le koroŋŋana. Mi som. Ni le koroŋ sa som.  
\q1 Mi tomtom toro, tere i na, toso ni sorokŋana. Mi som. Ni le koroŋ boozo.\x + \xo 13:7 \xt Tur 3:17; 2Kor 6:10\x*   
\q1
\v 8 Zin mbio uunu, sombe kan koi sa ipamoto zin mi iboobo pa le pat, na tirao be tiŋgiimi i, mi ni izem zin ma timbot.  
\q1 Mi wal sorrokŋan na, pataŋana ta kembei iwedet pizin som. Pa tomtom tiute: Zin len koroŋ sa som.   
\q1
\v 9 Wal ndeeŋeŋan tikamam mbotŋana ambaiŋana mi tiurur mat pizin tomtom.  
\q1 Mi wal sananŋan na, mbotŋana kizin kembei kai ta molo som mi imeete.\x + \xo 13:9 \xt Tut 20:20, 24:20; Mt 5:14; Pil 2:15\x*   
\q1
\v 10 Mbulu ki tapakurkur itundu, ina ipiyotyooto ŋoŋi boozo.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tileŋleŋ la sua na, ŋgar ambaiŋana imbotmbot la lelen.   
\q1
\v 11 Pat ta ka usomŋana mi ipet sorok, nako imap karau men mi ka ŋonoono sa som.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ikamam uraata mi iurur pat kini ilalae, na pat tana ko ipet ma iwe biibi.   
\b  
\q1
\v 12 Sombe tanamnaama koroŋ sa mi ipet karau som, inako ikam ma lelende isaana.  
\q1 Mi talala ma sombe takam koroŋ tana, inako ikam ma menmeen ti, mi tayamaana kembei mbotŋana kiti ambai.   
\q1
\v 13 Zin wal ta tirepilpiili sua ki Anutu kembei koroŋ sorok, nako tire kadoono pa mbulu kizin tana.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ileŋleŋ la tutu ki Anutu mi imoto kana, nako ikam le kadoono ambaiŋana.\x + \xo 13:13 \xt Tut 16:20; Yo 12:48\x*   
\q1
\v 14 Zin wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na, sua kizin kembei yok bukbukŋana ta ipiyotyooto mbotŋana ambaiŋana piti.  
\q1 Pa ipiŋgisŋgis kumbundu pa kilis tabe ikam ti ma temeete i.\x + \xo 13:14 \xt Tut 10:11, 14:27, 18:4\x*   
\q1
\v 15 Ŋgar ambaiŋana ta iurur ŋonoono, ina ikam ma tomtom lelen piti.  
\q1 Mi zin wal pakaamŋan ta tisu mini mi tiur koi pa zitun wal kizin na, zaala kizin ko ipata.   
\q1
\v 16 Zin wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na, timbot mi titiiri uraata ka zaala muŋgu, mana tikam.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, tipamalmaala ŋgar kizin talliŋana ila iwal biibi matan.   
\q1
\v 17 Sombe toŋgo tomtom sananŋana sa pa uraata, inako ikam pataŋana piti.  
\q1 Mi sombe ŋgoŋana kiti ila ma iso kat sua kiti, ina irao iurpe pataŋana kiti.\x + \xo 13:17 \xt Tut 10:26, 25:13\x*   
\q1
\v 18 Tomtom ta so ileŋsil sua tutŋana, na kaimer ko imbot ŋoobo mi ka miaŋ biibi.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ileŋleŋ la sua pazalŋana, na kaimer zaana ko iwe biibi.\x + \xo 13:18 \xt Tut 10:17\x*   
\q1
\v 19 Sombe tanamnaama koroŋ sa ma molo mana takam, inako ikam ti ma lelende ambai kat mi toso: “Aa buri!”  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, lelen be tipizil ndemen pa mbulu kizin sananŋana ri sa som.   
\b  
\q1
\v 20 Tomtom ta so igabgaaba wal ŋgarŋan, nako iwe tomtom ŋgarŋana.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so igabgaaba wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, ni ko indeeŋe pataŋana.\x + \xo 13:20 \xt Tut 1:10, 2:20, 12:26\x*   
\q1
\v 21 Zin wal ta mbulu kizin irao pa Anutu mataana som na, pataŋana indeŋdeeŋe zin.  
\q1 Mi wal ndeeŋeŋan na, mbotŋana ambaiŋana ta iwe len kadoono.   
\b  
\q1
\v 22 Mazwaana ta so tomtom ambaiŋana imbotmbot toono na, ni ikamam le koroŋ boozo. Tana kaimer sombe imeete, na lutuunu ma tumbuunu bizin ko tikam len matamur ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta mbulu kizin irao pa Anutu mataana som na, koroŋ boozomen ta tindoundou na, kaimer ko iwe wal ndeeŋeŋan len.   
\q1
\v 23 Ŋonoono, mokleene kizin wal sorrokŋan ipiyotyooto kini boozo.  
\q1 Tamen tomtom tipakamkaam zin mi tikamam ŋoobo mbulu pizin, tabe kan kini irao som.   
\q1
\v 24 Tomtom ta so lutuunu ikamam ŋoobo mbulu mi ni ibalisi som, na iurur kat leleene pa lutuunu som.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so iurur kat leleene pa lutuunu, nako karau men mi ipazali mi iurpe mbulu kini.\x + \xo 13:24 \xt Tut 3:12, 19:18, 22:15, 23:13, 29:15; Ep 6:4; Ibr 12:7\x*   
\q1
\v 25 Wal ndeeŋeŋan tikanan kini ma kopon bok.  
\q1 Mi wal sananŋan na, peteltel zin ma kopon golok kat.\x + \xo 13:25 \xt Tut 10:3\x*   
\c 14  
\q1
\v 1 Zin moori ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na, tikamam uraata be tiurpe ruumu kizin mi mboti ki wal kizin.  
\q1 Mi zin moori kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, mbulu kizin ipasansaana ruumu kizin mi mboti ki wal kizin.\x + \xo 14:1 \xt Tut 12:4, 19:14, 31:10+; Rut 4:11\x*   
\q1
\v 2 Sombe tomtom sa ipa pai kini ma ambai men pa Yooba mataana, ina iswe i kembei ni imototo Yooba, mi ileŋleŋ la kalŋaana.  
\q1 Mi sombe tomtom sa itoto zaala pakaamŋana, ina iswe i kembei ni irepilpiili Yooba kembei koroŋ sorok.   
\q1
\v 3 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, sua kizin talliŋana ta iwe uunu pizin be teene ikan zin.  
\q1 Mi wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na, sua kizin iporoukalkaala zin ma timbotmbot ambai.   
\q1
\v 4 Sombe tiŋgiimi lende bapolo, nako lende uraata be tuputu i. Mi irao tomoto pa ka uraata pepe.  
\q1 Pa ulaaŋa tabe ni ipimiili piti i, ko biibi ma ilip. Ko ikam ma mokleene kiti ipiyooto kini boozo.\x + \xo 14:4 \xt Tut 12:10\x*   
\q1
\v 5 Tomtom ŋonoono isombe ipombol tomtom toro sua kini, na irao ipakaam na som.  
\q1 Mi sombe tomtom pakamkaamŋana sa ipombol tomtom toro sua kini, na irao tendemeere sua kini tana na som. Pa zin wal ta kembei, kwon bok pa sua pakaamŋana.   
\q1
\v 6 Tomtom ta so ipakurkur itunu mi irepilpiili ŋgar ambaiŋana, sombe iru ŋgar ambaiŋana, nako irao indeeŋe na som. Ko ike pini.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta ŋgar kizin ipet kek, nako imarra pizin be tikam len ŋgar pakan ma isala ki.   
\q1
\v 7 Wal kankaanŋan ta tizorzooro na, garrau zin pepe. Mbotmbot molo pizin.  
\q1 Pa ŋgar ambaiŋana sa ko irao iyooto pa kwon na som.\x + \xo 14:7 \xt Ep 5:15\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 8 Wal ŋgarŋan na, matan iŋgalŋgal zitun mi tikamam ŋgar pa zaala ta titoto na: Zaala tana ambai, som ambai som?  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, ŋgar kizin talliŋana ipakankaana zin.   
\q1
\v 9 Sombe tomtom sa ikam patoronŋana pa sanaana kini, na wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, ko tikam sua repiiliŋana pini.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tikamam kat mbulu na, Anutu leleene pizin.   
\q1
\v 10 Tomtom toro sa irao iute kat lelende na som.  
\q1 Pa sombe lelende ipata kat, som menmeen ti biibi, na iti itundu men ta tayamaana.   
\q1
\v 11 Mbotŋana kizin wal sananŋan ko kembei ruumu ta ibuuzu ma borok su lene.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tikamam kat mbulu na, mbotŋana kizin ko kembei ruumu ta imbol ma imbotmbot.\x + \xo 14:11 \xt Tut 10:25; Mt 7:24-29\x*   
\q1
\v 12 Zaala pakan ta tomtom titoto na, tindemeere ma tiso ko zaala ambaimbaiŋan.  
\q1 Mi som. Ina zaala ki meeteŋana.\x + \xo 14:12 \xt Mt 7:13-14,21-23\x*   
\q1
\v 13 Wal pakan tizeŋzeeŋge sorok. Tamen lelen na, ambai som.  
\q1 Mi tomtom pakan ta koozi lelen ambai mi menmeen zin na, kaimer ko lelen ipata.   
\q1
\v 14 Tomtom ta so ipizil ndemeene pa zaala ki Anutu, nako ire kat kadoono pa mbulu kini tana.  
\q1 Mi wal ambaimbaiŋan ta kembena. Zin ko tikam len kadoono ambaiŋana pa mbulu ta tikamam na.   
\q1
\v 15 Zin wal ta len ŋgar biibi som na, tikanan la sorok sua ta boozomen.  
\q1 Mi wal ŋgarŋan na, tikamam ŋgar pa zaala ta titoto na: Zaala tana ambai, som ambai som?\x + \xo 14:15 \xt Tut 4:26\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 16 Tomtom ta le ŋgar ambaiŋana na, imototo kana mi imbotmbot molo pa koroŋ sananŋan.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, tipase pa zitun ma tiso tirao. Tanata timototo som, mi tikamam mbulu talliŋana tabe ipasaana zin i.\x + \xo 14:16 \xt Tut 28:14\x*   
\q1
\v 17 Tomtom ta so keteene malmal karau, nako ikam mbulu talliŋana.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta gorgori tirru zaala be tikam mbulu sananŋana na, tomtom tiurur koi pizin.\x + \xo 14:17 \xt Tut 12:16, 16:32; Tit 1:7; Yems 1:20\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 18 Zin wal ta len ŋgar biibi som na, tipamalmaala mbulu kizin talliŋana, kembei zin naroogo kan tipamalmaala aigau kizin.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na, ŋgar kizin tana iswe zin kembei zan bibip, kembei mogar ta zin king tiurur na.   
\q1
\v 19 Wal sananŋan ko tilek kumbun pizin wal ambaimbaiŋan.  
\q1 Ko tilala pa wal ndeeŋeŋan ruumu kizin kwon kwon, mi tipakurkur zin.\x + \xo 14:19 \xt Tur 3:9\x*   
\q1
\v 20 Wal sorrokŋan na, waen bizin tiurur kat lelen pizin som.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta mbio uunu na, len tomtom boozo.\x + \xo 14:20 \xt Tut 19:4,7\x*   
\q1
\v 21 Tomtom ta so mata pasom waene bizin, ina ni ikam sanaana.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so imuŋaiŋai zin wal ta timbot ŋoobo na, ni ko leleene ambai mi kampeŋana biibi imbotmbot se kini.\x + \xo 14:21 \xt Mbo 41:1; Tut 22:9, 31:9; Mt 5:7; Yems 2:12-16\x*   
\q1
\v 22 Zin wal ta lelen iurur pa mbulu sananŋana na, tisaŋsaŋ pa zaala ambaiŋana kek.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so irru zaala be ikam mbulu ambaiŋana pizin tomtom, na tomtom ko tiurur kat lelen pini. Irao tizemi na som.   
\q1
\v 23 Uraata boozomen ta so takam kat, inako iuulu iti.  
\q1 Mi sombe tombomboorende men, mi toyyo kwondo pa sua soroksorok, nako molo som to tusu ma tombot ŋoobo.\x + \xo 14:23 \xt Tut 21:5\x*   
\q1
\v 24 Zin wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na, tirao kat pa koroŋ boozo, mi koroŋ kizin tana iswe zin kembei zan bibip, kembei mogar ta zin king tiurur na.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, ta kembena. Mbulu kizin talliŋana ta izzwe zin.   
\b  
\q1
\v 25 Tomtom ta so ikam ŋoobo mbulu sa som, mi tipamenderi sorok be tipuni ma imeete, sombe le gaabaŋana sa be iso sua ŋonoono mi ipombol sua kini, na gaabaŋana tana ko irao be ikamke i.  
\q1 Mi sombe tomtom pakamkaamŋana sa ipombol tomtom toro sua kini, na irao tendemeere sua kini tana na som. Pa sua kini tana ko pakaamŋana.   
\b  
\q1
\v 26 Tomtom ta so imototo Yooba mi ileŋleŋ la kalŋaana, nako ipase pa Yooba be iporoukaali.  
\q1 Mi lutuunu bizin tomini ko tipase pa Yooba be iwe ur pizin.\x + \xo 14:26 \xt Tut 18:10, 20:7\x*   
\q1
\v 27 Mbulu ki tomototo Yooba mi teleŋleŋ la kalŋaana, ina kembei yok bukbukŋana ta ipiyotyooto mbotŋana ambaiŋana piti.  
\q1 Pa ipiŋgisŋgis kumbundu pa kilis boozomen tabe ikam ti ma temeete i.\x + \xo 14:27 \xt Tut 13:14\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 28 King sa, sombe imborro iwal biibi, nako niini ise mi ikam zaana biibi.  
\q1 Mi sombe imborro wal boozo som, inako mbotŋana kini isaana, mi zaana biibi som.   
\q1
\v 29 Sombe tomtom sa leleene luumuŋana, ina iswe i kembei ni le ŋgar biibi.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so keteene malmal karau, ina ni ipamaala mbulu kini talliŋana ma imbot kat mat.\x + \xo 14:29 \xt Tut 16:32, 17:27, 19:11; Yems 1:19\x*   
\q1
\v 30 Sombe lelende ambai, nako ikam ma kulindi imbot ambai tomini.  
\q1 Mi sombe matanda mburmbur, inako ikam mete piti.   
\q1
\v 31 Tomtom ta so ikototo zin wal sorrokŋan, ina ni irepilpiili Anutu ta iur zin na.  
\q1 Mi sombe tomtom sa ikampewe zin wal ta timbot ŋoobo, inako iwe zaala pa Anutu be ikam zaana biibi.\x + \xo 14:31 \xt Tut 17:5, 22:2; Mt 25:40; Yems 3:9\x*   
\q1
\v 32 Mbulu sananŋana ta wal sananŋan tikamam na, ko ipasaana zitun.  
\q1 Mi sombe wal ndeeŋeŋan timeete, na Anutu ko iwe ur pizin be tike lela ma timbot ambai.\x + \xo 14:32 \xt Mbo 49:14-15\x*   
\q1
\v 33 Zin wal ta ŋgar kizin ipet kek na, lelen iwe kembei ŋgar ambaiŋana muriini be imbotmbot pa.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, ŋgar ambaiŋana sa imbotmbot la lelen som.   
\q1
\v 34 Lele sa, sombe tikamam mbulu ndeeŋeŋana men, nako zan iwe biibi.  
\q1 Mi sombe tinoknok sanaana, ina ipamiaŋ zin.   
\q1
\v 35 Mbesooŋo sa, sombe le ŋgar ambaiŋana, nako king leleene pini ilip.  
\q1 Mi sombe mbesooŋo sa ipamiaŋ biibi kini, nako biibi kini keteene malmal pini.\x + \xo 14:35 \xt Mt 24:45-51, 25:14-30\x*   
\c 15  
\q1
\v 1 Sombe tomtom keten malmal piti mi tepekel pa sua luumuŋana, nako takam ma lelen iluumu.  
\q1 Mi sua kekeŋana, ina ipazas tomtom keten.\x + \xo 15:1 \xt Tut 25:15\x*  
\v 2 Zin wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na, tizzwe ŋgar kizin totomen som. Mazwaana tataŋa men ta tipiyotyooto ŋgar kizin pizin tomtom.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, kwon pereupereu pa sua. Sua kizin talliŋana ireere kembei ta yok!\x + \xo 15:2 \xt Tut 12:23, 13:16\x*  
\v 3 Yooba, ni mataana molo. Tana ire lele ta boozomen.  
\q1 Mataana ikamam zin wal sananaŋan, mi wal ambaimbaiŋan tomini.\x + \xo 15:3 \xt Mbo 33:13-15, 90:8, 139:1+; Ibr 4:13\x*  
\v 4 Sombe sua ta iwedet pa kwondo na iurpewe tomtom lelen, ina iwe kembei ke ta ipiyotyooto mbotŋana ambaiŋana pizin.  
\q1 Mi sombe sua pakaamŋana iwedet pa kwondo, ina ipasansaana tomtom lelen.\x + \xo 15:4 \xt Tut 6:19, 10:11, 22:22\x*  
\v 5 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, sombe taman bizin tipazal zin, na tileŋleŋ la kalŋan som.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta le ŋgar ambaiŋana na, ni ileŋleŋ la sua pazalŋana.\x + \xo 15:5 \xt Tut 12:1, 13:1,18\x*  
\v 6 Wal ndeeŋeŋan ruumu kizin, ina bok pa koroŋ ndabokbokŋan matakiŋa.  
\q1 Mi pat ta wal sananŋan tikamam, ina ikamam pataŋana pizin.\x + \xo 15:6 \xt Tut 10:2,16\x*  
\v 7 Zin wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na, sua ŋgarŋana ta iwedet pa kwon, ina irak ma irao zin tomtom.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, tikamam ta kembei som. Pa ŋgar ambaiŋana sa imbotmbot la lelen som.   
\b  
\q1
\v 8 Patoronŋana kizin wal sananŋan na, Yooba leleene pa ri sa som kat.  
\q1 Tamen zin wal ta tikamam kat mbulu na, ni leleene pa suŋŋana kizin ilip.\x + \xo 15:8 \xt Mbo 51:17; Tut 21:27, 28:9; Yo 9:31; Yems 5:16\x*  
\v 9 Zaala ta wal sananŋan titoto na, Yooba leleene pa ri sa som kat.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tikamam kinkiini pa mbulu ndeeŋeŋana na, ni iurur kat leleene pizin.\x + \xo 15:9 \xt Tut 21:21; 1Tim 6:11\x*  
\v 10 Tomtom ta so izem zaala ambaiŋana, nako mbulu kekeŋana sa ipet pini bekena ipazali.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so leleene iŋgis pa sua pazalŋana, nako imeete ma ila lene.   
\q1
\v 11 Andewa mi lele ta tipasansaana zin wal meeteŋan su pa i, ina Yooba irre. Ike pa mataana som.  
\q1 Mi so kembena, na ni irre iti tomtom lelende tomini.\x + \xo 15:11 \xt Mbo 44:20-21, 139:8\x*  
\v 12 Tomtom ta so ipakurkur itunu mi irepilpiili ŋgar ambaiŋana, sombe tipazali, nako leleene iŋgis.  
\q1 Tana wal ta kembei lelen be tila kizin wal ŋgarŋan ma tiuulu zin pa ŋgar pakan na som.   
\q1
\v 13 Sombe lelende ambai, nako tomtom tikilaala mar pa ruŋgundu.  
\q1 Mi sombe lelende ipata, nako ipasaana ŋgar kiti.\x + \xo 15:13 \xt Mbo 51:8; Tut 17:22, 18:14\x*  
\v 14 Tomtom ta so ŋgar kini ipet kek, nako ikam kinkiini be ikam le ŋgar pakan ma isala ki.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, tinoknok mbulu kizin talliŋana mi lelen pa ilip, kembei ta kini namutŋana.\x + \xo 15:14 \xt Tut 18:15\x*  
\v 15 Zin wal ta timbotmbot raama pataŋana na, aigule sa ambai pizin som.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so leleene ambai, na ni kembei tomtom ta ikanan ma iwinin mi menmeeni ikot aigule ta boozomen.   
\b  
\q1
\v 16 Iti sombe tomototo Yooba ma teleŋleŋ la kalŋaana, mi lende koroŋ rimen,  
\q1 nako mbotŋana kiti ambai ma ilip pizin wal ta len koroŋ boozo, mi tamen timbotmbot raama lelen ipata.\x + \xo 15:16 \xt Mbo 37:16-17, 39:6-7; Tut 17:1\x*  
\v 17 Iti sombe kanda kini biibi som, mi tamen lelende par piti,  
\q1 nako mbotŋana kiti ambai ma ilip pizin wal tau tikanan kini ambaiŋana, mi tamen tiurur lelen par pizin som.   
\b  
\q1
\v 18 Tomtom ta so keteene malmalŋana, nako ipeyei malmal.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta keten malmal karau som na, tipunmetmeete ŋoŋi.\x + \xo 15:18 \xt Tut 10:12, 26:21, 29:22; Yems 1:20\x*  
\v 19 Tomtom maolŋana isombe ila pa uraata, inako som. Pa koroŋ boozomen ko ipakalkaali ma kembei kolomboŋ ikowo i.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tikamam kat mbulu na, titoto zaala ambaiŋana ta mbaŋbaŋ sa isekaala som. Tana tipa pai kizin ma ambai men.\x + \xo 15:19 \xt Tut 22:5\x*  
\v 20 Sombe pikin sa le ŋgar ambaiŋana, nako ikam ma tamaana leleene ambai kat.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, tirepilpiili nan bizin.\x + \xo 15:20 \xt Tut 10:1, 17:21,25, 19:13, 29:3\x*  
\v 21 Zin wal ta len ŋgar somŋan i, na lelen ilip pa mbulu talliŋana.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ŋgar kini ipet kek na, ni itoto zaala ndeeŋeŋana men.   
\q1
\v 22 Sombe wal pakan tiuulu iti pa ŋgar kizin som, nako ŋgar kiti iur ŋonoono som.  
\q1 Mi sombe wal boozo tiuulu iti pa ŋgar kizin, nako uraata kiti iloondo ambai, mi ŋgar kiti iur ŋonoono.\x + \xo 15:22 \xt Tut 11:14, 20:18, 24:6\x*  
\v 23 Sombe tepekel sua kizin tomtom, mi sua kiti ila ma indeeŋe men, ina ikam ti ma lelende ambai kat.  
\q1 Tana tipiri sua karau pepe. Tombot mi tanaama ka mazwaana muŋgu. Iso ipet, to tipiri. Naso sua kiti itop la kat.\x + \xo 15:23 \xt Tut 24:26, 25:11\x*  
\v 24 Zin wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na, ko irao tisula Andewa na som. Zin ko tikam mbotŋana ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Pa titoto zaala ta izalla pa saamba.   
\q1
\v 25 Zin wal ta tipakurkur zitun na, Yooba irekreege ruumu kizin mi mboti kizin.  
\q1 Mi zin noroŋa na, ni mataana pizin: Kokena tomtom sa ipakaam zin mi ikam toono kizin.\x + \xo 15:25 \xt Tut 23:10-11; Lu 1:51; 1Pe 5:5\x*  
\v 26 Wal sananŋan na, Yooba leleene pa ŋgar kizin ri sa som kat.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta lelen ŋgeezeŋan na, ni leleene pa sua kizin.\x + \xo 15:26 \xt Mbo 18:26, 24:4\x*  
\v 27 Tomtom ta so mata koroŋŋana, na ni ikamam pataŋana pa wal kini.  
\q1 Mi mbulu ki tiŋgiimi zin tomtom bekena tigaaba iti, ina tomini ikamam pataŋana piti. Tana tomtom ta so iurur koi pa mbulu tana, nako imbot ambai.\x + \xo 15:27 \xt Mbo 15:5; Tut 28:25\x*  
\v 28 Wal ndeeŋeŋan timbot mi tikam kat ŋgar pa sua uunu muŋgu, mana tipekel.  
\q1 Mi sua ta iwedet pa wal sananŋan kwon, ina ambai som kat.\x + \xo 15:28 \xt Tut 10:32; 1Pe 3:15\x*  
\v 29 Yooba imbotmbot molo pizin wal sananŋan.  
\q1 Mi wal ndeeŋeŋan na, ni ileŋleŋ suŋŋana kizin.\x + \xo 15:29 \xt Yo 9:31\x*  
\v 30 Sombe ruŋgundu iswe iti kembei lelende ambai, nako ikam ma zin wal ta tire iti na, lelen ambai tomini.  
\q1 Mi sombe teleŋ uruunu ambaiŋana sa pizin wal pakan, inako ikam ma nindi ise.   
\q1
\v 31 Sombe tomtom tipazal ti bekena tiurpe mbotŋana kiti, mi teleŋ la kalŋan,  
\q1 nako tarao be tagaaba zin wal ŋgarŋan.   
\q1
\v 32 Sombe takam sua pazalŋana pa tomtom sa mi ni ileŋtut, ina ni mata pasom itunu.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ileŋleŋ la sua pazalŋana, na ŋgar kini ko izze.   
\q1
\v 33 Mbulu ki tomototo Yooba mi teleŋleŋ la kalŋaana, ina zaala ŋonoono tabe takam lende ŋgar ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Mi sombe lelende be zanda iwe biibi, na bela tokoto itundu muŋgu.\x + \xo 15:33 \xt Mt 23:12; Lu 14:11, 18:14; 1Pe 5:6\x*   
\c 16  
\q1
\v 1 Ŋonoono, iti tomtom lelende iurur pa mbulu matakiŋa tabe takam i.  
\q1 Mi sua ta iwedet pa kwondo na, Yooba itunu ta ikamam peeze pa. \x + \xo 16:1 \xt Tut 19:21; Yems 4:13-14\x*   
\q1
\v 2 Iti tomtom tendemeere itundu kembei mbulu kiti ta boozomen iŋgeeze men pa Anutu mataana.  
\q1 Mi Yooba, ni itirtiiri lelende mi iute uunu tau takamam mbulu kiti pa i. \x + \xo 16:2 \xt Mbo 139:23; Tut 21:2; 1Kor 4:4; Ibr 4:12\x*   
\q1
\v 3 Uraata boozomen ta lelem iurur pa be kam na, ur ila Yooba namaana.  
\q1 Naso ŋgar ku tana iur ŋonoono. \x + \xo 16:3 \xt Mbo 37:5, 55:22, 90:17; 1Pe 5:7\x*   
\q1
\v 4 Koroŋ boozomen ta Yooba iur na, kan uraata makiŋ.  
\q1 Zin wal sananŋan tomini. Yooba iur zin beso kan nol ipet, to iswe kete malmalŋana kini pizin. \x + \xo 16:4 \xt Kam 9:15-16\x*   
\q1
\v 5 Zin wal ta so tipakurkur zitun mi tikamam ŋgar kembei tilip pa waen bizin pakan na, Yooba leleene pizin ri sa som kat.  
\q1 Tana kam ŋgar boozo pizin pepe. Kola tire kadoono pa mbulu kizin tana. Ni ko irao ileele zin na som. \x + \xo 16:5 \xt Mbo 40:4; Tut 6:16-17\x*   
\q1
\v 6 Iti sombe tuurur lelende pa Yooba mi zin tomtom, mi tototo sua kiti mbukŋana, nako Yooba ireege sanaana kiti ma ila lene.  
\q1 Mi mbulu tau tomototo Yooba mi teleŋleŋ la kalŋaana, ina iuluulu iti be tombotmbot molo pa mbulu sananŋana.   
\q1
\v 7 Iti sombe takamam mbulu kiti ma irao Yooba leleene,  
\q1 na ni ko ikam ma kanda koi bizin tomini lelen piti, mi itiŋan taparlup ti ma tombot ambai. \x + \xo 16:7 \xt Ro 12:17-18; Ibr 12:14\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 8 Iti sombe lende koroŋ rimen, mi tamen mbulu kiti indeeŋe men pa Anutu mataana,  
\q1 na mbotŋana kiti ko ambai ma ilip pizin wal ta tikam len koroŋ boozomen pa zaala sananŋana. \x + \xo 16:8 \xt Mbo 37:16; Tut 15:16, 17:1\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 9 Sombe lelende iurur pa ŋgar sa.  
\q1 na bela Yooba iyok pa ŋgar kiti tana, tona iur ŋonoono. \x + \xo 16:9 \xt Tut 19:21, 20:24\x*   
\q1
\v 10 Sua ta iwedet pa king kwoono, ina Yooba ta ikamam peeze pa.  
\q1 Tana king isombe iurpe pataŋana kizin tomtom, na bela ikam ma indeŋdeeŋe men.   
\q1
\v 11 Iti sombe lelende be takam ŋgomo pa koroŋ sa, na Yooba leleene be tuur ka kadoono ma irao kat pa ka kin.  
\q1 Kokena tasala sorok pizin wal pakan, mi pakan na, tusu pizin. Takam kadoono raraate men pizin wal ta boozomen. Pa mbulu ta kembei, ina imar pa Yooba. \x + \xo 16:11 \xt Tut 11:1, 20:10\x*   
\q1
\v 12 Mbulu sananŋana na, zin king lelen pa ri sa som kat.  
\q1 Pa zin tiute: Bela lele ta zin timborro na titoto mbulu ndeeŋeŋana men, to peeze kizin imbol. \x + \xo 16:12 \xt Tut 20:28, 25:5, 29:4,14; Ro 13:3+\x*   
\q1
\v 13 Tomtom ta so kwoono izzwe mbulu ndeeŋeŋana na, zin king ko lelen ambai pini.  
\q1 Mi zin wal tau tizzo katkat sua ŋonoono men ta kembena. Zin king lelen pizin mi tipase pizin. \x + \xo 16:13 \xt Tut 22:11\x*   
\q1
\v 14 Sombe teleŋ kembei king keteene malmal, na tere iti. Pa ni irao ipun ti ma temetmeete!  
\q1 Tamen tomtom ta le ŋgar ambaiŋana na, ni ko irao be ipaluumu king leleene.   
\q1
\v 15 Sombe king menmeeni, nako iti ta boozomen tombot ambai.  
\q1 Pa sombe leleene ambai piti, nako kampeŋana kini isu ma isalakaala iti kembei ta yaŋ ipembesmbeeze toono. \x + \xo 16:15 \xt Tut 19:12\x*   
\q1
\v 16 Iti sombe takam lende ŋgar ambaiŋana, ina ambai ma ilip pa gol ma silba.  
\q1 Tana tuur lelende pa silba pepe. Takam kinkiini be tuute kat ŋgar ambaiŋana. Pa ina koroŋ ta ambai ma ilip. \x + \xo 16:16 \xt Mbo 49:20; Tut 3:13+, 8:10+\x*   
\q1
\v 17 Tomtom ta so ikamam kat mbulu, ina kembei ipa kat pa zaala biibi. Ilae imare som. Paso leleene be imbotmbot molo pa mbulu sananŋana.  
\q1 Tana nu sombe lelem be mbot ambai, na motom iŋgalŋgal pai ku be to zaala ambaiŋana men.   
\q1
\v 18 Mbulu ki nindi izze mi tapakurkur itundu, nako ipasaana iti ma tala lende.  
\q1 Tana sombe takam ŋgar kembei iti ambaiŋanda ma tilip pa waende bizin pakan, na tere iti. Pa ko molo som, to totop. \x + \xo 16:18 \xt Tut 11:2, 18:12\x*   
\q1
\v 19 Zin wal tau tipakurkur zitun mi tiwatkewe len koroŋ na, tomtom pakan tigabgaaba zin paso, lelen ilip pa ndomon ta wal tana tikamam pizin na.  
\q1 Tamen iti sombe tokototo itundu mi tagabgaaba zin wal sorrokŋan, nako mbotŋana kiti ambai ma ilip pizin tomtom ta kembei. \x + \xo 16:19 \xt Tut 3:34\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 20 Tomtom ta so ileŋleŋ la sua tutŋana mi itoto, nako indeeŋe mbotŋana ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ipase pa Yooba, nako leleene ambai kat mi kampeŋana ki Yooba imbotmbot se kini. \x + \xo 16:20 \xt Mbo 34:8, 37:5; Tut 13:13\x*   
\q1
\v 21 Zin wal tau lelen bok pa ŋgar ambaiŋana na, tomtom tiwidit urun pa ŋgar kizin.  
\q1 Mi sombe sua kiti ambai pa tomtom talŋan, nako ikam ma lelen be tileŋleŋ len. To ŋgar kizin ipet karau men.   
\q1
\v 22 Zin wal ta so tikamam kat ŋgar, na ŋgar kizin tana ko iwe kembei yok bukbukŋana ta ipiyotyooto mbotŋana ambaiŋana pizin.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, zin ko tire kadoono pa mbulu kizin talliŋana. \x + \xo 16:22 \xt Tut 13:14\x*   
\q1
\v 23 Ŋgar ambaiŋana ta imbotmbot la tomtom ŋgarŋana leleene, ina ikamam peeze pa sua ta iwedet pa kwoono na.  
\q1 Tana sua kini ipeyei ŋgar kizin tomtom.   
\q1
\v 24 Sua ambaiŋana ta ikamam lelende i, ina namutŋana kat, kembei ta bigil suruunu.  
\q1 Sua ta kembei iurpewe lelende mi ŋgar kiti, mi ikamam ma kulindi imbot ambai tomini.   
\q1
\v 25 Zaala pakan, tomtom tire na, tiso ko zaala ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Mi som. Sombe toto zaala tana ma tala, nako temetmeete ma tala lende. \x + \xo 16:25 \xt Mt 7:13-14\x*   
\q1
\v 26 Wal uraata kan sombe petel zin, nako timaŋga mi tikam kat uraata.  
\q1 Paso lelen be tikan kan kini. \x + \xo 16:26 \xt 2Tes 3:10\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 27 Zin wal ta tikamam mbulu soroksorok na, lelen iurur pa mbulu bozboozo.  
\q1 Mi sua kizin ipasansaana zin tomtom kembei ta you na. \x + \xo 16:27 \xt Mbo 140:2-3; Yems 3:6\x*   
\q1
\v 28 Zin wal ta tizem zaala ambaiŋana na, tipeyei ŋoŋi.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tininin kao na, tirao be tikam ma itiŋan torondo bizin ŋonoono taparmbotmbot molo piti.   
\q1
\v 29 Zin wal ta tikamam zaaba pizin tomtom na, tiyaryaaru waen bizin be tito zaala sananŋana.   
\q1
\v 30 Tomtom ta so mataana ikinmeete pa waene toro, na leleene iurur be ikam mbulu sa.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ikarrut zuruunu na, ni kola ikam malmal. Peteke i, na rao som. \x + \xo 16:30 \xt Tut 6:13, 10:10\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 31 Moomo kizin kolman ta iwe aigau pizin, mi ikam ma tomtom tipakurkur zin.  
\q1 Pa ina iswe zin kembei titoto zaala ndeeŋeŋana. \x + \xo 16:31 \xt Tut 20:29\x*   
\q1
\v 32 Tomtom ta so iyaramraama itunu, mi keteene malmal karau som, na ni ilip pizin wal ta tirao kat pa malmal na.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so imborro kat itunu, na ni ilip pizin wal malmal kan ta tiporou mbolŋana ma tilip pa kar ta kek. \x + \xo 16:32 \xt Tut 14:17, 19:11; Yems 1:19\x*   
\q1
\v 33 Tomtom tikamam mbulu matakiŋa bekena ipatooŋo zin pa zaala tabe tito i.  
\q1 Mi mbulu tana iso ipet be parei, na Yooba itunu ta ikamam peeze pa.   
\c 17  
\q1
\v 1 Sombe kanda kini ri sa, mi itiŋan wal kiti lelende ambai, mi taparlup ti ma tombotmbot,  
\q1 na mbotŋana kiti ko ambai ma ilip pizin wal ta kan kini biibi, mi tamen timbotmbot raama ŋoŋi. \x + \xo 17:1 \xt Mbo 37:16; Tut 15:16+, 16:8\x*   
\q1
\v 2 Tomtom sa, sombe lutuunu ipamiaŋi, nako iur mbesooŋo kini sorokŋana sa ta le ŋgar ambaiŋana na ma iwe biibi pa lutuunu tana be imboro i.  
\q1 Mi kaimer ni ko ikam mbesooŋo tana le matamur kini raraate kembei ta ikam pa itunu lutuunu bizin pakan.   
\q1
\v 3 You ikanan gol ma silba bekena kan muk ila ne ma tiŋgeeze kat.  
\q1 Mi iti tomtom na, Yooba izemzem pataŋana pakan ma iwedet piti bekena itoombo iti mi ipeŋgeeze mbulu kiti. \x + \xo 17:3 \xt Mbo 26:2, 139:23; 1Pe 1:7\x*   
\q1
\v 4 Tomtom sananŋana, ni ileŋleŋ la sua ta iwedet pa wal sananŋan kwon.  
\q1 Mi tomtom pakamkaamŋana na, ni iŋgungun talŋaana pizin wal ta tipasansaana tomtom urun.   
\q1
\v 5 Tomtom ta so igibgiibi sua repiiliŋana pizin wal sorrokŋan, ina ni kwoono pasom Anutu tomini. Pa ni ta iur zin wal sorrokŋan ma tipet.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ire tomtom toro ibaada sorok pataŋana mi leleene ambai pa, na ire i. Pa ni kola ire kadoono pa mbulu kini tana. Irao Anutu ileeli na som. \x + \xo 17:5 \xt Tut 14:31, 24:17\x*   
\q1
\v 6 Tomtom ta so iwe kolman kat mi ire tumbuunu bizin, nako niini ise. Paso tumbuunu bizin tana tiwe kembei aigau pini be tomtom tiwit uruunu.  
\q1 Mi zin pikin ta kembena. Nin se pa mbulu ki taman ma nan bizin. \x + \xo 17:6 \xt Mbo 128:5-6\x*   
\q1
\v 7 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, mbulu kizin pakurŋana tere kembei ambai som.  
\q1 Mi sombe zin bibip ta tikamam peeze i tipakamkaam, ina ambai som kat!   
\q1
\v 8 Zin wal ta tiwadat zin tomtom pa pat bekena tito ŋgar kizin na, tindemeere pat kizin tana kembei ta naborou i.  
\q1 Pa tire kembei pat tana iuluulu uraata kizin ta boozomen ma ilonloondo ambai men! \x + \xo 17:8 \xt Kam 23:8; Tut 15:27, 28:16; 1Tim 6:10\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 9 Iti sombe tuurur lelende pizin tomtom, nako matanda imbiriizikaala sanaana kizin.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so izeizei lene sua kizin wal pakan mi iyyo kwoono pa, na ni irao ikam ma itiŋan torondo bizin ŋonoono taparmbot molo piti. \x + \xo 17:9 \xt Tut 10:12, 16:28\x*   
\q1
\v 10 Tomtom ta so ŋgar kini ipet kek na, sombe tayaambi, nako karau men mi itooro mbulu kini.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, som. Sombe tabalis zin pa re pa tomto lamata, na takamam lende men. Mi irao titooro mbulu kizin sananŋana na som.   
\q1
\v 11 Wal sananŋan, ŋgar kizin imbol kat be tikam mbulu zooroŋana.  
\q1 Tana kaimer biibi sa kola ila ma ibalis kat zin. Mi ni ko irao imuŋai zin ri sa som.   
\q1
\v 12 Ŋge saŋsaŋŋana ta so ipeebe na, koroŋ ambai som. Sombe la garau ŋgini kini, nako imaŋga mi ikanu.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanŋan ta tizorzooro na, zin ambai som kat. Pa mbulu kizin talliŋana irao be ipasaana katu. Tana la garau zin pepe. \x + \xo 17:12 \xt Tut 29:9\x*   
\q1
\v 13 Tomtom ta so tikam mbulu ambaiŋana pini mi ipokot pa mbulu sananŋana,  
\q1 na ziŋan wal kini mbotŋana kizin ko isaana kat ma imborene ta kembei. Irao ambai mini na som. Som kat. \x + \xo 17:13 \xt Mbo 109:4+; Ro 12:17; 1Tes 5:15; 1Pe 3:9\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 14 Sombe pataŋana sa ipet na, kwom la pa karau pepe. Zem sua pa.  
\q1 Kokena kam ma ŋoŋi musaana ila ma iwe pataŋana biibi ŋonoono.   
\q1
\v 15 Zin bibip ta titirtiiri sua i, sombe tizem zin wal sananŋan ma tila sorok, som tiur sorok kadoono pizin wal ta len uunu sa som,  
\q1 na Yooba leleene pa mbulu ru tana ri sa som kat. \x + \xo 17:15 \xt Kam 23:6-8; Mbo 94:21-23\x*   
\q1
\v 16 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, titeege pat pepe.  
\q1 Pa zin tikam kinkiini pa ŋgar ambaiŋana som.   
\q1
\v 17 Torondo bizin ŋonoono, nako tiurur lelen piti pa mazwaana ta boozomen.  
\q1 Mi toŋmatiziŋ kiti timbotmbot be tiuulu iti pa pataŋana kiti. \x + \xo 17:17 \xt Rut 1:16; Tut 18:24; 1Kor 13:4-7\x*   
\q1
\v 18 Tomtom ta so imender pa tomtom toro mi imbuk sua ta kembei: “Sombe ni irao be ikot mbun kini som, na nio ituŋ ko aŋkot.”  
\q1 Na tomtom ta kembei, ni kankaanaŋana kat. \x + \xo 17:18 \xt Tut 6:1+, 11:5, 20:16, 22:26+\x*   
\q1
\v 19 Zin wal ta lelen pa mbulu sananŋana, ta tiŋoŋooŋo len sorok.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ipo siiri biibi bekena ipakuri pa, mibe iyembut itunu pa waene bizin pakan, na ni itoto zaala tabe ipasaani. \x + \xo 17:19 \xt Tut 16:18, 18:12, 29:22-23\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 20 Tomtom ta so ŋgar sanaŋana izeebi kek, nako irao indeeŋe mbotŋana ambaiŋana na som.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so miaana ibogboogo, nako indeeŋe pataŋana.   
\q1
\v 21 Pikin kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, tipasansaana taman bizin lelen.  
\q1 Tana taman bizin ko irao lelen ambai na som. \x + \xo 17:21 \xt Tut 10:1, 15:20\x*   
\q1
\v 22 Sombe lelende ambai mi menmeen ti, inako iuulu kulindi tomini be imbot ambai.  
\q1 Mi sombe lelende isaana ma tombotmbot, inako ikam mete piti. \x + \xo 17:22 \xt Mbo 32:3; Tut 15:13, 18:14\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 23 Wal sananŋan, sombe tomtom sa ipabeleu pat mi ikam pizin bekena tipakaam mi tiuuli pa sua kini, na zin ko tiyok pa men.  
\q1 Pa mbulu ki sua urpeŋana na, zin tikamam ŋgar pa ri sa som. \x + \xo 17:23 \xt Kam 18:21, 23:8\x*   
\q1
\v 24 Tomtom ta so ŋgar kini ipet kek, nako ŋgar ambaiŋana imbotmbot keren uunu totomen.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, matan ipinin pa koroŋ ŋonon somŋan tau timbotmbot molo pizin i. Mi ko tirao be tikam na som.   
\q1
\v 25 Pikin kankaanŋan ta tizorzooro na, ko tipasaana taman bizin lelen.  
\q1 Mi nan bizin ta tipeebe zin na tomini, ko keten pakpak. \x + \xo 17:25 \xt Tut 10:1\x*   
\q1
\v 26 Sombe tuur sorok pataŋana pizin wal ta tikamam kat mbulu, ina ambai som.  
\q1 Mi zin bibip tau tikamam kat uraata kizin ta kembena. Tapamiaŋ zin pepe, mi tiseeze sorok matan pepe.   
\b  
\q1
\v 27 Tomtom ta so le ŋgar ambaiŋana, nako imborro kat kwoono.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta ŋgar kizin ipet kek na, keten meeteŋan. \x + \xo 17:27 \xt Tut 10:19, 14:29; Yems 1:19\x*   
\q1
\v 28 Wal kankaanaŋan, sombe timborro kat kwon mi tizzo sua pe som,  
\q1 inako tomtom tire zin kembei zin tomini len ŋgar!   
\c 18  
\q1
\v 1 Tomtom ta so leleene be igaaba zin iwal biibi som mi isombe itutamen imbotmbot ndel, nako ikam ŋgar pa itunu men.  
\q1 Mi sombe wal pakan tiso i pa ŋgar ambaimbaiŋan pakan, nako izorzooro la kalŋan.   
\q1
\v 2 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, tindemeere sorok ma tiso zin tirao pa ŋgar kek. Tana lelen be tileŋ la tomtom pakan ŋgar kizin som.  
\q1 Lelen be zin men tizzo sua. \x + \xo 18:2 \xt Tut 13:16\x*   
\q1
\v 3 Mbulu sananŋana imuŋmuuŋgu, mi sua repiiliŋana itoto.  
\q1 Pa sombe takam ŋoobo mbulu, inako tomtom kwon pasom ti ma kanda miaŋ. \x + \xo 18:3 \xt Mbo 31:18; Tut 11:2\x*   
\q1
\v 4 Sua ta iwedet pa tomtom kwon, ina kembei yok ta ka li biibi. Pa sua kizin ka uunu biibi, mi uunu pakan na ike.  
\q1 Ŋgar ambaiŋana ta tomtom tipiyotyooto, ina kembei yok bukbukŋana ta irereere ma iwedet. \x + \xo 18:4 \xt Tut 10:11, 13:14, 20:5\x*   
\q1
\v 5 Sombe tuurpe pataŋana kizin wal ndeeŋeŋan som, som talae kizin wal sananŋan, ina ambai som. \x + \xo 18:5 \xt Tut 24:23, 28:21\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 6 Sua ta iwedet pa wal kankaanaŋan kwon, ta ipazas tomtom keten ma tikamam sua boozo pizin.  
\q1 Sua kizin talliŋana ikamam ma tomtom lelen be tiballis zin men.   
\q1
\v 7 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, zitun kwon ta ipasansaana zin.  
\q1 Sua kizin iwe kembei ta kilis be ikeene zin.   
\q1
\v 8 Zin wal ta tininin kao na, tomtom lelen pa sua kizin kembei kini ta inamut kat.  
\q1 Mi tere iti. Pa sua kizin sananŋana tana ko isula kat lelende ma ipasaana ŋgar kiti. \x + \xo 18:8 \xt Mbo 55:21; Tut 26:22\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 9 Mbulu ki tamaol pa uraata, ina igabgaaba mbulu zigzikŋana.  
\q1 Mbulu ru tana tiwe kembei ta toŋmatiziŋ.   
\q1
\v 10 Yooba zaana, ina iwe kembei ruumu mbolŋana piti.  
\q1 Wal ndeeŋeŋan tilonloondo pa ruumu tana, tabe timbotmbot ambai. \x + \xo 18:10 \xt Mbo 31:3, 61:3-4\x*   
\q1
\v 11 Mi zin wal ta mbio uunu na, tipase pa koroŋ kizin be iwe siiri mbolŋana pizin.  
\q1 Mi tindemeere ma tiso pataŋana sa ko irao ilela siiri kizin tana leleene na som. \x + \xo 18:11 \xt Tut 10:15\x*   
\q1
\v 12 Tomtom sa sombe leleene bok pa ŋgar pakurŋana, nako molo som to isu ma iwe koroŋ sorok.  
\q1 Mi mbulu ki tokototo itundu mi tembesmbeeze pizin tomtom, ina iwe zaala piti be kaimer zanda iwe biibi. \x + \xo 18:12 \xt Tut 15:33, 16:18, 22:4, 29:23\x*   
\q1
\v 13 Mbot mi waem toro iposop sua kini muŋgu, mana pekel.  
\q1 Serseere pa sua pepe. Pa ina mbulu kankaanaŋana tabe ipamiaŋu.   
\q1
\v 14 Iti sombe mete ikam ti, mi tamen lelende ambai, inako ipombolmbol ti.  
\q1 Mi sombe koroŋ sa ipasaana kat lelende, ina pataŋana biibi. Asiŋ irao be ibaada? Som. \x + \xo 18:14 \xt Tut 15:13, 17:22\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 15 Zin wal ta tikilaala ŋgar iŋgoi ta ambai ma ilip na, tikamam len ŋgar pakan ma isala ki.  
\q1 Pa zin wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na, gorgori tirru len ŋgar pakan, mi tiŋgungun talŋan pa. \x + \xo 18:15 \xt Tut 15:14\x*   
\q1
\v 16 Zin wal ta tiso tire tomtom biibi sa, nako naman men ma tila kini na som. Matan iŋgalŋgal be tikam koroŋ ambaiŋana sa be tikam pini.  
\q1 Pa zin tiute: Koroŋ tana ko iwe zaala pizin be tila kat kini ma ziŋan tiso sua.   
\q1
\v 17 Wal ru tisombe timender pa sua, mi kizin tasa iso sua kini muŋgu, nako tere kembei tomtom tana ilip to ambai.  
\q1 Tamen wiŋana imiili pini zen. Tana tombot mi teleŋ wiŋana pakan tabe tikam pini i. Naso tuute: Ni iso sua ŋonoono, o som?   
\q1
\v 18 Sombe wal ru ta tiparwe kan koi na, timender pa sua mi sua kizin iporou mete, ina ambai be takam mbulu sa bekena Anutu itunu iswe asiŋ ta iso sua ŋonoono. Naso sua kizin tana imap. \x + \xo 18:18 \xt Tut 16:33\x*   
\q1
\v 19 Sombe takam ŋoobo tomtom sa ma leleene iŋgis, ina ipata be takam leleene ma imiili piti mini. Pa ŋgar kini ko imbol kat kembei siiri mbolŋana ta iliu kar na.  
\q1 Mi sombe ŋoŋi sa imbotmbot la wal pakan mazwan, ina iwe mbukuunu biibi pizin mi ikam zin ma tiparmbot molo pizin.   
\b  
\q1
\v 20 Sua ta so kwondo ipiyotyooto, nako tere ka ŋonoono imiili piti, mi takan ma kopondo bok pa.  
\q1 Sombe sua kiti ambai, nako ipiyooto ŋonoono ambaiŋana piti, mi ikam ma lelende ndabok.   
\q1
\v 21 Kwondo na, mburaana biibi. Irao ikam ti ma tombot ambai, mi irao ipasaana iti ma temeete ma tala lende tomini.  
\q1 Tana zin wal ta lelen be tizzo sua, nako tire mbulu kizin tana ka ŋonoono. \x + \xo 18:21 \xt Mbo 12:2-4; Tut 13:2-3; Mt 12:36-37; Yems 3:5-6\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 22 Tomtom ta so iwoolo moori ŋonoono ta le ŋgar ambaiŋana, ina ni ikam le koroŋ ambaiŋana kat.  
\q1 Ina kampeŋana biibi ta imar pa Yooba. \x + \xo 18:22 \xt Tut 12:4, 19:14, 31:10+\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 23 Wal sorrokŋan, zin titaŋroro zin bibip bekena timuŋai zin.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta mbio uunu na, tinin tomtom sa som. Tana kezen keke pa sua.   
\q1
\v 24 Tomtom ta so le gaabaŋana boozo, nako indeeŋe pataŋana.  
\q1 Mi torondo bizin pakan na, tiurur kat lelen piti ma tilip pa toŋmatiziŋ kiti ŋonoono. \x + \xo 18:24 \xt Tut 17:17; Yo 15:13-15\x*   
\c 19  
\q1
\v 1 Tomtom sorokŋana ta so ipa pai kini ma ambai men,  
\q1 na ilip pizin wal kankaanaŋan ta kwon ipiyotyooto sua sananŋana na. \x + \xo 19:1 \xt Tut 28:6\x*   
\q1
\v 2 Iti sombe tombol kat pa mbulu sa, mi tamen takam kat ŋgar pa ka uunu som, ina ambai som.  
\q1 Mi mbulu ki ketende pitpit tomini, ina ambai som. Pa ina ko ikam ti ma tapaŋoobo pa zaala ambaiŋana. \x + \xo 19:2 \xt Tut 29:20; Ro 10:2\x*   
\q1
\v 3 Wal pakan mbulu kizin kankaanaŋana ta ipasansaana mbotŋana kizin.  
\q1 Tamen tiurur uunu ila ki Yooba, mi keten malmal pini sorok. \x + \xo 19:3 \xt Un 4:5; Yems 1:13-14\x*   
\q1
\v 4 Sombe iti lende koroŋ boozo, nako wal boozo lelen be tigaaba iti ma tiwe torondo bizin.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta len koroŋ somŋan na, toron bizin ŋonoono tipizil ndemen pizin tomini. \x + \xo 19:4 \xt Tut 14:20\x*   
\q1
\v 5 Tomtom ta so ipombol sorok sua pakaamŋana, na ni kola ire ka kadoono. Irao tileeli na som.  
\q1 Mi zin wal tau gorgori timbelmbel sua pakaamŋana ta kembena. Kadoono tabe ise kizin i, na tirao be tiko pa na som. \x + \xo 19:5 \xt Kam 20:16, 23:1; Tut 21:28\x*   
\q1
\v 6 Zin bibip ta tikamam peeze i, na wal boozomen tirru zaala be tikam lelen.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so irairai koroŋ kini, nako tomtom ta boozomen lelen be tigaabi ma tiwe toroono bizin.   
\q1
\v 7 Tomtom sorrokŋana na, waene bizin timbotmbot molo pini.  
\q1 Sombe iso pizin be timar kini, na irao tileŋi na som.  
\q1 Mi toŋmatiziŋ kini ŋonoono tomini, tiurur lelen pini som. \x + \xo 19:7 \xt Mbo 38:11; Tut 14:20\x*   
\q1
\v 8 Tomtom ta so leleene be kunuunu imbot ambai, nako iru zaala be ikam le ŋgar ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Mi sombe tomtom sa mataana iŋgalŋgal be ikiskis ŋgar ambaiŋana, inako indeeŋe mbotŋana ambaiŋana. \x + \xo 19:8 \xt Tut 8:35-36\x*   
\q1
\v 9 Tomtom ta so ipombol sorok sua pakaamŋana, na ni kola ire kadoono pa mbulu kini tana. Irao tileeli na som.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta timbelmbel sua pakaamŋana ta kembena. Ko tisaana ma tila len. \x + \xo 19:9 \xt Tur 21:8\x*   
\q1
\v 10 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, sombe tikam len mboti ambaiŋana kat, ina irao pa ŋgar kiti som.  
\q1 Mi sombe tiur mbesooŋo sorok sa ma iwe biibi be ikam peeze pizin bibip pakan, ina tomini, ambai som kat. \x + \xo 19:10 \xt Tut 17:16, 26:1, 30:21-22\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 11 Tomtom ta so le ŋgar ambaiŋana, nako keteene malmal karau som. Tana tere mbulu kini na, iŋgeeze men.  
\q1 Pa sombe tomtom tikam ŋoobo mbulu pini, na ni irao ikam ŋgar biibi pa na som. Ire kembei koroŋ sorok. \x + \xo 19:11 \xt Tut 14:29, 16:32\x*   
\q1
\v 12 Sombe king keteene malmal, ina ikamam ti ma tomototo kembei laion ta kalŋaana izalla be ikan tomtom.  
\q1 Mi kampeŋana ki king, ina kembei tolou ta izzu mi ipalumluumu kini. \x + \xo 19:12 \xt Tut 16:14+, 20:2\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 13 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, tipasansaana mbotŋana ki taman bizin.  
\q1 Mi sombe kusindi bizin tinoknok zooroŋana mi tiŋoŋooŋo, inako tikam ma mbotŋana kiti isaana kembei ruumu ta ka kooto sumbunsumbun, mi yaŋ itoptop su ruumu leleene na. \x + \xo 19:13 \xt Tut 10:1, 17:25, 21:9, 27:15\x*   
\q1
\v 14 Ruumu mi pat, ina matamur ta tamanda ma nanda bizin tikamam piti.  
\q1 Mi sombe towoolo moori ŋonoono ta le ŋgar ambaiŋana, ina kampeŋana biibi ta Yooba ikam piti. \x + \xo 19:14 \xt Tut 18:22, 31:10+\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 15 Wal maolŋan sombe tikeene, na tizemke zin kat.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ikamam uraata som mi imbomboorene sorok, nako peteli. \x + \xo 19:15 \xt Tut 6:6-11, 10:4, 20:13\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 16 Tomtom ta so ikamam ŋgar pa itunu be imbot ambai, nako mataana iŋgalŋgal be ito kat zaala ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so irepilpiili zaala ambaiŋana mi itoto som, na ni ko imeete ma ila lene. \x + \xo 19:16 \xt Tut 13:13, 16:17\x*   
\q1
\v 17 Tomtom ta so ikampewe zin wal sorrokŋan, ina ni ikamam mbulu tana pa Anutu.  
\q1 Mi kaimer Anutu itunu ko ipokot mbulu kini tana. \x + \xo 19:17 \xt Mt 10:42, 25:40\x*   
\q1
\v 18 Pazal lutum pataaŋa. Pa iŋgi mazwaana ta ni ileŋleŋ la sua ku.  
\q1 Re beso pazali som, ina kembei nu lelem be ni imeete ma ila lene. \x + \xo 19:18 \xt Tut 13:24, 22:15, 23:13\x*   
\q1
\v 19 Tomtom ta so keteene malmal karau, nako ire ka kadoono.  
\q1 Wal ta kembei, uulu zin pa pataŋana kizin pepe. Pa kaimer zin kola tikam mini mbulu raraate men tau.   
\q1
\v 20 Sombe tomtom tisope u mi tipazalu, na leŋ la kalŋan.  
\q1 Pa ina zaala tabe nu kam lem ŋgar ambaiŋana. \x + \xo 19:20 \xt Tut 1:8-9\x*   
\q1
\v 21 Iti tomtom lelende iurur pa mbulu matakiŋa be takam.  
\q1 Mi bela ŋgar kiti ito ŋgar ki Yooba, to iur ŋonoono. \x + \xo 19:21 \xt Mbo 33:11; Tut 16:1,9\x*   
\q1
\v 22 Sombe tuurur kat lelende pizin tomtom mi tototo sua kiti mbukŋana, ina koroŋ biibi kat. Mbulu ta kembei, tomtom lelen pa ilip.  
\q1 Sombe lende koroŋ som mi tombot ŋoobo, na turu zaala pakaamŋana sa bekena tawatke lende koroŋ pepe. Ambai be tombot ŋoobo.   
\q1
\v 23 Mbulu ki tomototo Yooba mi teleŋleŋ la kalŋaana, ina zaala tabe tombot ambai pa i.  
\q1 To tomoto koroŋ toro sa som, mi takam kene kiti ma ambai men, mi pataŋana sa irao ipasaana iti som.   
\b  
\q1
\v 24 Wal maolŋan naman isula timbiiri leleene be tipei kan kini.  
\q1 Tamen naman ipata be tiur ila kwon.   
\b  
\q1
\v 25 Zin wal ta tipakurkur zitun mi tirepilpiili ŋgar ambaiŋana na, sombe tabalis zin, ina ambai. Naso zin wal ta len ŋgar biibi som na tire mi ipei ŋgar kizin.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta ŋgar kizin ipet kek na, tabalis zin pepe. Toso men sua be tapazal zin. Pa zin ko tikam ŋgar. \x + \xo 19:25 \xt Mbo 141:5; Tut 21:11\x*   
\q1
\v 26 Pikin ta so imaŋga pa tamaana, mi iziiri naana ma ila lene pa ruumu,  
\q1 ina ni ipamiaŋ zin biibi kat. \x + \xo 19:26 \xt Kam 21:15; Tut 20:20\x*   
\q1
\v 27 Lutuŋ, nu sombe zeeze talŋom pa sua pazalŋana, ina ambai. Zeeze lak!  
\q1 Naso nu talli kat pa ŋgar ambaiŋana!   
\q1
\v 28 Sombe tomtom timender pa sua, mi takam wal sananŋan pakan ma timar be tipombol sua kizin, inako tepeŋeu sua urpeŋana tana ma iwe koroŋ sorok.  
\q1 Wal sananŋan lelen pa mbulu sananŋana ilip, kembei ta kini namutŋana.   
\q1
\v 29 Zin wal ta tipakurkur zitun mi tirepilpiili ŋgar ambaiŋana na, kadoono kizin inamnaama zin ma imbotmbot.  
\q1 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, tomtom ko tibalis zin ma ndemen berebere.   
\c 20  
\q1
\v 1 Tomtom ta so iwinin yok baen mi yok mbolŋana, nako kalŋaana izalla sorok mi ikamam mbulu bozboozo.  
\q1 Tana zin wal ta koroŋ ru tana iyaryaaru zin na, len ŋgar sa som. \x + \xo 20:1 \xt Tut 23:20-21; Ep 5:18\x*   
\q1
\v 2 Sombe king keteene malmal, ina ikamam ti ma tomototo kembei laion ta kalŋaana izalla be ikan tomtom.  
\q1 Pa tomtom ta so ipas king keteene, nako imeete.   
\q1
\v 3 Tomtom ta so iŋoŋooŋo som, nako uruunu ambai.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, zin ta boozomen karau men mi keten malmal ma tiŋoŋooŋo.   
\q1
\v 4 Sombe mazwaana ki kini paazaŋana ipet, na wal maolŋan tikamam uraata be tipaaza kan kini som.  
\q1 Tana mai ki kini isombe ipet, na tila tiru kan kini ma som.   
\q1
\v 5 Iti tomtom lelende, ina kembei yok ta ka li biibi. Pa ŋgar ta imbotmbot sula na, ka uunu biibi mi turkeŋana.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ŋgarŋana na, ni iute zaala tabe ikam ti ma teswe ŋgar kiti turkeŋana ma imbot mat.   
\q1
\v 6 Wal boozomen tizzo ta kembei: “Nio ti, aŋurur leleŋ pa Anutu mi zin tomtom mi aŋtoto sua tio mbukŋana.”  
\q1 Mi asiŋ irao indeeŋe tomtom sa ta ikamam mbulu ta kembei? Som. Tomtom sa ndemeereŋana som.   
\q1
\v 7 Wal ndeeŋeŋan tipa pai kizin ma ambai men.  
\q1 Tana kaimer lutun bizin ko lelen ambai kat, mi kampeŋana ki Anutu imbotmbot se kizin. \x + \xo 20:7 \xt Mbo 25:12-13, 112:1-2\x*   
\q1
\v 8 King mbuleene ise muriini peeze kana be iurpe pataŋana kizin tomtom.  
\q1 Ni le uraata be ipitpeleele zin tomtom. Ambaimbaiŋan tila ndel, sananŋan tila ndel.   
\q1
\v 9 Asiŋ irao iso ta kembei: “Nio motoŋ iŋgalŋgal ituŋ mi leleŋ iŋgeeze men. Nio ambaiŋoŋ, mi leŋ sanaana sa som.”  
\q1 Tomtom sa isombe iso sua ta kembei, ko sua kini ŋonoono? Som. \x + \xo 20:9 \xt Un 8:21; Mbo 51:1-5; Ro 3:23; 1Yo 1:8\x*   
\q1
\v 10 Iti sombe lelende be takam ŋgomo pa koroŋ sa, na Yooba leleene be tuur ka kadoono ma irao kat pa ka kin.  
\q1 Kokena tasala sorok pizin wal pakan, mi pakan na tusu pizin. Pa mbulu pakaamŋana ta kembei, Yooba leleene pa ri sa som kat. \x + \xo 20:10 \xt Tut 11:1, 16:11\x*   
\q1
\v 11 Mbulu kizin pikin ta izzwe zin.  
\q1 Sombe mbulu kizin ambai mi indeeŋe men, na zin pikin ambaimbaiŋan.   
\q1
\v 12 Yooba iur matanda be tere mi tikilaala.  
\q1 Mi iur talŋanda be teleŋ sua mi takam ŋgar pa. \x + \xo 20:12 \xt Mbo 94:9\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 13 Keene rimos! Kokena su ma mbot ŋoobo.  
\q1 Maŋga karau pa mankwoono mi kam uraata. Naso rao kat pa kom kini. \x + \xo 20:13 \xt Tut 6:9+, 19:15, 24:30-34\x*   
\q1
\v 14 Iti sombe takam mburooŋo pa koroŋ sa bekena kadoono isu, mi sombe mburooŋo kiti ila ambai,  
\q1 nako kaimer tala raama menmeen ti, mi tapakur itundu pa mburooŋo ta takam na.   
\q1
\v 15 Wal ta tizzo sua raama ŋgar na, zin boozo ŋan som. Tana iti sombe tendeeŋe lende tomtom sa ta kembei, ina koroŋ biibi.  
\q1 Pa wal ta kembei tilip pa gol mi pat milmilŋan ta kan kadon bibip na.   
\q1
\v 16 Waem sa, sombe imbuk sua pa tomtom toro ta ni iute i som na ma iso: “Sombe nu rao be kot mbun ku som, na nio ituŋ ko aŋmender pu mi aŋkot.” Ina ni ikam mbulu kankaanaŋana kat.  
\q1 Tana sombe ni iso pu be kam mbulu raraate men pini, na ndemeeri pepe. So pini be ikam koroŋ kini pakan ma imar imbot ku. Beso ni irao be ikot som, to koroŋ kini tana iwe lem.   
\q1
\v 17 Ŋonoono, kini ta so takam pa zaala ki pakaamŋana, sombe ila kwondo, ina inamut kat.  
\q1 Mi sombe takan ma isula kopondo, nako tayamaana ambai som. Ko kembei ta patpat! \x + \xo 20:17 \xt Tut 9:17, 10:2\x*   
\q1
\v 18 Sombe turru zaala pa koroŋ sa, na itundu men takam ŋgar pa pepe. Tiwi wal pakan be tiuulu iti pa ŋgar kizin tomini.  
\q1 Mi sombe malmal biibi sa ipet, to matanda iŋgal kat be takam lende wal pakan bekena tiso iti pa malmal ka zaala. \x + \xo 20:18 \xt Tut 11:14, 15:22, 24:6; Lu 14:31-32\x*   
\q1
\v 19 Wal ta tininin kao na, tizzwe sua turkeŋana ki waen bizin.  
\q1 Tana tomtom ta gorgori kwoono perper sorok na, nu mbotmbot molo pini: Kokena iswe sua ku ma wal pakan tileŋ. \x + \xo 20:19 \xt Tut 11:13, 25:9\x*   
\q1
\v 20 Tomtom ta so ipiri sua sananŋana pa tamaana som naana,  
\q1 nako imeete karau men. Ko iwe kembei lam ta tipunmeete mi lele zugut. \x + \xo 20:20 \xt Kam 21:17; Tut 30:17; Mt 15:4\x*   
\q1
\v 21 Rai koroŋ ku pa lutum bizin karau pepe.  
\q1 Kokena timboro kat som, to kampeŋana ki Anutu imbotmbot se koroŋ tana som. \x + \xo 20:21 \xt Tut 19:26; Lu 15:12-14\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 22 Sombe tomtom sa ikam mbulu sananŋana pu, na kam ŋgar be pokot pepe.  
\q1 Zem la Yooba namaana, mi ni ko iuulu u pa pataŋana ku tana. \x + \xo 20:22 \xt Mbo 27:14, 37:34; Ro 12:19; 1Tes 5:15\x*   
\q1
\v 23 Iti sombe lelende be takam ŋgomo pa koroŋ sa, na tuur ka kadoono ma irao kat pa ka kin. Kokena tasala sorok pizin wal pakan, mi pakan na tusu pizin.  
\q1 Pa mbulu pakaamŋana ta kembei, Yooba leleene pa ri sa som kat.   
\q1
\v 24 Yooba ta ikamam peeze pa pai kiti.  
\q1 Mbulu tabe ipet piti pa kaimer i, na asiŋ iute? Tomtom sa som. Yooba itutamen ta iute. \x + \xo 20:24 \xt Mbo 37:23, 90:12; Tut 16:9, 19:21\x*   
\q1
\v 25 Sombe tomtom sa ikam kat ŋgar som, mi imbuk sorok sua be iur koroŋ sa ma iwe Yooba lene, na ni iur kilis pa itunu.  
\q1 Pa kaimer sombe ŋgar kini itooro, na le zaala sa be ireege mini sua kini mbukŋana tana na som. \x + \xo 20:25 \xt Mt 15:5+\x*   
\q1
\v 26 King ta so le ŋgar ambaiŋana, nako ipitpeleele zin tomtom: Ambaimbaiŋan tila ndel, sananŋan tila ndel.  
\q1 Mi wal sananŋan na, ni ko ipun zin ma mburan imap.   
\q1
\v 27 Mat ki Yooba ta iyaryaara piti,  
\q1 mi izzwe ŋgar kiti turkeŋana ta imbotmbot sula lelende. \x + \xo 20:27 \xt Tut 16:2; 1Kor 2:10-11\x*   
\q1
\v 28 King sa isombe iurur leleene pa Anutu mi zin tomtom mi itoto sua kini mbukŋana, nako imbot ambai.  
\q1 Pa sombe iurur leleene pizin tomtom mi imuŋaiŋai zin, na peeze kini ko imbol ma imbotmbot.   
\q1
\v 29 Zin naŋgaŋ na, mburan biibi, tabe nin se pa.  
\q1 Mi zin kolman na, momo kizin ta iwe aigau pizin mi iswe zin kembei mbulu kizin iŋgeeze men. \x + \xo 20:29 \xt Tut 16:31\x*   
\q1
\v 30 Sombe tabalis zin wal sananŋan ma ruŋgun isaana,  
\q1 nako iurpe mbulu kizin, mi ipus zin ma lelen iŋgeeze.   
\c 21  
\q1
\v 1 Yooba ta imborro king leleene mi ikamam peeze pini.  
\q1 Tana king itoto Yooba leleene kembei ta yok itoto zalaana. \x + \xo 21:1 \xt Mbo 33:15-16\x*   
\q1
\v 2 Iti tomtom tendemeere kembei mbulu kiti ta boozomen indeeŋe men.  
\q1 Mi Yooba, ni itirtiiri lelende ma iute kat. \x + \xo 21:2 \xt Tut 16:2, 24:12; 1Kor 4:4-5; Ibr 4:12\x*   
\q1
\v 3 Sombe takamam mbulu ndeeŋeŋana men mi tuurpewe pataŋana kizin tomtom,  
\q1 na Yooba leleene pa mbulu ta kembei ma ilip pa patoronŋana matakiŋa ta tomtom tikamam pini na.   
\b  
\q1
\v 4 Wal sananŋan matan pasom zin tomtom mi tipakurkur zitun ma tiso tilip pizin.  
\q1 Gorgori ŋgar sananŋana tana ikamam peeze pizin. Tanata tinoknok sanaana kamŋana. \x + \xo 21:4 \xt Mbo 101:4-5\x*   
\q1
\v 5 Zin wal ta tikamam kat uraata raama ŋgar na, uraata kizin ilonloondo ambai mi iurur ŋonoono.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta gorgori tirru zaala be tindou len koroŋ boozo karau men, na uraata kizin ko iur ŋonoono som, mi tisu ma timbot ŋoobo. \x + \xo 21:5 \xt Tut 13:11, 28:20\x*   
\q1
\v 6 Sombe takam lende koroŋ boozo pa zaala ki pakaamŋana, na koroŋ tana ko irao imbot ma molo na som.  
\q1 Ko imap karau men kembei ta ŋauŋau, mi iwe kilis piti, mi ipasaana iti. \x + \xo 21:6 \xt Tut 10:2; Yems 5:1-5\x*   
\q1
\v 7 Wal sananŋan ta titekteege zaaba pizin tomtom na, mbulu kizin tana ko imiili pizin mi ipasaana zin.  
\q1 Pa zin lelen be tikam mbulu ndeeŋeŋana ri sa som.   
\q1
\v 8 Wal sananŋan tipaŋobŋoobo pa zaala ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Mi wal ndeeŋeŋan na, mbulu kizin iŋgeeze men.   
\b  
\q1
\v 9 Sombe kusim inoknok zooroŋana mi iŋoŋooŋo, na mbotmbot raami lela ruumu pepe.  
\q1 Ambai be zemi mi pera lem mat! \x + \xo 21:9 \xt Tut 19:13\x*   
\q1
\v 10 Wal sananŋan lelen pa mbulu sananŋana ilip.  
\q1 Mi irao timuŋai waen bizin pakan na som.   
\b  
\q1
\v 11 Zin wal ta tipakurkur zitun mi tirepilpiili ŋgar ambaiŋana na, sombe tire kadoono pa mbulu kizin, nako ipei ŋgar kizin wal ta len ŋgar biibi som na.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na, sombe tapaute zin, nako tikam len ŋgar pakan ma isala ki.   
\q1
\v 12 Anutu, ni ndeeŋeŋana, mi iute mbulu boozomen ta iwedet lela wal sananŋan ruumu kizin.  
\q1 Tanata ipasansaana zin.   
\b  
\q1
\v 13 Tomtom sa isombe izeeze talŋaana pa tiŋiizi kizin wal ta timbotmbot raama pataŋana na, kozo ire i.  
\q1 Pa kaimer sombe itaŋroro pa le ulaaŋa sa, nako irao tileŋi na som. \x + \xo 21:13 \xt Tut 22:8; Mt 18:23-34; 2Kor 9:6; Ga 6:7\x*   
\q1
\v 14 Sombe tomtom sa keteene malmal kat piti mi teseŋgeere le koroŋ ambaimbaiŋan pakan, nako tapaluumu leleene.  
\q1 Seŋgeeri ta so takam pini ki keŋana, nako iurpe leleene.   
\q1
\v 15 Sombe zin bibip tiurpewe pataŋana kizin tomtom, ina ikam zin wal ndeeŋeŋan ma lelen ambai kat.  
\q1 Tamen zin wal ta tikamam mbulu sananŋana na, tire ma timoto kan. \x + \xo 21:15 \xt Ro 13:3\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 16 Tomtom ta so isaŋsaŋ pa zaala ki ŋgar ambaiŋana,  
\q1 nako imeete ma ila igaaba zin wal meeteŋan.   
\q1
\v 17 Tomtom ta so leleene ilip be ikam le mbulu matakiŋa ta ki kulindi i, nako isu ma imbot ŋoobo.  
\q1 Mi sombe tomtom sa leleene ilip pa kini namutŋana mi yok baen, mi iwirri pat biibi pa, na ni ko irao iwe mbio uunu na som. \x + \xo 21:17 \xt Tut 23:20-21; Lu 15:13+\x*   
\q1
\v 18 Pataŋana tabe ikam zin wal ndeeŋeŋan mi zin wal tau tikamam kat mbulu i, ina Yooba ipiŋgisŋgis pizin, mi ilala ma ikamam zin wal sananŋan mi zin wal pakamkaamŋan tau tisu mini mi tiur koi pa zitun wal kizin na.   
\b  
\q1
\v 19 Sombe kusim inoknok zooroŋana mi iŋoŋooŋo, na mbotmbot raami lela ruumu pepe.  
\q1 Ambai be zemi mi la mbomboorem lele bilimŋana sa. \x + \xo 21:19 \xt Tut 25:25\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 20 Zin wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na, ruumu kizin bok pa koroŋ ndabokbokŋan matakiŋa.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, tirao be tiyaraama zitun som. Tana tipasansaana koroŋ kizin ta boozomen pa koroŋ soroksorok.   
\q1
\v 21 Tomtom ta so ikamam kinkiini be ito zaala ndeeŋeŋana mi iurur leleene pizin tomtom,  
\q1 nako ikam mbotŋana ambaiŋana, mi zaana iwe biibi, mi iwe tomtom ndeeŋeŋana. \x + \xo 21:21 \xt Mt 5:6\x*   
\q1
\v 22 Ŋonoono, kar pakan wal mburanŋan. Mi tomtom ta le ŋgar ambaiŋana na, ni ko irao be ikam malmal pizin mi ireege siiri kizin mbolŋana ta tipase pa na. \x + \xo 21:22 \xt Tut 23:5; 2Kor 10:4\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 23 Sombe lelem be pataŋana ikamu som,  
\q1 na motom iŋgalŋgal be mboro kat kwom! \x + \xo 21:23 \xt Tut 13:3\x*   
\q1
\v 24 Zin wal ta tizorzooro mi tipasomsom zin tomtom, na tawatwaata zin be wal matan repiiliŋan.  
\q1 Wal ta kembei timbel pakurŋana. Pa tiso tilip pizin tomtom ta boozomen.   
\b  
\q1
\v 25 Wal maolŋan lelen ilip be tikam len koroŋ.  
\q1 Tamen naman ikamam uraata som. Tana tiru zaala pakan be tikam len koroŋ, mi ina ipasaana zin ma timeete.   
\q1
\v 26 Zoŋ ise ma ila zoŋ isula na, wal maolŋan timbombooren, mi ŋgar kizin ilala pa koroŋ boozomen ta lelen pa i.  
\q1 Mi wal ndeeŋeŋan na, tirairai koroŋ kizin pakan pizin wal sorrokŋan. Tirutruutu som. \x + \xo 21:26 \xt Mbo 37:26, 112:5; Ep 4:28\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 27 Patoronŋana kizin wal sananŋan na, Anutu leleene pa ri sa som.  
\q1 Mi re beso tikam patoronŋana kizin raama ŋgar sananŋana sa, na ni leleene pa ri sa som kat! \x + \xo 21:27 \xt Tut 15:8\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 28 Tomtom ta so ipombol sua pakaamŋana, nako ila lene.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ileŋleŋ kat sua, nako tomtom lelen be tiŋgun talŋan pa sua kini.   
\q1
\v 29 Wal sananŋan, nin zze mi tipakurkur zitun kembei timoto kosasa som.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tikamam kat mbulu na, matan iŋgalŋgal zitun be tito zaala ambaiŋana men.   
\b  
\q1
\v 30 Ŋgar sa, som sua sa, som koroŋ toro sa irao ilip pa Yooba na som. \x + \xo 21:30 \xt Tut 16:9, 19:21; 1Kor 3:18-20\x*   
\q1
\v 31 Sombe malmal sa be ipet, nako taparaŋraŋ lende mburu malmal kana.  
\q1 Mi tilip, som tilip som, ina koroŋ ki Yooba. Ni itunu ta imborro. \x + \xo 21:31 \xt Mbo 3:8, 33:16+, 147:10+\x*   
\c 22  
\q1
\v 1 Tomtom lelen pa gol ma silba mi koroŋ ndabokbokŋan pakan.  
\q1 Tamen sombe urundu ambai mi tomtom lelen piti, ina ilip kat pa koroŋ ta boozomen tana.   
\b  
\q1
\v 2 Yooba iur tomtom ta boozomen raraate men.  
\q1 Zin mbio uunu ta len koroŋ boozo, mi zin wal ta sorrokŋan na tomini.   
\q1
\v 3 Tomtom ŋgarŋana, ni irao iur itunu ila zaaba kwoono sorok na som. Sombe ikilaala kembei pataŋana sa be ipet, na loŋa men mi iru zaala be iko pa.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta len ŋgar biibi som na, tikilaala som. Tila men. Tabe tindeeŋe pataŋana.   
\q1
\v 4 Iti sombe tokototo itundu, mi tomototo Yooba mi teleŋleŋ la kalŋaana,  
\q1 nako lende koroŋ boozo, mi urundu ambai, mi mbotŋana kiti ambai.   
\q1
\v 5 Zaala ta wal sananŋan titoto, ina ipata. Pa worwooro matanmatanŋan mi kilis boozomen imbotmbot la.  
\q1 Tana tomtom ta so mataana iŋgalŋgal itunu, nako imbotmbot molo pa zaala kizin.   
\b  
\q1
\v 6 Paute lutum pa zaala tabe ito i.  
\q1 Naso itum raama ŋgar ambaiŋana, mi ikiskis ma irao iwe kolman. Irao izem na som. \x + \xo 22:6 \xt  Tut 4:10-13; Ep 6:4\x*   
\q1
\v 7 Wal sorrokŋan tileŋleŋ la zin mbio uunu kalŋan. Irao tizooro zin na som.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ikam mbun, nako iwe kembei mbesooŋo sorok pa tomtom ta iuuli na.   
\q1
\v 8 Mbulu sananŋana ta tomtom tiwaswaaza, ina kaimer ipiyotyooto pataŋana pizin.  
\q1 Tona mburan imap, mi tirao be tipasaana zin tomtom mini som. \x + \xo 22:8 \xt  Tut 12:21; Ga 6:7\x*   
\q1
\v 9 Tomtom ta mata merereŋana, nako indeeŋe kampeŋana.  
\q1 Paso irairai kini mi koroŋ kini pakan pizin wal sorrokŋan.   
\q1
\v 10 Zin wal ta tizorzooro mi tirepilpiili ŋgar ambaiŋana na, ziiri zin ma tila len.  
\q1 Naso mbulu ki zooroŋana, ŋoŋi, mi repiiliŋana imap. \x + \xo 22:10 \xt  Tut 26:20+\x*   
\q1
\v 11 Tomtom ta so leleene ŋgeezeŋana mi ikamam sua ambaiŋana men,  
\q1 nako king itunu leleene pini mi ikami ma iwe le gaabaŋana. \x + \xo 22:11 \xt  Mbo 24:4; Mt 5:8\x*   
\q1
\v 12 Yooba itunu ta mataana pa ŋgar ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Mi zin wal pakamkaamŋan tau tisu mini mi tiur koi pa zitun wal kizin na, ni ikamam ma sua kizin iurur ŋonoono som.   
\q1
\v 13 Wal maolŋan, sombe toso pizin be tila tikam uraata, na tipandelndel sua piti ta kembei: “Aiss, nio mburoŋ som. Ko aŋdeeŋe laion sa isu zaala lwoono mi ikan yo, som wal sananŋan tipun yo ma aŋmeete ma iŋgi.”  
\q1 Tana tila pa uraata som.   
\q1
\v 14 Zin moori ta tiyaryaaru zin tomooto na, sua kizin kembei naala ta isula kat.  
\q1 Mi wal ta Yooba kete malmalŋana kini imbotmbot se kizin ta titoptop sula. \x + \xo 22:14 \xt  Tut 5:3-5, 7:25+, 23:27\x*   
\q1
\v 15 Zin naŋgaŋ lelen bok pa ŋgar talliŋana.  
\q1 Mi sombe taballis zin mi tapazalzal zin, nako ŋgar kizin talliŋana tana imap pizin. \x + \xo 22:15 \xt  Tut 13:24, 19:18, 23:13\x*   
\q1
\v 16 Tomtom ta so iur pataŋana pizin wal sorrokŋan bekena ikoto zin mi ikam koroŋ kizin ma iwe lene,  
\q1 som ipomosmoozo zin wal mbio uunu, na kaimer ni ko isu ma imbot ŋoobo.   
\s1 Sua tutŋan tomoota laamuru  
\q1
\v 17-18 Zin wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na, ŋgun talŋom pizin mi leŋleŋ la sua kizin.  
\q1 Mi ŋgar ta so nio aŋpaute u pa i, na kiskis ma imbol la lelem.  
\q1 Pa nu so kam ta kembei, nako ikamu ma lelem ambai.  
\q1 Mi ko irao ru zolom pa sua sa na som.   
\q1
\v 19 Nio leleŋ be nu tina pase pa Yooba.  
\q1 Tanata koozi aŋpaute u pa ŋgar ti.   
\q1
\v 20 Nio aŋso aŋpaute u pa sua ŋgarŋana tabe ikam peeze pu i.  
\q1 Tana lem sua tomoota mi laamuru ta iŋgi be ima i.   
\q1
\v 21 Sua tabe aŋpaute u pa i, ina sua ŋonoono men. Nu irao pase pa kat.  
\q1 Tana nu sombe miili ma la kizin wal tau tiŋgo u ma mar na, nu irao swe ŋgar tiŋgi pizin. Pa ina ŋonoono men.   
\s1 1  
\q1
\v 22 Ŋonoono, wal sorrokŋan, len mburan biibi be tiporoukaala zitun som. Tamen nu irao pamoto zin sorok mi kem koroŋ kizin pepe.  
\q1 Mi sombe timender pa sua, na koto zin sorok pepe. Tiiri kat sua kizin, mi urpe ma indeeŋe men.   
\q1
\v 23 Pa tomtom sa isombe iyo sorok koroŋ kizin wal sorrokŋan,  
\q1 na Yooba itunu ko imender pizin mi itatke koroŋ kizin tana pini. \x + \xo 22:23 \xt  Kam 22:22-27, 23:6,7; Mbo 12:5, 140:12; Yems 2:5-6\x*   
\s1 2  
\q1
\v 24-25 Tomtom ta so leleene tataŋa mi keteene malmal karau men,  
\q1 na we toroono pepe, gabgaabi pepe.  
\q1 Kokena ikeske u pa mbulu kini, to iwe kilis pu. \x + \xo 22:24-25 \xt  Tut 12:13; 1Kor 15:33; Ep 5:6-7\x*   
\s1 3  
\q1
\v 26 Mi sombe tomtom sa leleene be ikam mbun, tana iwi u be uuli mi mbuk sua mbolŋana ta kembei: “Sombe ni irao ikot mbun kini som, na nio ko aŋmender pini mi aŋkot.”  
\q1 Na nu yok pa sua kini tana pepe.   
\q1
\v 27 Pa kaimer sombe nu rao be kot mbun kini som, nako tiniimi koroŋ ku ta boozomen ma imap.  
\q1 Itum mbalia ku ta kenne pa i, ina tomini, ko tikam ma tila!   
\s1 4  
\q1
\v 28 Toono ka kambasa ta tumbundu bizin tiur ta muŋgu kek na, tisiri pepe.   
\s1 5  
\q1
\v 29 Re la pizin wal ta tirao kat pa uraata kizin. Wal ta kembei ko irao tikam uraata pizin tomtom sorok na som.  
\q1 Pa zin king ko lelen pizin mi tikam zin pa uraata kizin. \x + \xo 22:29 \xt  Un 39:2-4, 41:39-40\x*   
\c 23  
\s1 6  
\q1
\v 1 Sombe tomtom peeze kana sa iluŋke u ma la be niomru mbuleyom su pa kini kanŋana, na kam kat ŋgar pa kini tana ka uunu muŋgu, mana kan. Pa ni iboobu sorok som.   
\q1
\v 2 Mi sombe nu motom kiniŋom, na rre be yaraama itum   
\q1
\v 3 Kokena kini namtuŋana tana ikam motom, to kan sorok.  
\q1 Pa kini tana na, ka zaala pakaamŋana sa ko imbotmbot. \x + \xo 23:3 \xt  Mbo 141:4\x*   
\s1 7  
\q1
\v 4 Nu lem ŋgar. Tana pun kat mburom be we mbio uunu pepe.  
\q1 Ŋonoono, nu lelem be kam koroŋ boozo. Tamen yaraama itum.   
\q1
\v 5 Pa koroŋ boozomen ta tomtom tindoundou isu toono na, ina imapmap karau men. Ina kembei koroŋ ta terre la pa, mi matanda kolom na, ila ne kek.  
\q1 Nu so koroŋ ku tana ko imbotmbot ma molo? Som. Ko kembei ta manboŋ. Itir begeene na, irie ma ila ne kek! \x + \xo 23:5 \xt  Tut 27:24; Mt 6:19; 1Tim 6:6-10; Ibr 13:5\x*   
\s1 8  
\q1
\v 6 Zin wal ta so tikampewe zin tomtom som na, ŋgurem kutkut pa kini kizin pepe.  
\q1 Ŋonoono, kini ambaimbaiŋan matakiŋa imbotmbot se mbalia kizin be kan.  
\q1 Mi kini tana ikam motom pepe.   
\q1
\v 7 Pa wal ta kembei, gorgori tikamam ŋgar biibi pa pat kizin ta tipasansaana pa kini na.  
\q1 Ŋonoono, kwon na, tiso pu be kan ma win. Mi tiur kat lelen pu som.   
\q1
\v 8 Tana kini ri ta so kan, na kaimer ko lulu.  
\q1 Mi sua pakurŋana ta so kam pizin pa kini tana, na nu so sorok. Pa kaimer zin ko tikam kosasa pu mini som.   
\s1 9  
\q1
\v 9 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, la kizin ma niomŋan koso sua pepe.  
\q1 Pa sua ŋgarŋana ta so kam pizin, na zin ko tirepiili kembei koroŋ sorok. \x + \xo 23:9 \xt  Tut 1:7, 9:7-8, 12:1; Mt 7:6\x*   
\s1 10  
\q1
\v 10 Toono ka kambasa tau tiur ta muŋgu kek na, siri pepe.  
\q1 Mi sei lem toono kizin monmoondo pepe.   
\q1
\v 11 Pa zin len Tomtom Mburaanaŋana ta imbotmbot be imenderkaala zin.  
\q1 Sombe niomru kakam sua, ko rao? \x + \xo 23:11 \xt  Kam 22:22-23; Mbo 10:14, 12:5, 68:5, 146:7,9\x*   
\s1 11  
\q1
\v 12 Sua pazalŋana ta so tikam pu, na kiskis ma imbol la lelem.  
\q1 Mi sua ta izzwe ŋgar ambaiŋana na, ŋgungun talŋom pa.   
\s1 12  
\q1
\v 13 Sombe lutum sa ikamam ŋoobo mbulu, na leeli pepe. Kam ke mi balisi pa bekena pazali.  
\q1 Kam ŋgar boozo pepe. Ni ko irao imeete na som.   
\q1
\v 14 Tana balisi.  
\q1 Naso kamke i pa zaala ki meeteŋana. \x + \xo 23:14 \xt  Tut 13:24, 19:18, 22:15\x*   
\s1 13  
\q1
\v 15 O lutuŋ, sombe nu kiskis ŋgar ambaiŋana ila lelem,  
\q1 nako kam ma leleŋ ambai kat.   
\q1
\v 16 Mi sombe sua ndeeŋeŋana men iwedet pa kwom,  
\q1 nako leleŋ ndabok kat.   
\s1 14  
\q1
\v 17 Zin wal ta mbulu kizin irao pa Anutu mataana som na, motom berber pizin pepe.  
\q1 Zoŋ ise ma ila zoŋ isula na, mototo Yooba mi leŋleŋ la kalŋaana.   
\q1
\v 18 Naso mbot ambai,  
\q1 mi koroŋ ambaiŋana ta urur motom pa i, nako kam. \x + \xo 23:18 \xt  Mbo 37:1-4,37, 73:2+\x*   
\s1 15  
\q1
\v 19 O lutuŋ, leŋ la sua tio ti. Naso we tomtom ŋgarŋom.  
\q1 Mi motom iŋgalŋgal be to kat zaala ambaiŋana.   
\q1
\v 20 Zin wal ta tiwinin yok baen ma zaza na, mbotmbot raama zin pepe.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tikanan saaba kini na, gabgaaba zin pepe.   
\q1
\v 21 Pa wal ta kembei tikamam uraata som mi gorgori tikenne len sorok.  
\q1 Tana kaimer zin ko tisu ma timbot ŋoobo, mi tizebzeebe zin pa mburu marrazaŋana men. \x + \xo 23:21 \xt  Tut 21:17\x*   
\s1 16  
\q1
\v 22 Tomom ta iuru. Tana leŋleŋ la kalŋaana.  
\q1 Mi sombe nom iwe kolman ma isaana, na motom pasomi pepe. \x + \xo 23:22 \xt  Tut 15:20, 30:17\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 23 Re: Kokena ziiri sua ŋonoono ma ila ne.  
\q1 Kam kinkiini pa sua ŋonoono mi ŋgar ambaimbaiŋan matakiŋa bekena kam ma iwe lem.   
\q1
\v 24 Pikin ta so ikamam mbulu ndeeŋeŋana, nako tamaana menmeeni biibi pini.  
\q1 Mi sombe ikam le ŋgar ambaiŋana, nako tamaana leleene pini ilip.   
\q1
\v 25 Motom iŋgal mbulu tabe ikam ma tomom ma nom lelen ambai.  
\q1 Kam mbulu ambaiŋana. Naso nom ta ipeebu na menmeeni biibi.   
\s1 17  
\q1
\v 26 O lutuŋ, ur kat lelem pio.  
\q1 Mi motom iŋgalŋgal be to zaala tio.   
\q1
\v 27 Kozo re u pizin moori zaala lwoono kan mi zin tau tiurur nol na.  
\q1 Pa zin kembei naala ta isula kat.   
\q1
\v 28 Gorgori tizaŋzaaŋa zin tomooto kembei zin wal kuumbuŋan.  
\q1 Mi tikamam ma tomooto boozomen tirekreege sua kizin mbukŋana mi tipasansaana ula kizin.   
\s1 18 (Mbulu kizin wal ta tiwinin)  
\q1
\v 29 Ziŋoi ta len pataŋana boozomen mi tiyakyak?  
\q1 Mi ziŋoi ta timbotmbot raama ŋoŋi mi tomtom tiyyo kwon pizin?  
\q1 Mi ziŋoi ta kulin berebere sorok, mi matan uunu isiŋsiŋ?   
\q1
\v 30 Ina zin wal ta tizemzem yok baen winŋana som,  
\q1 mi lelen be titoombo yok mbolŋan matakiŋa.   
\q1
\v 31 Ŋonoono, yok baen ku tana isiŋsiŋ kat.  
\q1 Yok ta imbotmbot sula mbooro ku na, ambai kat be rre lem.  
\q1 Mi sombe win, na ikamam ŋgurem.   
\q1
\v 32 Tamen kaimer ko ikanu kembei ta mooto.  
\q1 Mi ipasaanu kembei mooto sananŋana ta ikanan zin tomtom ma timetmeete i.   
\q1
\v 33 Ŋgar ku ko ikankaana,  
\q1 mi nu ko re koroŋ pakan ta ipa ndel.   
\q1
\v 34 Mi keeneŋana ku ko kembei mbotmbot sala wooŋgo,  
\q1 mi duubu ipiri u ma la kena, la kena.   
\q1
\v 35 Mi ko kam sua ta kembei: “Aiss, tipun yo ma ruŋguŋ isaana.  
\q1 Tamen iŋgi kuliŋ iyoyou som, mi aŋyamaana kosasa som.  
\q1 Tana karau men mi motoŋ ikam pak, mi aŋla aŋru koŋ yok mbolŋana sa be aŋwin mini!”   
\c 24  
\s1 19  
\q1
\v 1 Wal sananŋan na, motom berber pizin pepe,  
\q1 tikam lelem pepe, mi gabgaaba zin pepe.   
\q1
\v 2 Pa wal ta kembei lelen be tikamam zaaba pizin tomtom.  
\q1 Gorgori tiluplup zin mi timburmbuuru pizin tomtom.   
\s1 20  
\q1
\v 3 Sombe ŋgar kiti ipet mi takam ŋgar ambaiŋana ma iwe lende, nako tuurpe mbulu kiti mi mboti kiti.  
\q1 Naso itiŋan wal kiti tombot ambai. Ko kembei topo lende ruumu ambaiŋana be tombot lela.   
\q1
\v 4 Pa ŋgar ta iwe zaala piti be ruumu kiti bok pa koroŋ ambaimbaiŋan mi ndabokbokŋan matakiŋa ta kan kadon bibip i.   
\s1 21  
\q1
\v 5 Tomtom ta le ŋgar ambaiŋana na, ni ilip pizin wal ta len mburan biibi na.  
\q1 Gorgori wal ŋgarŋan mburan izze.   
\q1
\v 6 Iti sombe lelende be takam malmal, na turu zin wal ŋgarŋan be tikam peeze piti mi tiso iti pa malmal ka zaala.  
\q1 Pa bela wal boozo tiuulu iti pa ŋgar kizin, tona tilip pa kanda koi bizin. \x + \xo 24:6 \xt Tut 11:14, 15:22, 21:22\x*   
\s1 22  
\q1
\v 7 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, tikam kinkiini pa ŋgar ambaiŋana. Mi tirao som.  
\q1 Tana sombe tomtom tilup zin pa sua, na wal kankaanaŋan len sua sa som. Timaane men.   
\s1 23  
\q1
\v 8 Tomtom ta so gorgori irru zaala be ikam mbulu sananŋana, nako tipaati be pakaamŋana katuunu.   
\q1
\v 9 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, sombe tirru zaala pa koroŋ sa, na ŋgar kizin ilala pa zaala sananŋan men.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tipakurkur zitun mi tirepilpiili ŋgar ambaiŋana na, tomtom lelen pizin ri sa som kat.   
\s1 24  
\q1
\v 10 Sombe nu mbotmbot la pataŋana sa leleene mi mburom imap, na nu tomtom ŋonoono som.  
\q1 Pa zin wal ta tomtom ŋonoono na, timendernder mbolŋana mi tirao be tibaada pataŋana. \x + \xo 24:10 \xt Ga 6:9\x*   
\s1 25  
\q1
\v 11 Zin wal ta len uunu sa som, mi kan koi bizin tikam zin sorok ma tila be tipun zin ma timeete na, re be tatke zin la kan koi bizin naman.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta titoto zaala ki meeteŋana mi sursur ma tila na, karau men la mi kamke zin.   
\q1
\v 12 Kokena pakaam ma so: “Wai, mi mbulu ta iwedet pizin na, niam ti amute som.”  
\q1 Pa Anutu, ni irre iti tomtom lelende ma imap. Tana mbulu ta kam na, ni iute kek.  
\q1 Pa Ni ta imborro u na, ikankaana pu som.  
\q1 Mi ni kola iur kadoono piti tomtom tataŋa ikot mbulu kiti kiti. \x + \xo 24:12 \xt Mbo 82:3-4, 94:9-11; Tut 31:8-9; Ro 2:6\x*   
\s1 26  
\q1
\v 13 O lutuŋ, win bigil suruunu. Pa ina koroŋ ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Sombe win, na inamut kat.   
\q1
\v 14 Mi ŋgar ambaiŋana ta kembena. Nio leleŋ be nu ute kat ta kembei: Sombe kam ma iwe lem, nako yamaana ambai.  
\q1 Pa sombe ndeeŋe ŋgar ambaiŋana, na kaimer ko mbot ambai.  
\q1 Swom ko irao imap karau na som. Tana koroŋ ambaiŋana ta urur motom pa i, nako mbotmbot mi re kat ka ŋonoono. \x + \xo 24:14 \xt Yems 1:5, 3:13,17-18\x*   
\s1 27  
\q1
\v 15 Nu tomtom sananŋom, zaŋzaaŋa zin wal ndeeŋeŋan su ruumu kizin pepe.  
\q1 Mi petepaala ruumu kizin mi kem koroŋ kizin pepe.   
\q1
\v 16 Pa sombe tomtom ndeeŋeŋana sa itop, nako imaŋga mini. Ni irao itop pa lamata mi ru. Mi toŋgo. Ni kola imaŋga mini.  
\q1 Mi zin wal sananŋan na som. Sombe pataŋana sa ikam zin ma tisu, na tisu timbot pataaŋa. \x + \xo 24:16 \xt Mbo 34:19, 37:24; 2Tim 3:10-11\x*   
\s1 28  
\q1
\v 17 Kom koi sa, sombe pataŋana ikami, na menmeenu pepe.  
\q1 Mi sombe itop, na nim se pepe.   
\q1
\v 18 Kokena Yooba ire mbulu ku tana,  
\q1 to kete malmalŋana kini ikam kat kom koi tana som.   
\s1 29  
\q1
\v 19 Zin wal sananŋan na, tipas ketem pepe, mi motom berber pizin pepe.  
\q1 Kokena tikam ma ŋgar ku isaana.   
\q1
\v 20 Pa kaimer zin ko irao timbot ambai na som.  
\q1 Anutu ko iyembut swon ma timeete karau men, kembei lam ta tupunmeete na. \x + \xo 24:20 \xt Mbo 37:1-2, 38\x*   
\s1 30  
\q1
\v 21 O lutuŋ, mototo Yooba ziru king, mi leŋleŋ la kalŋan.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta so tizorzooro la Yooba ziru king kalŋan, na mbotmbot molo pizin.   
\q1
\v 22 Pa molo som to, wal ru tana tipamorsop zin wal zorzooroŋan pa pataŋana sa.  
\q1 Mi zaala tabe tipasaana zin pa i, ina tuute som. \x + \xo 24:22 \xt Ro 13:1-7; 1Pe 2:17\x*   
\s1 Sua pakan kizin wal ŋgarŋan  
\q1
\v 23 Iŋgi sua pakan kizin wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na.  
\b  
\q1 Sombe iti lende uraata be tuurpe pataŋana kizin tomtom, na titiiri kat sua kizin. Kokena talae sorok kizin wal pakan. Pa ina mbulu ambai som.   
\q1
\v 24 Biibi ta so itirtiiri kat sua som, mi iso pizin wal ta tikamam ŋoobo mbulu na ta kembei: “Nio aŋre kembei leyom uunu sa isaana som.”  
\q1 Na biibi ta kembei, iwal biibi ko keten malmal pini, mi tigiibi sua sananŋana pini.   
\q1
\v 25 Mi zin bibip ta tiurur kat kadoono pizin wal sananŋan ma ikot mbulu kizin,  
\q1 inako timbot ambai, mi kampeŋana ki Anutu imbotmbot se kizin.   
\b  
\q1
\v 26 Sombe tomtom sa iso kat sua pu,  
\q1 ina iswe i kembei ni torom ŋonoono mi iurur kat leleene pu.   
\b  
\q1
\v 27 Paaza lem koroŋ, kam uraata pa mokleene ma imap, mi po lem ruumu, mana woolo.  
\q1 Naso niomŋan wal ku kombot ambai.   
\b  
\q1
\v 28 Sombe tipamender tomtom sa, na ŋgal sorok sua pini pepe,  
\q1 mi kwom pakaam pepe.   
\q1
\v 29 Re: Kokena nu so ta kembei: “A buri! Mbulu ta ni ikam pio, ta iŋgi be kadoono aŋpokot.  
\q1 Nio ko aŋkam mbulu raraate men pini, kembei ta ni ikam pio.” Na mbulu ta kembei, kam pepe. \x + \xo 24:29 \xt Tut 14:5, 20:22; Mt 5:38-44; 1Pe 3:9\x*   
\s1 Mbulu kizin wal maolŋan  
\q1
\v 30 Aigule ta na, nio aŋwwa ma aŋla mi aŋre la pa tomtom ta mokleene mi baen lene kini.  
\q1 Tomtom tana, ni maolŋana mi ŋgar somŋana.   
\q1
\v 31 Worwooro matanmatanŋan mi mbutmbuutu sananŋan ise pa mokleene kini mi ilol ma imap.  
\q1 Mi siiri ta iliu lele kini tana na, borok su lene lup.   
\q1
\v 32 To aŋkam ŋgar pa mbulu ta aŋre na,  
\q1 mi ŋgar tio ipet.   
\q1
\v 33 Iti sombe namanda mburanda pa uraata som,  
\q1 mi tuurur matanda ri, tekenene lende ri, tombomboorende ri,   
\q1
\v 34 na molo som, to tusu ma tombot ŋoobo kat.  
\q1 Koroŋ kiti ko imap kat, kembei tomtom kuumbuŋana sa iyo lup ma ila ne.   
\c 25  
\s1 Sua tutŋana pakan ki King Salumo  
\q1
\v 1 Iŋgi sua tutŋana mi sua tooroŋan pakan ki King Salumo. Hezekia, king ta imborro lele pakaana ki Yudea na, wal uraata kan kini ta tibeede sua ti ise ro na.   
\b  
\q1
\v 2 Anutu, ni ikamam zaana biibi pa mbulu kini pakan ta turkeŋan na.  
\q1 Mi zin king na, zan iwe biibi paso, tirao be tipeeze koroŋ turkeŋan. \x + \xo 25:2 \xt Ro 11:33-36\x*  
\v 3 Mbulu ta iwedet pa kar saamba, som sula kat toono leleene na, asiŋ irao iute? Som.  
\q1 Mi ina raraate pa ŋgar ta imbotmbot la king leleene na. Tomtom toro sa irao iute na som.   
\q1
\v 4 Sombe tikam pat silba ka muk ma ila ne, to silba tana iŋgeeze,  
\q1 mi tirao be tiurpe ma iwe koroŋ ambaiŋana.   
\q1
\v 5 Mi ina raraate men pizin wal sananŋan. Sombe tatatke zin pa king kereene uunu ma tila len,  
\q1 to king ikam mbulu ndeeŋeŋana men mi peeze kini imbol. \x + \xo 25:5 \xt Tut 16:12, 20:8,28\x*  
\v 6 Sombe mbotmbot raama king, na pakur itum pepe,  
\q1 mi serseere be gaaba zin bibip pakan pepe.   
\q1
\v 7 Kokena kaimer king iseru ma la lem, to kom miaŋ biibi ila matan.  
\q1 Tana mbotmbot mi namnaama. Sombe king itunu iboobu be sala kini, tona la. Zaala ta kembei, ina ambai ma ilip. \x + \xo 25:7 \xt Lu 14:8-11 \x*  
\v 8 Sombe nu re waem sa ikam ŋoobo mbulu, na loŋa pamenderi ila zin bibip matan pepe. Mbot mi kam kat ŋgar muŋgu.  
\q1 Pa sombe sua ku ila ma ambai som, mi waem tana ilip, nako kom miaŋ biibi.  
\q1 Manako kam so? \x + \xo 25:8 \xt Tut 17:14, 24:28; Mt 5:25\x*  
\v 9 Sombe nu niomru waem sa koŋooŋo, na koŋooŋo lak!  
\q1 Mi re: Kokena kwom iyabakes pa wal pakan sua kizin turkeŋan. \x + \xo 25:9 \xt Tut 11:13, 20:19\x*  
\v 10 Pa sombe zitun tileŋ, nako tipamiaŋu ma urum isaana kat.  
\q1 Kaimer urum ko irao ambai mini na som.   
\b  
\q1
\v 11 Tomtom sa isombe iso sua ma sua kini itop la kat, na tere kembei ambai.  
\q1 Ina kembei aigau milmilŋana ta tiurpe pa gol ma silba na. \x + \xo 25:11 \xt Tut 15:23\x*  
\v 12 Tomtom ta le ŋgar ambaiŋana na, isombe ipazal tomtom sa mi tomtom tana ileŋ la kalŋaana, na tere kembei ambai.  
\q1 Ina tomini kembei aigau milmilŋana ta tiurpe pa gol na. \x + \xo 25:12 \xt Tut 1:9, 3:22, 4:9, 15:31 \x*  
\v 13 Sombe zin bibip tiŋgo mbesooŋo kizin tasa ma ila pa uraata sa, mi ni ikam kat uraata tana,  
\q1 inako zin bibip kini lelen ambai kat mi tiso: “Ulei,”  
\q1 kembei wal uraata kan ta keten su mi tiwin kan yok lomoŋana na. \x + \xo 25:13 \xt Tut 13:17\x*  
\v 14 Tomtom ta so ipakurkur itunu sorok pa kampeŋana kini, mi tamen ikamam koroŋ pizin tomtom som,  
\q1 ina ni kembei miiri tiene ta igabgap ma imar ila ne, mi yaŋ sa isu som. \x + \xo 25:14 \xt Yud 12 \x*  
\v 15 Sombe zin bibip ŋgar kizin imbol kat pa koroŋ sa mi nu lelem be tooro ŋgar kizin, na toombo be kam sua riŋariŋa men pizin.  
\q1 Pa sombe nim gesges som, mi noknok men sua luumuŋana pizin, nako kam ma tileŋ la kalŋom. \x + \xo 25:15 \xt Tut 14:29, 15:1; Lu 18:1-5 \x*  
\v 16 Nu sombe ndeeŋe bigil suruunu, na win ma zaza pepe.  
\q1 Kokena ipasaana kopom, to lulu.   
\q1
\v 17 Mi waem bizin ta kembena. Lala taparpaara pa ruumu kizin pepe.  
\q1 Kokena pagesges zin, to kam ma lelen be tire u mini som.   
\b  
\q1
\v 18 Tomtom ta so iŋgal sorok sua pakaamŋana pa waene toro,  
\q1 ina sua kini ko ipasaana waene toro tana kembei zaaba, buza, o peene lutuunu mataanaŋana. \x + \xo 25:18 \xt Kam 20:16; Mbo 59:7\x*  
\v 19 Re. Sombe zoŋondo iyoyou, ko tarao be takan kini? Mi sombe kumbundu imbekes, ko tarao be temender se? Som.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta ndemeereŋan som na, ta kembena. Irao tapase pizin pa mazwaana ki pataŋana na som.   
\q1
\v 20 Mi parei? Sombe lele ilomo kat, mi waem sa ikoto i pa kawaala, mi nu la ma tatke pini, ko leleene ambai? Som.  
\q1 Mi sombe lombo ise mbeete ku keteene, \f + \fr 25:20 \ft Iburu iso ta kembei: “Sombe tuur vinegar ise mbeete, ko ambai?” Vinegar, ina koroŋ ta iyes ti. Tana iŋgi ampekel vinegar pa lombo. Pa tomtom boozo tiute vinegar som.\f*  
\m ko lelem ambai? Som kat!  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta timbot la pataŋana leleene na, ta kembena. Sombe kalŋanda izalla mi tombombo lende mboe mi zin tileŋ, nako tapasaana lelen. \x + \xo 25:20 \xt Mbo 137:1-4; Ro 12:15\x*   
\p
\v 21 Sombe kom koi sa peteli, na kam ka kini.  
\q1 Mi so miri i, na kam ka yok. \x + \xo 25:21 \xt Kam 23:4-5; Mt 5:44; Ro 12:20\x*  
\v 22 Naso kami ma ka miaŋ biibi pa mbulu ta ni ikam pu na,  
\q1 mi Yooba ikam lem kadoono ambaiŋana.   
\b  
\q1
\v 23 Sombe taŋgal sorok sua pakaamŋana pizin tomtom,  
\q1 inako tapas keten mi zurun imbukmbuk piti, kembei ta re ipol mi ipei miiri ma duubu.   
\b  
\q1
\v 24 Sombe kusim inoknok zooroŋana mi iŋoŋooŋo, na mbotmbot raami lela ruumu leleene pepe.  
\q1 Ambai be yooto ma wwa lem mat!   
\b  
\q1
\v 25 Sombe tomtom sa ileŋ uruunu ambaiŋana sa ta imbot lele molo mi imar,  
\q1 nako ikami ma leleene ambai, kembei tomtom ta ikam uraata ma niini isaana mi iwin ka yok lomoŋana.   
\q1
\v 26 Sombe wal sananŋan tikamam mbulu sananŋana mi tomtom ndeeŋeŋana sa igedgeede zin men,  
\q1 na ni kembei yok touŋana, som yok bukbukŋana ta imunmuundu ma isaana na.   
\b  
\q1
\v 27 Sombe tiwin bigil suruunu ma zaza, ina ambai som.  
\q1 Mi sombe takam kinkiini be zanda iwe biibi, ina tomini ambai som.   
\q1
\v 28 Sombe tomtom sa irao be iyaraama itunu som,  
\q1 na ni kembei kar ta ka siiri borok su lene, mi koroŋ sa imbot be ipakaala kan koi bizin mini som.   
\c 26  
\s1 Mbulu kizin wal kankaanŋan ta tizorzooro  
\q1
\v 1 Iti tuute: Sombe lele ibayou, na irao ŋauŋau isu na som. Mi sombe yaŋpat isu pa mazwaana ki kini ŋgaamaŋana, inako ipasaana kini.  
\q1 Ina raraate men pizin wal kankaanŋan ta tizorzooro na. Sombe tapakur zin, ina indeeŋe som. Pa kaimer zin ko tikam pataŋana piti. \x + \xo 26:1 \xt  Tut 17:16, 19:10\x*   
\q1
\v 2 Sombe tomtom sa ikam ŋoobo mbulu sa som, mi tisuŋ sosor pini be Merere ipasaani, na suŋŋana tana ko irao ikam kosa sa pini na som.  
\q1 Ina kembei man ta irie ma ila, mi le muriini sa be imbot pa na som.   
\q1
\v 3 Koroŋ ta boozomen kan uraata makiŋ. Re na, taballis zin hos pa. Mi wooro na, tuurur la bapolo kuzun bekena tapazal zin pa.  
\q1 Mi teene ta kembena. Imbotmbot be tabalis zin wal kankaanaŋan pa! Naso tepei ŋgar kizin. \x + \xo 26:3 \xt  Mbo 32:8-9; Tut 10:13\x*   
\q1
\v 4 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, pekel sua kizin talliŋana pepe.  
\q1 Kokena nu we kembei ta zin. \x + \xo 26:4 \xt  Tut 22:9; Mt 7:6\x*   
\q1
\v 5 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, zem zin ma tizzo sua kizin talliŋana pepe. Re be pekel.  
\q1 Kokena maane men, to nin se mi tindemeere sorok kembei tirao pa ŋgar.   
\q1
\v 6 Nu sombe ŋgo tomtom kankaanaŋana sa ma ila be iso kalŋom pizin wal pakan, nako kam pataŋana pa itum.  
\q1 Ina kembei nu yembut itum kumbum ma ila ne. Pa ni ko ila ma itooro kalŋom, to ikam ma malmal ipet. \x + \xo 26:6 \xt  Tut 10:26, 13:17\x*   
\q1
\v 7 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, sombe tikam sua tutŋana pizin tomtom, na asiŋ ko ileŋ la kalŋan? Som.  
\q1 Sua kizin ko mburaana som, kembei tomtom ta kumbuunu imeete mi kolkol ma imbotmbot.   
\q1
\v 8 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, tapakur zin pepe. Pa ina takam mbulu talliŋana tabe imiili piti mi ipasaana iti.  
\q1 Ina kembei tembe ta tuurpe kat som, mi ka pat imiili ma ipetepaala ndomondo na!   
\q1
\v 9 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, sombe tikam sua tutŋana pizin tomtom, na tire zin. Pa sua tana ko imiili pa zitun!  
\q1 Ina kembei tomtom ta iwin ma ikankaana, mi iteege wooro matanmatanŋana mi wooro tana iŋgal namaana.   
\q1
\v 10 Wal kankaanŋan ta tizorzooro na, mi zin wal ta tuute zin som na, tuur zin be tikam uraata piti pepe.  
\q1 Mbulu tana kankaanaŋana kat, kembei tomtom ta iwenweene sorok zin tomtom pa peene lutuunu.   
\q1
\v 11 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, irao tizem mbulu kizin talliŋana ma imborene kat na som.  
\q1 Kaimer ko tikam mini, kembei me ta ilulu, to imiili mi ikan luluŋana mini. \x + \xo 26:11 \xt  Mbo 85:8; Tut 23:35; 2Pe 2:22\x*   
\q1
\v 12 Wal kankaanaŋan, ina ipata piti be tepei ŋgar kizin.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so indemeere sorok kembei ni irao kat pa ŋgar, sombe totoombo be tepei ŋgar kini, nako tarao som kat.   
\s1 Mbulu kizin wal maolŋan  
\q1
\v 13 Wal maolŋan, sombe toso zin be tila ma tikam uraata, nako tipandelndel sua piti ma tiso:  
\q1 “Aiss, nio mburoŋ som. Pa laion biibi sa ko imbotmbot zaala ma iŋgi. Kokena imaŋga mi ikan yo!”   
\q1
\v 14 Wal maolŋan, sombe tikeene, na titortooro zin sala mbalia kizin, kembei kataama ta ilala mi imarmar.   
\q1
\v 15 Wal maolŋan na, tiŋgwol kat. Naman isula timbiiri leleene be tipei kan kini.  
\q1 Mi naman ipata be tiur ila kwon!   
\q1
\v 16 Wal maolŋan tire zitun kembei tirao kat pa ŋgar.  
\q1 Tipakurkur zitun ma tiso ŋgar kizin ilip pizin wal lamata mi ru ta len ŋgar na.   
\s1 Mbulu ta ipeyei ŋoŋi  
\q1
\v 17 Tomtom ta so izeizei lene ŋoŋi kizin wal pakan,  
\q1 ina ni kembei tomtom ta imbuulu me ki waene toro. Kozo ire i: Kokena me tana imaŋga mi ikani!   
\q1
\v 18-19 Tomtom ta so ikam sua pakaamŋana pa waene toro, mi kaimer isu mini mi iso: “A, kam ŋgar boozo pa sua tana pepe. Ina nio aŋkam ŋeu pu men.”  
\q1 Na tomtom ta kembei, ŋgar kini italli kat. Ni kembei tomtom kankaanaŋana ta iwenweene sorok zin tomtom pa peene lutuunu tau timus koroŋ sananŋana ise mataana mi you ikanan la.   
\q1
\v 20 Tesegergeere you, to ikanan. Som, to imeete.  
\q1 Mi ŋoŋi ta kembena. Sombe tomtom tininin kao pa som, nako karau men mi imap.   
\q1
\v 21 Tesegergeere you, to ikan ma biibi.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tizorzooro pa sua na, ta kembena. Ko tikam ma ŋoŋi iwe biibi.   
\q1
\v 22 Zin wal ta tininin kao na, tomtom lelen pa sua kizin ilip, kembei kini namutŋana.  
\q1 Mi tere iti. Pa sua kizin sananŋana tana ko isula kat lelende mi ipasaana ŋgar kiti.   
\s1 Takan la sorok sua kizin tomtom pepe. Kokena tipakaam ti.  
\q1
\v 23 Tomtom ta so ikamam sua mbuyeeneŋana piti, mi tamen ŋgar sananŋana imbotmbot la leleene,  
\q1 ina ni kembei kuuru ta tipot ndemeene ma imilmil kat, mi leleene na tiŋtiiŋgiŋana. \x + \xo 26:23 \xt  Mt 23:25\x*   
\q1
\v 24 Sombe itiŋan kanda koi bizin toso sua mi kalŋan ambai piti, na tendemeere zin pepe.  
\q1 Pa ŋgar sananŋana sa ko imbotmbot la lelen.   
\q1
\v 25 Tana kom koi sa isombe ikam sua ambaiŋana pu, na kan la sua kini pepe.  
\q1 Pa ŋgar sananŋan boozomen ta ko imbotmbot la leleene.   
\q1
\v 26 Ŋgar sananŋana ta imbotmbot la leleene na, ni irao iswe na som. Iturkewe.  
\q1 Tamen kaimer, ŋgar kini sananŋana mi pakaamŋana kini ko ipet mat ma tomtom tiute. \x + \xo 26:26 \xt  Lu 8:17\x*   
\q1
\v 27 Tomtom ta so ikel naala pizin wal pakan, nako itunu itop sula.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ipatimbil pat bekena ipasaana waene bizin pakan, inako pat tana ipili. \x + \xo 26:27 \xt  Mbo 7:16, 9:16, 57:6\x*   
\q1
\v 28 Tomtom ta so iurur koi pizin tomtom, nako ikam sua pakaamŋana pizin bekena ipasaana zin.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta kwon imbesmbeeze piti sorok na, tere iti pizin. Pa zin ko tipasaana iti.   
\c 27  
\q1
\v 1 Koroŋ tabe kam pa kaimer i, na pakur itum pa pepe.  
\q1 Pa mbulu tabe ipet i, ina nu ute som. \x + \xo 27:1 \xt  Lu 12:9-10; Yems 4:13-15\x*   
\q1
\v 2 Sombe wal pakan tiwe kwom mi tipakuru, ina ambai.  
\q1 Mi nu na, kam mbulu pakurŋana ma wit itum urum pepe. Pa ina mbulu ambai som. \x + \xo 27:2 \xt  2Kor 10:12,18\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 3 Pat ma magargaara na, koroŋ pataŋan. Tabaada na, ipata.  
\q1 Mi wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, ta kembena. Sombe tipagesges iti, ina pataŋana biibi kat be tabaada.   
\q1
\v 4 Mbulu ki ketende malmal mi ketende ibayou kat, ina ambai som. Pa sombe tomtom tipas ketende, inako tumuŋai zin som, mi teseseeze matan.  
\q1 Tamen mbulu ki matanda mburmbur, ina sananŋana ma ilip. Re sombe tomtom toro imbuuru ila ki waene, ko rao mender su kereene uunu? Som! \x + \xo 27:4 \xt  Tut 6:34\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 5 Waende sa isombe ikam ŋoobo mbulu mi iti tuur kat leleene pini, na tamaane pepe.  
\q1 Mbulu ki tozzo katkat sua pizin tomtom mi tapazalzal zin, ina ambai ma ilip.   
\q1
\v 6 Kom koi, ni irao ikam mbulu ambaimbaiŋan boozomen pu, bekena ipakaamu mi ikam lelem.  
\q1 Mi torom ŋonoono ta iurur kat leleene pu, na ni ko iyaamba katu mi ipazalu. \x + \xo 27:6 \xt  Mbo 141:5; Tut 15:31, 28:23; Mt 26:49-50\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 7 Tomtom ta so ikan kini ma kopoono bok, nako leleene be ikan kini mini som. Koroŋ ambaiŋana kat tomini kembei bigil suruunu, ni ko leleene pa som.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so peteli, na irao ipeleele kini sa na som. Kini sananŋana tomini, ni ko leleene pa mi ire kembei kini namutŋana.   
\q1
\v 8 Tomooto ta so izem ruumu mi wal kini ma timboren, mi ila ma iwwa le sorok,  
\q1 ni kembei man ta izem ŋgini kini raama lutuunu bizin ma timbot, mi irie ma ila lene pa lele pakaana toro.   
\q1
\v 9 Ŋgere mi koroŋ pakan ta kuzinŋan na, sombe tusuulu kulindi pa, ina ikamam ti ma nindi se mi lelende ambai.  
\q1 Mi torondo bizin ta kembena. Sombe tiuulu iti pa ŋgar ambaimbaiŋan pakan, ina ikam ti ma lelende ambai.   
\q1
\v 10 Itum torom bizin ziŋan tomom toroono bizin na, pizil ndemem pizin pepe.  
\q1 Mi sombe pataŋana sa indeeŋu mi toŋmatiziŋ ku timbotmbot molo, na la kizin pepe. Koŋuru zin wal ta timbotmbot kolouŋana pu na. Pa zin ko tikam ulaaŋa biibi pu ma tilip pizin toŋmatiziŋ ku ŋonoono. \x + \xo 27:10 \xt  Tut 17:17\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 11 O lutuŋ, motom iŋgal be swe ŋgar ambaiŋana men pizin tomtom. Naso kam ma leleŋ ambai.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tigiibi sua repiiliŋana pio, sombe tire mbulu ku, nako sua kizin imap.   
\q1
\v 12 Tomtom ta so le ŋgar, na irao iur itunu ila zaaba kwoono sorok na som. Sombe ikilaala kembei pataŋana be ipet, na loŋa men mi iru zaala be iko pa.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta len ŋgar biibi som na, tila men. Tabe tindeeŋe pataŋana. \x + \xo 27:12 \xt  Tut 7:21-23, 9:16-18\x*   
\q1
\v 13 Waem sa, sombe imbuk sua pa tomtom toro ta ni iute i som na ma iso: “Sombe nu rao be kot mbun ku som, na nio ko aŋmender pu mi aŋkot.” Ina ni ikam mbulu kankaanaŋana kat.  
\q1 Tana sombe ni iso pu be kam mbulu raraate men pini, na ndemeeri pepe. So pini be ikam koroŋ kini pakan ma imar imbot ku. Beso ni ikot som, to koroŋ kini tana iwe lem.   
\q1
\v 14 Sombe waem sa ikenne, mi mbeŋbeŋŋana mi nu la kini ma kalŋom izalla mi kam mankwoono pini, ko leleene ambai? Som.  
\q1 Ko kam ma keteene malmal kembei ta piri sua sananŋana pini.   
\b  
\q1
\v 15 Sombe kusindi bizin tinoknok zooroŋana mi tiŋoŋooŋo, inako tikam ma mbotŋana kiti isaana,  
\q1 kembei ruumu ta ka kooto sumbunsumbun, mi yaŋ itoptop su ruumu leleene na. \x + \xo 27:15 \xt  Tut 19:13\x*   
\q1
\v 16 Zin moori ta kembei, tayaraama zin, na tarao som.  
\q1 Ina kembei totoombo be teteege miiri, som koroŋ sipirpirŋana.   
\b  
\q1
\v 17 Sombe totwooro buza, na tere ka pail ta tiurpe pa ain na. Pa ain men ta irao ikam uraata pa ain.  
\q1 Mi ina raraate men piti tomtom. Bela taparuluulu iti pa ŋgar mi taparpazalzal ti, tona takam ma mbulu kiti iŋgeeze.   
\q1
\v 18 Tomtom ta so imborro kat ke fik, nako ikan ka ŋonoono.  
\q1 Mi zin mbesooŋo ta kembena. Sombe timboro kat uraata ta zin bibip kizin tiur la naman, nako zan iwe biibi. \x + \xo 27:18 \xt  Un 39:2-4; Mt 25:21; Lu 12:42-44; Yo 12:26; 2Tim 2:6\x*   
\q1
\v 19 Iti sombe lelende be tere ruŋgundu, na titiiri itundu ila yok.  
\q1 Mi sombe lelende be tuute iti tomtom pareiŋanda, na tere mbulu tau tomtom tikamam piti na. Pa ina iswe iti.   
\q1
\v 20 Meeteŋana ikam wal boozomen kek. Tamen imap zen.  
\q1 Mi iti tomtom ta kembena. Takam lende koroŋ boozo kek. Tamen toso: “Iŋgi irao zeen.” \x + \xo 27:20 \xt  Tut 30:15-16\x*   
\q1
\v 21 Tomtom tinenne gol ma silba, bekena tiute: Gol ma silba tana ambaiŋan som sananŋan?  
\q1 Mi iti tomtom ta kembena. Sombe tomtom tipakur ti, tona teswe itundu: iti pareiŋanda.   
\q1
\v 22 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, tirao be tizem mbulu kizin talliŋana na som.  
\q1 Sombe tupun zin ma ruŋgun isaana, ina tomini irao ikam zin ma tizem na som.   
\s1 Matanda iŋgalŋgal uraata kiti. Naso tombot ambai  
\q1
\v 23 Motom pizin mbili ku mi mboro zin ma timbot ambai.   
\q1
\v 24 Pa pat ma koroŋ ku pakan ko irao imbot ma alok na som.  
\q1 Mi king ziŋan zin bibip pakan ta kembena. Ko irao tikam peeze ma alok na som.   
\q1
\v 25-26 Tana ndemeere zin pepe. Mboro kat zin mbili ku. Beso mbutmbuutu ise pa abal zilŋanzilŋan, mi mazwaana ki yembutŋana ipet, mi tomtom tiur mbutmbuutu ilae pizin mbili be tikan, na mbili ku tana ko tipeebe ma boozo.  
\q1 Mi sipsip ma mekmek ku ko tiwe zaala pu be kam lem mburu, toono, ma koroŋ pakan.   
\q1
\v 27 Nu ko irao kam ŋgomo pa tui kizin mekmek ku,  
\q1 mi niomŋan wal ku mi zin mbesooŋo moori ku kombotmbot se ka pat.   
\c 28  
\q1
\v 1 Wal sananŋan mbulu kizin, ta ipakoikoi zin. Tana tomtom tiketoto zin som, mi tikowo len sorok.  
\q1 Mi wal ndeeŋeŋan na, timototo som. Timendernder mbolŋana kembei ta laion.   
\q1
\v 2 Lele sa, sombe ka tomtom bizin wal zorzooroŋan, nako tizirziiri zin peeze kan kizin kolouŋana kolouŋana.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so le ŋgar ambaiŋana mi ikilaala mbulu iŋgoi ta ambai ma ilip, nako ikam ma koroŋ ta boozomen iloondo ambai. \x + \xo 28:2 \xt  Tut 8:15-16, 29:4\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 3 Biibi ta so ikototo zin wal sorrokŋan,  
\q1 ina ni kembei yaŋpat ta isu mi ipasaana kini.   
\q1
\v 4 Zin wal ta tipakurkur zin wal sananŋan na, tiswe kembei tipizil ndemen pa tutu ki Anutu kek.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta matan iŋgalŋgal tutu kini mi titoto, na tikamam uraata be tikoto zin wal sananŋan.   
\q1
\v 5 Wal sananŋan tikilaala mbulu ndeeŋeŋana som.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tikamam kinkiini be tiute Yooba mibe timbot kolouŋana pini na, tiute mbulu ndeeŋeŋana ma imap.   
\q1
\v 6 Tomtom sorokŋana ta so ipa pai kini ma ambai men,  
\q1 na ilip pizin mbio uunu ta tipaŋobŋoobo pa zaala ambaiŋana na. \x + \xo 28:6 \xt  Tut 19:1\x*   
\q1
\v 7 Sombe lutundu bizin matan iŋgalŋgal tutu mi titoto, ina iswe kembei ŋgar kizin ipet kek.  
\q1 Mi sombe pikin sa igabgaaba zin wal tau tiwirri pat ma koroŋ kizin pa koroŋ soroksorok men, ina ni ipamiaŋ tamaana.   
\q1
\v 8 Sombe tomtom tikam mbun mar kiti, na toso pizin be tipekel raama gegeene biibi pepe.  
\q1 Pa pat ta so tondou pa zaala ta kembei, na Anutu ko itatke piti, mi ikam pizin wal ta tikampewe zin wal sorrokŋan na. \x + \xo 28:8 \xt  Kam 22:25\x*   
\q1
\v 9 Tomtom ta so izezeeze talŋaana pa tutu,  
\q1 na Anutu ko leleene be ileŋ suŋŋana kini ri sa som. \x + \xo 28:9 \xt  Mbo 66:18; Yo 9:31\x*   
\q1
\v 10 Tomtom ta so ipakamkaam zin wal ndeeŋeŋan mi iyaryaaru zin be tito zaala sananŋana, nako itop la itunu kilis kini.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta so tipa pai kizin ma ambai men, nako tikam len matamur ambaiŋana. \x + \xo 28:10 \xt  Tut 26:27; Mt 15:14; Ibr 6:12\x*   
\q1
\v 11 Zin mbio uunu nin se ma tindemeere sorok kembei zin len ŋgar biibi.  
\q1 Tamen zin wal sorrokŋan ta ŋgar kizin ipet kek na, tikilaala mbulu ta zin mbio uunu tikamam.   
\b  
\q1
\v 12 Sombe wal ndeeŋeŋan tilip pa kan koi bizin, na tomtom lelen ambai kat mi menmeen zin biibi.  
\q1 Mi sombe wal sananŋan timaŋga be tikam peeze, na tomtom tiru zaala be tike pizin. \x + \xo 28:12 \xt  Tut 29:2\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 13 Tomtom ta so iwatkaala sanaana kini, na mboti kini ko irao ambai kat na som.  
\q1 Mi sombe tomtom sa iswe sanaana kini mi izem, nako Anutu leleene isaana pini mi imuŋai i. \x + \xo 28:13 \xt  Mbo 32:3-5; 1Yo 1:9\x*   
\q1
\v 14 Tomtom ta so imototo Anutu mi mataana iŋgalŋgal itunu, nako leleene ambai mi kampeŋana ki Anutu imbotmbot se kini.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ŋgar kini imbolmbol se pa mbulu ki zooroŋana, na ni ko indeeŋe pataŋana. \x + \xo 28:14 \xt  Tut 14:16\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 15 Sombe tomtom sananŋana sa ikamam peeze mi ikototo zin wal sorrokŋan,  
\q1 ina ni kembei laion ta kalŋaana izalla, o bea ta ilonloondo ma ila be ikan tomtom.   
\q1
\v 16 Biibi sa isombe ikototo sorok zin wal ta timbot la ni kopo mbarmaana, ina iswe i kembei ŋgar kini ipet zen.  
\q1 Mi sombe biibi sa iurur koi pa mbulu ki watkeŋana, na ni ko imbot ambai su toono ma molo. \x + \xo 28:16 \xt  Tut 29:4\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 17 Tomtom ta so ipun tomtom toro ma imeete, na kaimer ko irao mbuleene su kat na som.  
\q1 Ko imototo mi leleene ipata pa mbulu kini tana ma irao meeteŋana kini.  
\q1 Mi ko irao ikam le gaabaŋana sa be ipomboli na som. \x + \xo 28:17 \xt  Un 4:14, 9:6; Kam 21:12-15\x*   
\q1
\v 18 Tomtom ta so ipa pai kini ma ambai men, nako Anutu itatke i pa pataŋana kini.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ipaŋobŋoobo pa zaala ambaiŋana, nako molo som to imeete ma isula lene Andewa. \x + \xo 28:18 \xt  Tut 12:13\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 19 Tomtom ta so ikamam uraata pa toono kini, nako irao kat pa ka kini.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tilala pa koroŋ soroksorok ta ŋonon somŋan i, nako tisu ma timbot ŋoobo kat.   
\q1
\v 20 Tomtom ta so izzo sua ŋonoono men mi itoto sua kini mbukŋana, nako indeeŋe kampeŋana biibi.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta gorgori tirru zaala pakaamŋana sa be karau men mi tindou len koroŋ boozo, na Anutu ko irao ileele zin na som. Zin kola tire kadoono pa mbulu kizin. \x + \xo 28:20 \xt  Tut 20:21, 21:5; 1Tim 6:6,9\x*   
\q1
\v 21 Sombe iti lende uraata be tiurpe pataŋana kizin tomtom, mi talae kizin wal pakan, ina mbulu ambai som. Bela takam mbulu raraate men pizin wal ta boozomen.  
\q1 Tamen zin bibip pakan ta titirtiiri sua i, sombe tomtom tikam len koroŋ rimen ŋonoono, nako tilae kizin mi tiuulu zin pa sua kizin. \x + \xo 28:21 \xt  Tut 24:23\x*   
\q1
\v 22 Zin wal ta matan konŋan na, tirru zaala be karau men mi tindou len koroŋ boozo.  
\q1 Mi tikilaala som. Zaala ta titoto na, kaimer ko ikam zin ma tisu ma timbot ŋoobo.   
\q1
\v 23 Nu sombe yaamba tomtom sa bekena pazali,  
\q1 na kaimer ni ko leleene ambai pu ma ilip pizin wal ta kwon imbesmbeeze pini sorok na. \x + \xo 28:23 \xt  Tut 9:8, 27:5\x*   
\q1
\v 24 Tomtom ta so ikam kuumbu pa tamaana ma naana, mana kaimer isu mi iso: “Nio aŋkam ŋoobo mbulu sa som.”  
\q1 Na ni kembei igabgaaba zin wal ta tikamam zigzik na. \x + \xo 28:24 \xt  Tut 19:26; Mt 15:4-6\x*   
\q1
\v 25 Zin wal ta matan koroŋŋan na, tipasansaana tomtom lelen, mi tikamam ma ŋoŋi iwedet.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ipase pa Yooba, nako imbot ambai mi itum kat.   
\q1
\v 26 Tomtom ta so ipase pa itunu, na ikankaana kat.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so itoto zaala ki ŋgar ambaiŋana, na pataŋana sa ko irao ipasaana kati na som. \x + \xo 28:26 \xt  Tut 3:5,7; 1Kor 3:18-20\x*   
\q1
\v 27 Tomtom ta so irairai koroŋ kini pakan pizin wal sorrokŋan, nako irao iru zalaana pa koroŋ sa som.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so irre zin men, mi iuluulu zin som, nako tigiibi sua sanaŋan boozo pini. \x + \xo 28:27 \xt  Mbo 109:15-16; Tut 19:17, 22:9\x*   
\q1
\v 28 Sombe wal sananŋan timaŋga be tikam peeze, na tomtom tiru zaala be tike pizin.  
\q1 Mi sombe wal sananŋan timeete ma tila len, inako zin wal ndeeŋeŋan timasak ma tiwe boozo. \x + \xo 28:28 \xt  Tut 11:10, 29:2\x*   
\c 29  
\q1
\v 1 Tomtom ta so imbelmbel sua pazalŋana leŋŋana, mi tamen inoknok men zooroŋana,  
\q1 nako lwoono sa to pataŋana biibi ipasaani. To zaala sa be imbot ambai mini na som.   
\q1
\v 2 Sombe wal ndeeŋeŋan timasak ma tiwe boozo, to tomtom menmeen zin mi lelen ambai kat.  
\q1 Mi sombe wal sananŋan tikamam peeze, na tomtom lelen ipata mi tikaraŋesŋeeze.\x + \xo 29:2 \xt  Kam 2:23-24; Tut 11:10, 28:12,28\x*   
\q1
\v 3 Pikin sa, sombe leleene ilip be ikam le ŋgar ambaiŋana, nako ikam ma tamaana leleene ambai kat.  
\q1 Mi pikin ta so igabgaaba zin moori zaala lwoono kan, nako ipasaana koroŋ ki tamaana.\x + \xo 29:3 \xt  Tut 10:1, 15:20, 27:11; Lu 15:13-30\x*   
\q1
\v 4 King ta so ikamam mbulu ndeeŋeŋana men, nako ipombol zin tomtom be tikam mbulu ambaiŋana, mi lele kini imbot ambai.  
\q1 Mi king ta so mata koroŋŋana mi isombe tomtom tiŋgiimi i, tona iuulu zin, nako ikam ma lele kini isaana.\x + \xo 29:4 \xt  Tut 16:12, 28:16\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 5 Tomtom ta so kwoono imbesmbeeze pa waene toro,  
\q1 na iurpewe kilis pini be ikeeni.   
\q1
\v 6 Zooroŋana kizin wal sananŋan ko iwe kilis pizin mi ipasaana zin.  
\q1 Mi wal ndeeŋeŋan na, zin lelen ambai men mi tilonloondo ma tila pa zaala ambaiŋana.   
\b  
\q1
\v 7 Wal ndeeŋeŋan tikamam ŋgar biibi pizin wal sorrokŋan, mi lelen be tikam ŋoobo zin som.  
\q1 Mi wal sananŋan na, tikamam ŋgar pa koroŋ ta kembei som.   
\q1
\v 8 Zin wal ta tipakurkur zitun mi tirepilpiili ŋgar ambaiŋana na, tipesese zin tomtom be tipasaana kar.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta len ŋgar ambaiŋana na, tipalumluumu tomtom lelen bekena keten malmalŋana kizin imap.   
\q1
\v 9 Tomtom ta le ŋgar ambaiŋana na, isombe ipamender tomtom kankaanaŋana sa pa sua,  
\q1 nako tomtom kankaanaŋana tana kalŋaana izalla mi ikam sua repiiliŋana boozo pini. Irao iur niini na som.   
\q1
\v 10 Zin wal ta tipa pai kizin ma ambai men na, wal ta tikamam zaaba pizin tomtom tiurur koi pizin.  
\q1 Mi wal ndeeŋeŋan na, tikamam kinkiini be tiuulu zin ma timbot ambai.   
\q1
\v 11 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, tirao be tiyaraama keten malmalŋana kizin som. Tizzwe ma imbot mat.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta le ŋgar ambaiŋana na, ni iyaramraama itunu.   
\b  
\q1
\v 12 Tomtom peeze kana sa isombe ileŋleŋ la sua pakaamŋana,  
\q1 na wal uraata kan kini ko timap ma tiwe wal sananŋan.   
\q1
\v 13 Wal sorrokŋan mi zin bibip ta tiseseeze tomtom matan na, zin raraate som. Mi koroŋ tamen ta ilup zin:  
\q1 Yooba ipayaryaara zin mi ikiskis zin, ta timbot matan yaryaara.\x + \xo 29:13 \xt  Mt 5:45\x*   
\q1
\v 14 King ta so iurpewe pataŋana kizin wal sorrokŋan ma indeŋdeeŋe men,  
\q1 na peeze kini ko imbol ma imbotmbot.   
\b  
\q1
\v 15 Sombe tabalis zin tomtom mi tapazal zin, nako tikam len ŋgar ambaiŋana.  
\q1 Mi sombe tezem pikin sa ma inoknok mbulu sananŋana, na kaimer ni ko ipamiaŋ naana.\x + \xo 29:15 \xt  Tut 13:24, 22:6,15, 23:13\x*   
\q1
\v 16 Sombe wal sananŋan timasak ma tiwe boozo, na mbulu sananŋana ko ipet ma iwe biibi.  
\q1 Tamen kaimer wal ndeeŋeŋan ko tire kat ki matan ta kembei: Wal sananŋan ko tisu ma mburan imap.   
\q1
\v 17 Pazal lutum. Naso lelem ipata som mi mbotmbot raama menmeenu.  
\q1 Pa ni ko ikamu ma lelem ndabok kat.   
\q1
\v 18 Sombe Anutu kwoono bizin tizzwe sua kini som, nako tomtom timaŋga mi tikam mbulu bozboozo. Pa koroŋ sa be iyaraama zin mini som.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so mataana iŋgalŋgal tutu ki Anutu mi itoto, nako leleene ambai mi kampeŋana ki Anutu imbotmbot se kini.   
\b  
\q1
\v 19 Nu sombe so sua men pa mbesooŋo ku, nako rao urpe mbulu kini na som.  
\q1 Ŋonoono, sua ni ileŋleŋ. Mi ko irao ikan la na som. Bela nu balisi, tona ileŋ la kalŋom.   
\q1
\v 20 Wal kankaanaŋan ta tizorzooro na, ipata pizin be titooro mbulu kizin.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ikam kat ŋgar som, mi iwirri sorok sua, nako ipata kat pini be itooro mbulu kini.\x + \xo 29:20 \xt  Tut 26:12; Yems 1:19\x*   
\q1
\v 21 Sombe mbesooŋo ku naŋgaŋŋana mi kwom ikanani pa uraata som,  
\q1 na kaimer ni ko irao ikam kat uraata som, mi ikam pataŋana pu.   
\q1
\v 22 Tomtom ta so keteene bayouŋana, nako ipeyei ŋoŋi boozo,  
\q1 mi itunu ikamam sanaana boozo.   
\b  
\q1
\v 23 Mbulu ki tapakurkur itundu ko ikam ti ma kanda miaŋ.  
\q1 Mi sombe tomtom sa ikototo itunu mi imbesmbeeze pizin tomtom, ina zaala tabe zaana iwe biibi.\x + \xo 29:23 \xt  Tut 15:33, 18:12; Lu 14:11; 1Pe 5:5\x*   
\q1
\v 24 Nu sombe gaaba tomtom toro pa mbulu ki kuumbu, na ur itum ila pataŋana.  
\q1 Pa kaimer, sombe tipamenderu, mi tiso pu be so kat sua ŋonoono ila Anutu mataana, nako kam so? Pa sombe swe mbulu ku tana, nako tiur kadoono pu. Mi sombe watkaala, nako Anutu itunu keteene malmal pu mi ipasaanu.   
\q1
\v 25 Mbulu ki tomototo zin tomtom ko iwe kilis piti.  
\q1 Mi tomtom ta so ipase pa Yooba, na Yooba ko mataana pini mi imboro i ma imbot ambai. Irao koroŋ sa ipasaani na som.\x + \xo 29:25 \xt  Mt 10:28; Yo 12:42-43; Ŋgo 4:18-21\x*   
\q1
\v 26 Wal boozomen tirru zaala be tila tire zin peeze kan. Pa tiso ko zin tiuulu zin pa pataŋana kizin.  
\q1 Mi tundu ŋonoono na Yooba. Pa ni ta iuluulu kat iti pa pataŋana kiti.   
\q1
\v 27 Wal ndeeŋeŋan lelen pizin wal sananŋan ri sa som.  
\q1 Mi wal sananŋan ta kembena. Lelen pizin wal ta titoto zaala ambaiŋana na ri sa som kat.   
\c 30  
\s1 Sua pakan ki Agur  
\q1
\v 1 Iŋgi sua ki Agur ta Yake lutuunu na. Ŋgar taiŋgi, Anutu iswe pini.  
\b  
\q1 Ni iso ta kembei: “O Anutu, nio niŋ isaana kek.  
\q1 Ŋonoono kat, iŋgi niŋ isaana ma mburoŋ imap kat.   
\q1
\v 2 Nio ti, kembei tomtom som. Pa leŋ ŋgar ri sa som kat.  
\q1 Wal boozomen ta timbotmbot toono na, ŋgar kizin ilip pio.   
\q1
\v 3 Nio, tipaute yo pa ŋgar ambaiŋana som.  
\q1 Mi Anutu potomŋana na, aŋute kati som.   
\q1
\v 4 Lak, asiŋ ta isala saamba, mi isu mini be iso ka sua?  
\q1 Mi asiŋ ta ikiskis miiri ila namaana keteene,  
\q1 mi iurur yaŋ ilala miiri tiene?  
\q1 Asiŋ iur toono ka seŋgaaŋa ta boozomen?  
\q1 Ni zaana asiŋ, mi lutuunu zaana asiŋ?  
\q1 Sombe nu ute, na so yo lak!   
\b  
\q1
\v 5 Anutu sua kini ta boozomen na, totoombo ma tikilaala kek: Ina ŋonoono men.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta tipase pini be iporoukaala zin na, ni iwe siŋgiao pizin. \x + \xo 30:5 \xt  Mbo 12:6, 18:30, 91:4\x*   
\q1
\v 6 Re: Kokena pagaaba sua ku ila raama sua kini,  
\q1 to ni iyaambu, mi tomtom tiso nu kwom pakamkaamŋom. \x + \xo 30:6 \xt  Tur 22:18\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 7 O Yooba, koroŋ ru ta nio leleŋ be aŋwi u pa.  
\q1 Mazwaana ta aŋbotmbot su toono na, ruutu koroŋ ru taiŋgi pio pepe.   
\q1
\v 8 Mbulu boozomen ta pakamkaamŋan mi ŋonon somŋan na, ziiri ma timbotmbot molo pio.  
\q1 Mboro kat yo. Kokena leŋ koroŋ som mi aŋbot ŋoobo, som leŋ koroŋ boozo mete. Kam koŋ kini ta irao yo. \x + \xo 30:8 \xt  Mt 6:11; 1Tim 6:8\x*   
\q1
\v 9 Pa sombe leŋ koroŋ boozo mete, nako aŋpizil ndemeŋ pu mi aŋrepiilu ma aŋso: “Yooba, ni asiŋ?”  
\q1 Mi sombe leŋ koroŋ som mi aŋbot ŋoobo, nako aŋkam kuumbu mi aŋpamiaŋ Anutu tio zaana.   
\b  
\q1
\v 10 La ki biibi sa ma ŋgal sorok sua pa mbesooŋo kini pepe.  
\q1 Kokena mbesooŋo tana ileŋ, to isuŋ Anutu be ipasaanu.  
\q1 Pa nu uunu ku.   
\s1 Wal pakan ta tembel zin kek  
\q1
\v 11 Tomtom pakan, zin tizuŋzuŋ Anutu be ikampe nan bizin som,  
\q1 mi tigibgiibi sua sananŋan boozomen pa taman bizin.   
\q1
\v 12 Mi wal pakan na, tire zitun kembei mbulu kizin iŋgeeze men.  
\q1 Tamen mbulu kizin pakan ta tikamam ki keŋana na, sananŋana kat. Iŋgeeze som.   
\q1
\v 13 Mi tomtom pakan na, tipakurkur zitun,  
\q1 mi matan pasom waen bizin pakan ma tau!   
\q1
\v 14 Mi wal pakan na, kwon kembei ta buza. Sua kizin ipasansaana kat zin wal sorrokŋan ta timbotmbot raama pataŋana na,  
\q1 Pa tisombe tipambiriizi zin ma timap kat pa toono.   
\b  
\q1
\v 15 Wal pakan, zin kembei ta ndeeme i.  
\q1 Pa gorgori tizzo ta kembei: “Kam leŋ koroŋ. Kam koŋ koroŋ.”  
\b  
\q1 Koroŋ paŋ, ta gorgori tizzo ta kembei: “Iŋgi amkam irao zeen.”   
\q1
\v 16 Koroŋ ta kembei: Meeteŋana, zin moori ta kopon somŋan, toono ta ka yok somŋana mi ikerekere na, mi you.   
\b  
\q1
\v 17 Tomtom ta so mata pasom tamaana, mi irepilpiili naana mi izorzooro la kalŋaana, na meeteŋana kini ko ambai som kat, mi irao titwi i na som.  
\q1 Putuunu ko imbot mat mi man aŋkor timar ma tipai mata kutuluunu mi tikan!   
\b  
\q1
\v 18-19 Mbulu tel ta tipa ndel kat.  
\q1 Aŋkam ŋgar pa ma aŋrao som.  
\q1 Mbulu ki manboŋ ta irie pa maŋaanaŋana na,  
\q1 mbulu ki mooto ta iwwa se pat na,  
\q1 mi mbulu ki wooŋgo ta ikowo pa tai na.  
\q1 Mi toro ta iwe paŋ pa na, ina mbulu tau zin naŋgaŋ ma tamuriŋriŋ tikamam. Aŋkam ŋgar pa ma aŋrao som kat.   
\q1
\v 20 Mbulu kizin raraate kembei zin moori tau timololo ula ka tutu na.  
\q1 Pa zin kembei tikan kini, to timus kwon ma tiso: “Niam ti amkam ŋoobo mbulu sa som.”   
\b  
\q1
\v 21 Mbulu paŋ ta iwedet su toono, mi tamen irao pa iti tomtom ŋgar kiti som.  
\q1 Tere na, tumurur pa.   
\q1
\v 22 Ta na, mbulu tau mbesooŋo sorok iwe king.  
\q1 Mi iwe ru pa na, mbulu tau wal kankaanaŋan timbot ambai mi tirao kat pa kan kini mi len koroŋ.   
\q1
\v 23 To iwe tel pa na, mbulu tau moori sa iwoolo, mi tamen kusiini iurur leleene pini som.  
\q1 Mi iwe paŋ pa na, mbulu tau mbesooŋo moori sa ikam moori ta imborro i na muriini ma iwe biibi pini.   
\b  
\q1
\v 24 Koroŋ munmun paŋ ta timbotmbot toono, mi len ŋgar biibi kat. Koroŋ ta kembei:   
\q1
\v 25 Ta na, moolo. Pa zin len mburan biibi som.  
\q1 Tamen mazwaana ki zoŋ na, tikamam uraata biibi bekena tindoundou kan kini. Beso yaŋ imar ma lele isaana, to kan kini imbotmbot. Tiru zalan som.   
\q1
\v 26 Mi iwe ru pa na, moozo. Pa zin tomini len mburan biibi som.  
\q1 Tamen gorgori tirru len lele be tike lela mi timbot ambai.   
\q1
\v 27 Mi iwe tel pa na, siizi pakan. Pa zin len king sa som.  
\q1 Tamen sombe tipa, na tiparto zin mi tipa raraate men.   
\q1
\v 28 Mi iwe paŋ pa na, ŋguloŋ. Pa ina koroŋ musaana. Irao teteege pa namanda.  
\q1 Tamen timbotmbot lela ruumu bibip kizin king tomini.   
\b  
\q1
\v 29 Mi koroŋ paŋ ta tizarra kan mbooro mi tiwwa. Tana lelende be terre lende.   
\q1
\v 30 Ta na, laion. Pa ni mburaana biibi ma ilip pa koroŋ boozomen ta tiwwa pa toono na.  
\q1 Tana kosasa irao ikami ma iko na som.   
\q1
\v 31 Mi iwe ru pa na, man tatariigi ta iwwa.  
\q1 To iwe tel pa na, mekmek.  
\q1 Mi iwe paŋ pa na, king ta iwwa raama zin malmal kan kini.   
\b  
\q1
\v 32 Sombe nu kamam ŋgar be kam mbulu kankaanaŋana mi pakur itum, som lelem iurur pa mbulu sananŋana, na ambai be so sua sa pepe.  
\q1 Maane men, mi zem ŋgar pa mbulu tana.   
\q1
\v 33 Sombe totooro tui, nako iwe bata.  
\q1 Mi sombe tumbuulu tomtom sa kuzuunu, nako takam ma siŋ isu.  
\q1 Mi sombe tapamalmal tomtom keten, nako takam ma malmal ipet!   
\c 31  
\s1 Sua ki King Lemuel  
\q1
\v 1 Iŋgi sua ki King Lemuel. Ŋgar taiŋgi, Anutu iswe la ki Lemuel naana, mi naana kadoono ikam la kini.   
\b  
\q1
\v 2 O lutuŋ, nom ŋonoono ta nio i. Indeeŋe ta nu mbotmbot men lela kopoŋ leleene na, aŋbuk sua pa Anutu be aŋuru ma we ni lene.  
\q1 Tana kozo ŋgun talŋom pa sua tio ti.   
\q1
\v 3 Re: Kokena pasaana koroŋ ku pizin moori mi zem mburom pizin.  
\q1 Pa ina zaala ta ipasansaana king boozomen ma tizanzaana pa i.   
\b  
\q1
\v 4 O Lemuel, motom iŋgal. Zin wal ta tikamam peeze na, yok mbolŋana irao ipasiksik ŋguren na pepe.   
\q1
\v 5 Kokena tiwin, to matan mbeleele tutu ta imbot pataaŋa kek na,  
\q1 mi tiurpe kat pataŋana kizin wal sorrokŋan som.   
\q1
\v 6 Yok mbolŋana mi baen, ina king koroŋ kizin som.  
\q1 Ina koroŋ kizin wal ta tikamam be timeete i, mi zin wal ta lelen ipata kat ma timbotmbot.   
\q1
\v 7 Pa zin wal ta len koroŋ som ma timbot ŋoobo, mi zin wal ta lelen ipata kat na, tiwinin bekena matan mbeleele pataŋana kizin.   
\b  
\q1
\v 8 Zin wal ta tirao be tiporoukaala zitun som na, sombe tomtom tikam ŋoobo zin, na nu maane pepe. Maŋga mi so sua bekena uulu zin.  
\q1 Zin wal ta timbotmbot raama pataŋana na, mender pizin mi urpe pataŋana kizin ma indeeŋe men.   
\q1
\v 9 Tana sombe tomtom timbotmbot raama pataŋana mi tiru zalan na, nu maane pepe. Maŋga mi so sua bekena uulu zin.  
\q1 Mender pizin, mi urpe pataŋana kizin ma indeeŋe men.   
\s1 Mbulu ki moori ambaiŋana  
\q1
\v 10 Sombe tomooto sa leleene be iwoolo, mi indeeŋe moori ŋonoono ta ikamam kat mbulu, na ni ikam le koroŋ ambaiŋana kat.  
\q1 Zin moori ta kembei tilip pa pat milmilŋan ta kan kadon bibip i. Tamen zin boozo som. Ko tendeeŋe zin la ki parei? \x + \xo 31:10 \xt  Rut 3:11; Tut 18:22, 19:14\x*  
\v 11 Moori ta kembei na, kusiini ko irao ipase pini kat.  
\q1 Mi ni ko iuulu kusiini be ikam koroŋ ndabokbokŋan boozo. \x + \xo 31:11 \xt  Tut 12:4, 14:1\x*  
\v 12 Mazwaana ta imbotmbot su toono, na ikamam mbulu ambaiŋana men pa kusiini.  
\q1 Irao ikam mbulu sananŋana sa pini na som.   
\q1
\v 13 Ni moori nama mosŋana. Irao iurpe sipsip rumuunu mi koroŋ pakan ma iwe mburu be tomtom tizeebe zin pa.  
\q1 Mi ni mata seŋana, mi ikamam uraata raama menmeeni.   
\q1
\v 14 Ni kembei wooŋgo ta ilala lele molo mi ikamam koroŋ popoŋan ma timar.  
\q1 Pa ilala irru kini matakiŋa bekena ikam pa wal kini.   
\q1
\v 15 Mbeŋbeŋŋana mi ni imaŋgaŋga be iteege you pa wal kini,  
\q1 mi iurur zin mbesooŋo moori kini pa uraata.   
\q1
\v 16 Ni irru toono ambaimbaiŋan be iŋgiimi ma iwe lene.  
\q1 Mi iŋgiimi toono tana pa pat ta ikamam pa uraata kini na, mi ipaaza ke baen isula.   
\q1
\v 17 Ni maolŋana som.  
\q1 Ni moori uraataŋana.   
\q1
\v 18 Mburooŋo ta ni ikamam na, isipirpir som. Ire kembei iurur ŋonoono.  
\q1 Mi lam kini na, imetmeete som. Pa ni ikamam uraata pa mbeŋ tomini.   
\q1
\v 19 Ni iurpewe koroŋ pakan be isese ma iwe mburu.   
\q1
\v 20 Mi iwelweele namaana mi irairai koroŋ pakan pizin wal sorrokŋan.  
\q1 Mi zin wal ta timbotmbot raama pataŋana na tomini, ni iuluulu zin.   
\q1
\v 21 Sombe lele isaana, na ni irao ikam ŋgar boozo pa na som. Pa iparaŋraŋ wal kini len mburu pataaŋa kek.  
\q1 Wal kini tizebzeebe zin pa mburu ambaimbaiŋan men.   
\q1
\v 22 Tana irao nin tekteege pa mbeŋ som. Pa ni iurpewe len mburu be tikototo zin pa.  
\q1 Mi ni itunu na, izebzeebi pa mburu ndabokbokŋan ta kan mos ambaimbaiŋan na.   
\b  
\q1
\v 23 Tomooto ta so iwoolo moori ta kembei, isombe ila ma ziŋan zin kolman tilup zin pa sua, nako tomtom len ŋger pini, mi tire i kembei tomtom ŋonoono.   
\b  
\q1
\v 24 Moori ta kembei, ni isese mburu ambaimbaiŋan mi ikamam ŋgomo pa.  
\q1 Mi iurpewe pus bekena tomtom tiŋgiimi mi tila tikam ŋgomo pa.   
\q1
\v 25 Mbulu kini ŋgeezeŋana ta iwe aigau pini, mi ikam ma tomtom tipakuri ma tiso ni moori ŋonoono.  
\q1 Mi mbulu tabe ipet pa kaimer i, na ni imototo som. Pa mbulu pareiŋana ta so ipet, na ni ko imender mbolŋana.   
\q1
\v 26 Ni izzo sua raama ŋgar.  
\q1 Mi ipaute wal kini be tiurur kat lelen pa Anutu mi zin tomtom.   
\q1
\v 27 Ni imborro kat ruumu kini.  
\q1 Irao imbomboorene mi ikam mbulu kembei ta wal maolŋan na som. Ikamam kat uraata.   
\b  
\q1
\v 28 Moori ŋonoono ta kembei na, lutuunu bizin ko lelen ambai pini mi tipakurkuri.  
\q1 Mi kusiini tomini ko iwidit uruunu ma iso ta kembei:   
\q1
\v 29 “Moori boozomen tirao pa mbulu.  
\q1 Mi nu na, lip kat pizin.”   
\b  
\q1
\v 30 Tana moori ruŋgun, som mbulu kizin pakan ta ikamam zin tomooto lelen, na takam ŋgar pa pepe. Pa ina koroŋ ŋonoono som. Imbot rimen mi imap.  
\q1 Mi moori ta so imototo Yooba mi ileŋleŋ la kalŋaana, to tapakuri. \x + \xo 31:30 \xt  Tut 11:22\x*  
\v 31 Pa ni ikamam kat mbulu. Tana iti tapakuri pa uraata ta ni ikamam na,  
\q1 mi tiwit uruunu ila iwal biibi matan, to indeeŋe.   